#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce provides several options to organize the ordering and "
"checkout process. It offers different :ref:`order button <ecommerce/checkout/"
"order-buttons>` options and sequential :ref:`checkout steps <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>`, some of which support additional features. The related "
"buttons and checkout pages can be customized using the :doc:`website editor "
"<../website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce ponuja več možnosti za organizacijo procesa naročanja in "
"blagajne. Ponuja različne možnosti :ref:`gumba za naročilo <ecommerce/"
"checkout/order-buttons>` in zaporedne :ref:`korake blagajne <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>`, od katerih nekateri podpirajo dodatne funkcije. Povezani "
"gumbi in strani blagajne se lahko prilagodijo z uporabo :doc:`urejevalnika "
"spletnih strani <../website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:14
msgid "Order buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi za naročilo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:16
msgid "To customize the ordering process in Odoo eCommerce, you can:"
msgstr "Za prilagoditev postopka naročanja v Odoo eCommerce lahko:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:18
msgid ""
"change the :ref:`Add to Cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>` button's "
"behavior;"
msgstr ""
"spremenite obnašanje gumba :ref:`Dodaj v košarico <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-"
"cart>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:19
msgid ""
"replace it with a :ref:`customized <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-sale>` button;"
msgstr ""
"ga zamenjajte s :ref:`prilagojenim <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-sale>` gumbom;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:20
msgid "add a :ref:`Buy now <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>` button."
msgstr "dodajte gumb :ref:`Kupi zdaj <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:25
msgid "Add to cart options"
msgstr "Možnosti dodajanja v košarico"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:28
msgid "Default add to cart behavior"
msgstr "Privzeto vedenje dodajanja v košarico"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:30
msgid ""
"When clicking the :guilabel:`Add to cart` button, different actions can be "
"triggered. To configure them, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` "
"section, and select one of the following options for the :guilabel:`Add to "
"Cart` feature:"
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico`, se lahko sprožijo različna "
"dejanja. Če jih želite konfigurirati, pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno "
"mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in izberite eno od naslednjih možnosti za "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Stay on Product Page`: The customer remains on the product page "
"after adding a product to the cart. If the added product has "
"linked :ref:`optional products <ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`, the "
"customer can choose between :guilabel:`Add to cart` (to stay on the product "
"page) and :guilabel:`Go to Checkout` :icon:`fa-chevron-right` (to be "
"redirected to the cart)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ostani na strani izdelka`: Stranka ostane na strani izdelka po "
"dodajanju izdelka v košarico. Če ima dodani izdelek povezane :ref:`izbirne "
"izdelke <ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`, lahko stranka izbira "
"med :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico` (da ostane na strani izdelka) "
"in :guilabel:`Pojdi na blagajno` :icon:`fa-chevron-right` (da se preusmeri v "
"košarico)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Go to cart`: The customer is redirected to the cart immediately."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pojdi v košarico`: Stranka je takoj preusmerjena v košarico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:45
msgid "Button customization"
msgstr "Prilagoditev gumba"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:47
msgid ""
"You can replace the :guilabel:`Add to Cart` button with a :guilabel:`Contact "
"Us` button, which redirects users to the default contact form."
msgstr ""
"Gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico` lahko nadomestite z "
"gumbom :guilabel:`Kontaktirajte nas`, ki preusmeri uporabnike na privzeti "
"kontaktni obrazec."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:51
msgid ""
"Removing the ability to add products to the cart is often used by businesses "
"that want to display an online catalog but cannot share prices publicly "
"(e.g., to offer custom or variable pricing)."
msgstr ""
"Odstranitev možnosti dodajanja izdelkov v košarico pogosto uporabljajo "
"podjetja, ki želijo prikazati spletni katalog, vendar ne morejo javno deliti "
"cen (npr. za ponudbo cen po meri ali spremenljivih cen)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:54
msgid ""
"To display the :guilabel:`Contact Us` button, you need to :ref:`hide prices "
"<ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` on the product page. When the customer "
"clicks the :guilabel:`Contact Us` button, by default, they are redirected to "
"the contact form where the :guilabel:`Subject` field is already auto-filled "
"with the requested product's name."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz gumba :guilabel:`Kontaktirajte nas` morate :ref:`skriti cene "
"<ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` na strani izdelka. Ko stranka klikne "
"gumb :guilabel:`Kontaktirajte nas`, je privzeto preusmerjena na kontaktni "
"obrazec, kjer je polje :guilabel:`Zadeva` že samodejno izpolnjeno z imenom "
"zahtevanega izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:60
msgid "Additional add to cart buttons"
msgstr "Dodatni gumbi za dodajanje v košarico"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:62
msgid ""
"You can add additional :guilabel:`Add to Cart` buttons and link them to "
"specific products on any website page. To add them, open the website editor "
"and place the :guilabel:`Add to Cart Button` inner content building block. "
"Once placed, click the button, scroll to the :guilabel:`Add to Cart Button` "
"section, and configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Na katero koli spletno stran lahko dodate dodatne gumbe :guilabel:`Dodaj v "
"košarico` in jih povežete z določenimi izdelki. Za dodajanje odprite "
"urejevalnik spletnega mesta in postavite gradnik notranje "
"vsebine :guilabel:`Gumb Dodaj v košarico`. Ko je postavljen, kliknite gumb, "
"pomaknite se do razdelka :guilabel:`Gumb Dodaj v košarico` in konfigurirajte "
"naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:67
msgid ":guilabel:`Product`: Select the product to link the button with."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Izdelek`: Izberite izdelek, ki ga želite povezati z gumbom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Action`: Choose whether to use an :guilabel:`Add to Cart` "
"or :ref:`Buy Now <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>` button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dejanje`: Izberite, ali želite uporabiti gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj v "
"košarico` ali :ref:`Kupi zdaj <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:72
msgid ""
"If the product has variants, either choose one or leave the option set "
"to :guilabel:`Visitor's Choice`, which prompts the customer to select a "
"variant before choosing to :guilabel:`Add to cart` and continue shopping or "
"to :guilabel:`Go to Checkout`."
msgstr ""
"Če ima izdelek variante, izberite eno ali pa pustite možnost nastavljeno "
"na :guilabel:`Izbira obiskovalca`, kar stranko pozove, naj izbere varianto, "
"preden se odloči za :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico` in nadaljuje nakupovanje "
"ali za :guilabel:`Pojdi na blagajno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:75
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Add to cart` button does not offer those options, but "
"its label can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico` ne ponuja teh možnosti, vendar je "
"mogoče spremeniti njegovo oznako."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:79
msgid ""
"In the website editor, it is also possible to show or hide the :icon:`fa-"
"shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`cart`) icon in the page's header. To do so, click "
"the header, go to the :guilabel:`Style`, navigate to the :guilabel:`Show/"
"Hide Elements` section, and toggle the :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` "
"(:guilabel:`cart`) button next to the :guilabel:`Show Empty` option. If it "
"is not enabled, the cart icon appears only when an item is added to the "
"cart. The number of items in the cart is also displayed next to the icon."
msgstr ""
"V urejevalniku spletnega mesta je mogoče tudi prikazati ali skriti "
"ikono :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`košarica`) v glavi strani. Za to "
"kliknite glavo, pojdite na :guilabel:`Slog`, se pomaknite do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Prikaži/skrij elemente` in preklopite gumb :icon:`fa-"
"shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`košarica`) poleg možnosti :guilabel:`Prikaži "
"prazno`. Če ni omogočeno, se ikona košarice prikaže le, ko je element dodan "
"v košarico. Poleg ikone je prikazano tudi število elementov v košarici."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:89
msgid "Buy now"
msgstr "Kupi sedaj"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:91
msgid ""
"To let customers choose to go directly to the :ref:`Order summary <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>` step, add an additional :guilabel:`Buy now` button. "
"To do so, go to any product's page, open the website editor, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Buy Now` "
"button next to the :guilabel:`Purchase Options`."
msgstr ""
"Da strankam omogočite izbiro za neposreden prehod na korak :ref:`Povzetek "
"naročila <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`, dodajte dodaten "
"gumb :guilabel:`Kupi zdaj`. Za to pojdite na stran katerega koli izdelka, "
"odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in "
"kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Kupi zdaj` "
"poleg :guilabel:`Možnosti nakupa`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:None
msgid "Buy now button"
msgstr "Gumb kupi zdaj"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:102
msgid "Reorder products"
msgstr "Ponovno naročilo izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:104
msgid "Customers can reorder items from a previous sales order:"
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko ponovno naročijo izdelke iz prejšnjega prodajnega naloga:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:106
msgid ""
"from their customer portal, using the :guilabel:`Order Again` button. All "
"products from the selected order are automatically added to the cart, and "
"customers can then :guilabel:`Remove` any items they don't want to reorder."
msgstr ""
"iz svojega portala za stranke z uporabo gumba :guilabel:`Naroči ponovno`. "
"Vsi izdelki iz izbranega naročila so samodejno dodani v košarico, stranke pa "
"lahko nato :guilabel:`Odstranijo` vse artikle, ki jih ne želijo ponovno "
"naročiti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:0
msgid "Reorder button"
msgstr "Gumb za ponovno naročanje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:113
msgid ""
"from the cart, by clicking :guilabel:`Quick reorder` at the :ref:`Order "
"summary step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`. Customers can then adjust "
"quantities as needed and click the :icon:`fa-cart-plus` :guilabel:`(cart)` "
"button next to the product(s) they want to reorder."
msgstr ""
"iz košarice s klikom na :guilabel:`Hitro ponovno naročanje` v :ref:`koraku "
"Pregled naročila <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`. Stranke lahko nato "
"prilagodijo količine po potrebi in kliknejo gumb :icon:`fa-cart-"
"plus` :guilabel:`(košarica)` poleg izdelkov, ki jih želijo ponovno naročiti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:0
msgid "Quick reorder button"
msgstr "Gumb za hitro ponovno naročanje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:123
msgid "Checkout steps"
msgstr "Koraki zaključka nakupa"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:125
msgid "During checkout, customers are taken through the following steps:"
msgstr "Med postopkom nakupa so stranke vodene skozi naslednje korake:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:127
msgid ":ref:`Order summary <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Pregled naročila <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:128
msgid ":ref:`Address <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Naslov <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:129
msgid ":ref:`Extra Info (if enabled) <ecommerce/checkout/extra_step>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dodatne informacije (če je omogočeno) <ecommerce/checkout/extra_step>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:130
msgid ":ref:`Payment <ecommerce/checkout/payment>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Plačilo <ecommerce/checkout/payment>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:131
msgid ":ref:`Order confirmation <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Potrditev naročila <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:135
msgid ""
"Each step can be customized using the website editor by "
"adding :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` or "
"opening the :guilabel:`Style` tab to enable various checkout options."
msgstr ""
"Vsak korak lahko prilagodite z urejevalnikom spletnega mesta z "
"dodajanjem :doc:`gradnikov <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` ali "
"odpiranjem zavihka :guilabel:`Slog`, da omogočite različne možnosti nakupa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:140
msgid "Content added through building blocks is **specific** to each step."
msgstr "Vsebina, dodana prek gradnikov, je **specifična** za vsak korak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:143
msgid ""
"Restrict access to the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"and :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` for "
"specific customers, e.g., in a :doc:`B2B <../ecommerce/configuration/"
"b2b_b2c>` business setup."
msgstr ""
"Omejite dostop do :ref:`trgovine <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"in :ref:`zaključka nakupa <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` za "
"določene stranke, npr. v :doc:`B2B <../ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c>` "
"poslovni nastavitvi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:150
msgid "Order summary"
msgstr "Pregled naročila"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:152
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Order summary` step allows customers to see the items they "
"added to their cart, adjust quantities, :guilabel:`Remove` products, "
"and :ref:`reorder products from a previous order <ecommerce/checkout/"
"reorder>`. Information on product prices and the taxes applied is also "
"displayed. Customers can then click the :guilabel:`Checkout` :icon:`fa-"
"chevron-right` button to continue to the :ref:`Address <ecommerce/checkout/"
"delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"Korak :guilabel:`Povzetek naročila` omogoča strankam, da vidijo elemente, ki "
"so jih dodale v svojo košarico, prilagodijo količine, :guilabel:`odstranijo` "
"izdelke in :ref:`ponovno naročijo izdelke iz prejšnjega naročila <ecommerce/"
"checkout/reorder>`. Prikazane so tudi informacije o cenah izdelkov in "
"uporabljenih davkih. Stranke lahko nato kliknejo "
"gumb :guilabel:`Blagajna` :icon:`fa-chevron-right`, da nadaljujejo na "
"korak :ref:`Naslov <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:158
msgid ""
"Open the website editor to :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` checkout options such as:"
msgstr ""
"Odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta, da :ref:`omogočite <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` možnosti zaključka nakupa, kot so:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:161
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggested Accessories`: to showcase :ref:`accessory products "
"<ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Predlagana dodatna oprema`: za prikaz :ref:`dodatnih izdelkov "
"<ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Promo Code`: to allow customers to redeem :ref:`gift cards "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` and apply :doc:`discount codes <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>` or :ref:`promotional codes <ecommerce/"
"prices/promotional-code>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Promocijska koda`: da strankam omogočite unovčenje :ref:`darilnih "
"kartic <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` in uporabo :doc:`kod za popust <../../"
"sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount>` ali :ref:`promocijskih kod "
"<ecommerce/prices/promotional-code>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:166
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add to Wishlist`: :ref:`Enable wishlists <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` to allow signed-in users to remove a product "
"from their cart and add it to their wishlist using the :guilabel:`Save for "
"Later` option."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj na seznam želja`: :ref:`Omogočite sezname želja <ecommerce/"
"products/additional_features/wishlists>`, da prijavljen uporabniki omogočite "
"odstranitev izdelka iz košarice in dodajanje na njihov seznam želja z "
"možnostjo :guilabel:`Shrani za pozneje`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:171
msgid ""
"If a :doc:`fiscal position <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` is detected automatically, the product tax is determined "
"based on the customer's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Če je :doc:`davčni položaj <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` zaznan samodejno, se davek na izdelek določi na podlagi "
"IP-naslova stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:173
msgid ""
"If the installed :doc:`payment provider <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"supports :ref:`express checkout <payment_providers/express_checkout>`, a "
"dedicated button is displayed, allowing customers to go straight from the "
"cart to the confirmation page without filling out the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Če nameščeni :doc:`ponudnik plačil <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"podpira :ref:`hitro zaključevanje <payment_providers/express_checkout>`, se "
"prikaže namenski gumb, ki strankam omogoča, da gredo naravnost iz košarice "
"na stran s potrditvijo, ne da bi izpolnile obrazec s kontaktnimi podatki."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:181
msgid "Address"
msgstr "Naslov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:183
msgid "Once they have reviewed their order:"
msgstr "Ko pregledajo svoje naročilo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:185
msgid ""
"Unsigned-in customers are prompted to :guilabel:`Sign in` or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Name` and :guilabel:`Email` address, along with their "
"delivery address and phone details;"
msgstr ""
"Neprijavljene stranke so pozvane, naj se :guilabel:`Prijavijo` ali vnesejo "
"svoje :guilabel:`Ime` in :guilabel:`E-poštni naslov` skupaj s svojim "
"dostavnim naslovom in telefonskimi podatki;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:187
msgid ""
"Signed-in customers can select the appropriate :guilabel:`Delivery address`."
msgstr ""
"Prijavljene stranke lahko izberejo ustrezen :guilabel:`Naslov za dostavo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:189
msgid ""
"They can then :doc:`choose a delivery method <shipping>`, select or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Billing Address` (or toggle the :guilabel:`Same as delivery "
"address` switch if the billing and delivery addresses are identical), and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm` to proceed to the next step."
msgstr ""
"Nato lahko :doc:`izberejo način dostave <shipping>`, izberejo ali vnesejo "
"svoj :guilabel:`Naslov za račun` (ali preklopijo stikalo :guilabel:`Enak kot "
"naslov za dostavo`, če sta naslova za račun in dostavo enaka) ter "
"kliknejo :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da nadaljujejo na naslednji korak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:194
msgid ""
"For B2B customers, you can also :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` optional :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` "
"in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Za B2B stranke lahko tudi :ref:`omogočite <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` izbirna :ref:`B2B polja <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` v "
"urejevalniku spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:196
msgid ""
"You can add a checkbox for users without an account to sign up for a "
"newsletter. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Newsletter` feature, and select a :guilabel:`Newsletter List`."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabnike brez računa lahko dodate potrditveno polje za prijavo na "
"novice. To storite tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknete navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`eCommerce`, omogočite funkcijo :guilabel:`Novice` in "
"izberete :guilabel:`Seznam za novice`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:200
msgid ""
"When the :ref:`Pick up in store <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>` "
"delivery method is selected, the customer can :guilabel:`Choose a pick-up "
"point`, provided several pick-up points are available."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana dostava :ref:`Prevzem v trgovini <ecommerce/shipping/instore-"
"pickup>`, lahko stranka :guilabel:`izbere prevzemno točko`, pod pogojem, da "
"je na voljo več prevzemnih točk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:207
msgid "Automatic address validation"
msgstr "Samodejno preverjanje naslova"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:209
msgid ""
"Use the :doc:`Google Places API </applications/general/integrations/"
"address_autocomplete>` to ensure that partner delivery addresses are valid. "
"Addresses are automatically validated as the user types during checkout."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :doc:`Google Places API </applications/general/integrations/"
"address_autocomplete>`, da zagotovite veljavnost naslovov za dostavo "
"partnerjev. Naslovi se samodejno preverijo, ko uporabnik tipka med plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:213
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, the :ref:`Google Places API <address_autocomplete/"
"places-api-configuration>` needs to be configured first. Then, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`General` section, enable :guilabel:`Google Address "
"Validation`, then paste the :ref:`Google Places API key "
"<address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>` in the :guilabel:`API Key` field."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, je treba najprej konfigurirati :ref:`Google "
"Places API <address_autocomplete/places-api-configuration>`. Nato pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Splošno` omogočite :guilabel:`Preverjanje naslova "
"Google`, nato prilepite :ref:`ključ API-ja Google Places "
"<address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>` v polje :guilabel:`Ključ API`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:222
msgid "Extra info"
msgstr "Dodatne informacije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:224
msgid ""
"You can add an :guilabel:`Extra Info` step in the checkout process to "
"collect additional customer information through an online form, which is "
"then included in the :ref:`sales order <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. To do "
"so, :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` the :guilabel:`Extra "
"Step` option in the website editor. The form can be :ref:`customized "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"V postopek zaključka nakupa lahko dodate korak :guilabel:`Dodatne "
"informacije`, s katerim zberete dodatne podatke o strankah prek spletnega "
"obrazca, ki je nato vključen v :ref:`prodajni nalog <ecommerce/handling/"
"sales>`. To storite tako, da v urejevalniku spletne strani :ref:`omogočite "
"<ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` možnost :guilabel:`Dodatni korak`. "
"Obrazec je mogoče :ref:`prilagoditi <website/building_blocks/form>` po "
"potrebi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:233
msgid "Payment"
msgstr "Plačilo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:235
msgid ""
"At the :guilabel:`Payment` step, customers can choose a :guilabel:`Payment "
"method`, enter their payment details, and click :guilabel:`Pay now`."
msgstr ""
"V koraku :guilabel:`Plačilo` lahko stranke izberejo :guilabel:`Način "
"plačila`, vnesejo svoje podatke o plačilu in kliknejo :guilabel:`Plačaj "
"zdaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:239
msgid ""
"When the :ref:`Cash on Delivery <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"cash_on_delivery>` payment option is enabled, the customer must click "
"the :guilabel:`Confirm` button and pay upon delivery."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočena možnost plačila :ref:`Plačilo po povzetju <payment_providers/"
"inperson_payments/cash_on_delivery>`, mora stranka klikniti "
"gumb :guilabel:`Potrdi` in plačati ob dostavi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:243
msgid ""
"To make payment methods available to customers, configure and enable one or "
"more :doc:`payment provider(s) </applications/finance/payment_providers>`. "
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment "
"Providers`, :guilabel:`Activate` the relevant payment provider, "
"and :ref:`configure <payment_providers/add_new>` it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite strankam omogočiti načine plačila, konfigurirajte in omogočite "
"enega ali več :doc:`ponudnikov plačil </applications/finance/"
"payment_providers>`. To storite tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Spletna "
"stran --> Konfiguracija --> Ponudniki plačil`, :guilabel:`Aktivirajte` "
"ustreznega ponudnika plačil in ga :ref:`konfigurirajte <payment_providers/"
"add_new>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:249
msgid ""
"The options displayed at checkout depend on the active payment providers, "
"the enabled :ref:`payment methods <payment_providers/payment_methods>`, "
"the :ref:`customer’s country and currency <payment_providers/"
"currencies_countries>`, and, optionally, the :ref:`maximum amount "
"<payment_providers/maximum_amount>` set for the provider."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti, prikazane ob nakupu, so odvisne od aktivnih ponudnikov plačil, "
"omogočenih :ref:`načinov plačila <payment_providers/"
"payment_methods>`, :ref:`države in valute stranke <payment_providers/"
"currencies_countries>` ter po možnosti :ref:`največjega zneska "
"<payment_providers/maximum_amount>`, določenega za ponudnika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:254
msgid ""
"To display an :ref:`availability <payment_providers/availability>` report "
"for payment providers and payment methods and help diagnose potential "
"availability issues on the payment form, enable the :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>`, and click the :icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`bug)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz poročila o :ref:`razpoložljivosti <payment_providers/"
"availability>` za ponudnike plačil in plačilne metode ter pomoč pri "
"diagnosticiranju morebitnih težav z razpoložljivostjo na obrazcu za plačilo "
"omogočite :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>` in kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`hrošč`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:41
msgid "Terms and conditions"
msgstr "Pravila in pogoji"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:261
msgid ""
"To require customers to agree to the :doc:`terms and conditions <../../"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` before payment, open "
"the website editor and toggle the :guilabel:`Accept Terms` switch in "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"Če želite od strank zahtevati, da se pred plačilom strinjajo s :doc:`pogoji "
"poslovanja <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>`, "
"odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta in preklopite stikalo :guilabel:`Sprejmi "
"pogoje` v zavihku :guilabel:`Slog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:266
msgid "eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "Elektronske denarnice in darilne kartice"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:268
msgid ""
"Customers can pay with an eWallet or gift card during checkout. To offer "
"these options, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"and enable :menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` in "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section. Then, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Gift cards & eWallet` and :doc:`create a gift card and/or "
"eWallet program </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"ewallets_giftcards>`."
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko med nakupom plačajo z e-denarnico ali darilno kartico. Če "
"želite ponuditi ti možnosti, pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in omogočite :menuselection:`Popusti, zvestoba "
"in darilne kartice` v razdelku :guilabel:`eCommerce`. Nato pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> eCommerce --> Darilne kartice in e-"
"denarnica` ter :doc:`ustvarite program darilnih kartic in/ali e-denarnice </"
"applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:None
msgid "Gift card and eWallet options at checkout"
msgstr "Možnosti darilne kartice in e-denarnice ob nakupu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:280
msgid "Order confirmation"
msgstr "Potrditev naročila"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:282
msgid ""
"The final step of the checkout process is the order confirmation page, which "
"provides a summary of the customer's purchase details. A sales order is "
"automatically created in the backend. Enable the :ref:`Automatic Invoice "
"<ecommerce/handling/invoices>` setting to automatically send an invoice to "
"the customer."
msgstr ""
"Zadnji korak procesa blagajne je stran potrditve naročila, ki ponuja "
"povzetek podrobnosti nakupa stranke. Prodajni nalog je samodejno ustvarjen v "
"zalednem sistemu. Omogočite nastavitev :ref:`Samodejni račun <ecommerce/"
"handling/invoices>`, da stranki samodejno pošljete račun."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:288
msgid ":doc:`Order handling <order_handling>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Obdelava naročil <order_handling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:9
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce enables the configuration of products, categories, variants, "
"and pricing. It also manages customer accounts and access, supporting both "
"B2B and B2C business models."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce omogoča konfiguracijo izdelkov, kategorij, variant in cen. "
"Upravlja tudi račune strank in dostop ter podpira poslovne modele B2B in B2C."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:3
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Izdelki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:14
msgid ""
"Configure products, manage their visibility, add images and videos, create "
"product combos, and attach digital files. Define selling strategies, "
"translate product information, and manage stock and packaging."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte izdelke, upravljajte njihovo vidnost, dodajte slike in "
"videoposnetke, ustvarite kombinirane izdelke in priložite digitalne "
"datoteke. Določite prodajne strategije, prevedite informacije o izdelkih ter "
"upravljajte zaloge in embalažo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:22
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:3
msgid "Categories and variants"
msgstr "Kategorije in različice"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:22
msgid ""
"Use product variants and attributes to offer multiple product options. "
"Create attribute and e-commerce categories to better organize the shop and "
"product pages."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite variante in atribute izdelkov za ponudbo več možnosti izdelkov. "
"Ustvarite atribute in kategorije e-trgovine za boljšo organizacijo trgovine "
"in strani izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:13
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:3
msgid "Prices"
msgstr "Cene"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:29
msgid ""
"Configure different prices and taxes using prices per unit, pricelists, and "
"discounts. Prices can also be hidden, and sales can be restricted when "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte različne cene in davke z uporabo cen na enoto, cenikov in "
"popustov. Cene je mogoče tudi skriti, prodaja pa je po potrebi omejena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:36
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:67
msgid "Customer accounts"
msgstr "Računi strank"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:36
msgid ""
"Control access to the shop, the checkout, and the customer portal, and use "
"customer accounts to support B2B and B2C operations."
msgstr ""
"Nadzirajte dostop do trgovine, zaključka nakupa in portala za stranke ter "
"uporabite račune strank za podporo operacijam B2B in B2C."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:3
msgid "B2B and B2C"
msgstr "B2B in B2C"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:42
msgid ""
"Configure separate websites and shops for B2B and B2C businesses and "
"customize them to meet the specific needs of each business model."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte ločene spletne strani in trgovine za podjetja B2B in B2C ter "
"jih prilagodite specifičnim potrebam vsakega poslovnega modela."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce is designed to fulfill the needs of both B2B and B2C "
"companies. It allows you to configure :doc:`prices <prices>`, "
"manage :doc:`access <customer_accounts>` for specific customers, "
"and :ref:`customize the website <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` to "
"support B2B, B2C, or both business models."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce je zasnovan za izpolnjevanje potreb podjetij B2B in B2C. "
"Omogoča vam, da konfigurirate :doc:`cene <prices>`, upravljate :doc:`dostop "
"<customer_accounts>` za določene stranke in :ref:`prilagodite spletno stran "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` za podporo poslovnim modelom B2B, B2C "
"ali obema."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:15
msgid ""
"While B2C businesses sell directly to the end consumer with a :ref:`tax-"
"included <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` price, B2B businesses "
"usually :ref:`exclude taxes <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` and "
"may even prefer to hide prices altogether, showcasing only their products "
"instead. To configure a B2B-specific online shop, make sure the :ref:`Tax-"
"Excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>` option is enabled, and complete the "
"configuration to :ref:`hide the pricing <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>`."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko podjetja B2C prodajajo neposredno končnemu potrošniku s "
"ceno :ref:`z vključenimi davki <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`, "
"podjetja B2B običajno :ref:`izključijo davke <ecommerce-price-management-tax-"
"display>` in morda celo raje skrijejo cene ter prikazujejo samo svoje "
"izdelke. Za konfiguracijo spletne trgovine, specializirane za B2B, se "
"prepričajte, da je omogočena možnost :ref:`Brez davkov <ecommerce/prices/"
"taxes>`, in dokončajte konfiguracijo za :ref:`skrivanje cen <ecommerce/"
"prices/hide-prices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:24
msgid ""
"To make sure that only customers with an :ref:`account and granted access "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` can see the prices, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon from the search bar, and select "
"the :guilabel:`Archived` filter. Then click the :guilabel:`Public user` "
"card, go to the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and add the zero-priced "
"pricelist configured to :ref:`cover all countries <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`. Keep the :guilabel:`Public User` contact :guilabel:`Archived` at "
"all times. Website visitors now see the products without prices, while only "
"customers with an :ref:`account invitation <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"account-creation>` and an assigned :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` can view the pricing in the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Da zagotovite, da lahko cene vidijo samo stranke z :ref:`računom in "
"dodeljenim dostopom <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, pojdite "
"v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> Stranke`, kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(spustni meni)` v iskalni vrstici in "
"izberite filter :guilabel:`Arhivirano`. Nato kliknite "
"kartico :guilabel:`Javni uporabnik`, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja "
"in nabava` ter dodajte cenik z ničelno ceno, nastavljen tako, "
"da :ref:`pokriva vse države <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`. "
"Stik :guilabel:`Javni uporabnik` naj bo vedno :guilabel:`Arhiviran`. "
"Obiskovalci spletnega mesta zdaj vidijo izdelke brez cen, medtem ko lahko "
"samo stranke z :ref:`povabilom za račun <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-"
"creation>` in dodeljenim :ref:`cenikom <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` vidijo "
"cene v portalu za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:36
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/B2B_B2C`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/B2B_B2C`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:37
msgid ":ref:`Discounts <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Popusti <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:42
msgid "Access request"
msgstr "Zahteva za dostop"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:44
msgid ""
"When running a B2B business, you usually :ref:`hide the pricing <ecommerce/"
"b2b_b2c/prices>` on the web shop and make it available for :ref:`logged-in "
"users <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` only. To prevent anyone "
"from signing up freely, set the :ref:`Customer Account <ecommerce/"
"customer_accounts/account-creation>` setting option to :guilabel:`On "
"invitation`. To create a page where customers request access, open "
"the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`, :ref:`create a form <website/building_blocks/form>`, customize "
"it, and in the :guilabel:`Action` field, select :guilabel:`Create a "
"customer`."
msgstr ""
"Pri vodenju poslovanja B2B običajno :ref:`skrijete cene <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"prices>` v spletni trgovini in jih naredite dostopne samo "
"za :ref:`prijavljene uporabnike <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`. "
"Da preprečite prosto registracijo, nastavite možnost :ref:`Račun stranke "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` na :guilabel:`Na povabilo`. "
"Za ustvarjanje strani, kjer stranke zahtevajo dostop, "
"odprite :doc:`urejevalnik spletne strani </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`, :ref:`ustvarite obrazec <website/building_blocks/form>`, ga "
"prilagodite in v polju :guilabel:`Dejanje` izberite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"stranko`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:53
msgid ""
"You can assign tags created on a contact form under :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Configuration --> Customers` to identify what kind of customers have "
"submitted the form. To do so, select a field in the form while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode, click the :guilabel:`+ Field` button under "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and set the field's :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Tags`. Toggle the tags that should be automatically assigned "
"when a customer fills in the form and set the field's :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"to :guilabel:`Hidden`."
msgstr ""
"Oznake, ustvarjene na kontaktnem obrazcu pod :menuselection:`Spletna stran --"
"> Konfiguracija --> Stranke`, lahko dodelite za prepoznavanje vrste strank, "
"ki so oddale obrazec. To storite tako, da v načinu :guilabel:`Uredi` "
"izberete polje v obrazcu, kliknete gumb :guilabel:`+ Polje` pod "
"zavihkom :guilabel:`Slog` in nastavite :guilabel:`Vrsto` polja "
"na :guilabel:`Oznake`. Vklopite oznake, ki naj se samodejno dodelijo, ko "
"stranka izpolni obrazec, in nastavite :guilabel:`Vidnost` polja "
"na :guilabel:`Skrito`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:60
msgid ""
"When a customer submits the form, a new contact is automatically created in "
"the database. The contact is assigned the first pricelist from the list of "
"available pricelists, and, if applicable, the specified tags."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranka odda obrazec, se v bazi podatkov samodejno ustvari nov stik. "
"Stiku je dodeljen prvi cenik s seznama razpoložljivih cenikov in po potrebi "
"navedene oznake."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:64
msgid ""
"Submitted requests can be found under the :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Customers`. Select the customer you want to :ref:`grant portal "
"access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/grant-access>` to. Once done, the "
"selected customer is able to view the B2B prices and products. Make sure the "
"correct pricelist is assigned to their contact form."
msgstr ""
"Poslane zahteve najdete v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> "
"Stranke`. Izberite stranko, ki ji želite :ref:`dodeliti dostop do portala "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/grant-access>`. Ko je to opravljeno, lahko "
"izbrana stranka vidi B2B cene in izdelke. Prepričajte se, da je v obrazcu "
"stika dodeljen pravilen cenik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:71
msgid ""
"It is also possible to hide the entire shop from the public using "
"the :ref:`Ecommerce Access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"setting and only make it available for logged-in customers."
msgstr ""
"Celotno trgovino je mogoče tudi skriti pred javnostjo z "
"nastavitvijo :ref:`Dostop do e-trgovine <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>` in jo omogočiti samo prijavljenim strankam."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:74
msgid ""
"Configure the :ref:`checkout policy <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>` to allow/disallow guest checkout for B2C businesses."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte :ref:`pravilnik blagajne <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"checkout-access>`, da dovolite/prepoveste nakup kot gost za B2C podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:76
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`Shared Customer Accounts <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"multiple-websites>` feature to allow customers to use the same account "
"on :ref:`all <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` your websites."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite funkcijo :ref:`Skupni računi strank <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"multiple-websites>`, da strankam omogočite uporabo istega računa "
"na :ref:`vseh <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` vaših spletnih mestih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:334
msgid ":doc:`customer_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`customer_accounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:3
msgid "Multiple websites"
msgstr "Več spletnih mest"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:88
msgid ""
"Settings are website-specific, which means it is possible to configure "
"different behaviors for each website. For example, you can set up a B2C "
"website that allows :ref:`guest checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"checkout-access>` and displays :ref:`tax-included prices <ecommerce-price-"
"management-tax-display>`, and a B2B website that requires :ref:`sign-in "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` and shows :ref:`tax-excluded "
"prices <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`. However, "
"each :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` can only be assigned to "
"one website at a time. If you want to use the same pricelist on several "
"websites, duplicate the pricelist and assign each copy to its corresponding "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve so specifične za spletno mesto, kar pomeni, da je mogoče "
"konfigurirati različna vedenja za vsako spletno mesto. Na primer, lahko "
"nastavite B2C spletno mesto, ki omogoča :ref:`nakup kot gost <ecommerce/"
"customer_accounts/checkout-access>` in prikazuje :ref:`cene z davkom "
"<ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`, ter B2B spletno mesto, ki "
"zahteva :ref:`prijavo <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` in "
"prikazuje :ref:`cene brez davka <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`. "
"Vendar pa je lahko vsak :ref:`cenik <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` dodeljen "
"samo enemu spletnemu mestu naenkrat. Če želite uporabiti isti cenik na več "
"spletnih mestih, podvojite cenik in dodelite vsako kopijo ustreznemu "
"spletnemu mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are running a B2B and B2C business, we *strongly* recommend to create "
"two :doc:`separate websites </applications/websites/website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` and assign a :ref:`zero-priced pricelist <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"prices>` to the B2B website and a regular pricelist to the B2C website. In "
"case, you prefer using a single website, configure it using :ref:`country "
"groups <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` and assigning :ref:`pricelists "
"<ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` to customers, and deactivate "
"the :ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>` option."
msgstr ""
"Če vodite poslovanje B2B in B2C, *močno* priporočamo, da ustvarite "
"dve :doc:`ločeni spletni strani </applications/websites/website/"
"configuration/multi_website>` in dodelite :ref:`cenik z ničelno ceno "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` spletni strani B2B ter običajen cenik spletni "
"strani B2C. Če raje uporabljate eno spletno stran, jo konfigurirajte z "
"uporabo :ref:`skupin držav <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` in "
"dodeljevanjem :ref:`cenikov <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` strankam ter "
"deaktivirajte možnost :ref:`Izbirno <ecommerce/prices/selectable-"
"pricelists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:3
msgid "Additional features"
msgstr "Dodatne funkcije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:116
msgid "Invoice"
msgstr "Račun"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:118
msgid ""
"Depending on the type of business (B2B or B2C), you might want to issue an "
"invoice. An invoice can either be generated automatically (for B2B) or on "
"demand of the customer (for B2C). This process can be automated if (and "
"when) the online payment is :ref:`confirmed <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. To "
"automate invoicing, enable the :ref:`Automatic Invoice <ecommerce/handling/"
"invoices>` setting. If this feature has not been enabled, the customer only "
"receives an order confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Glede na vrsto poslovanja (B2B ali B2C) boste morda želeli izdati račun. "
"Račun se lahko ustvari samodejno (za B2B) ali na zahtevo stranke (za B2C). "
"Ta postopek se lahko avtomatizira, če (in ko) je spletno "
"plačilo :ref:`potrjeno <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. Za avtomatizacijo "
"izdajanja računov omogočite nastavitev :ref:`Samodejni račun <ecommerce/"
"handling/invoices>`. Če ta funkcija ni omogočena, stranka prejme le "
"potrditev naročila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:127
msgid "B2B fields at checkout"
msgstr "B2B polja pri blagajni"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:129
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Order summary` page, open the :doc:`website editor </"
"applications/websites/website/web_design>`, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, "
"and toggle the :guilabel:`Show B2B Fields` switch to display B2B-specific "
"additional fields like :guilabel:`VAT` or :guilabel:`Company Name` during "
"the :ref:`delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Povzetek naročila` odprite :doc:`urejevalnik spletne "
"strani </applications/websites/website/web_design>`, pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in preklopite stikalo :guilabel:`Prikaži polja "
"B2B`, da prikažete dodatna polja, specifična za B2B, kot sta :guilabel:`DDV` "
"ali :guilabel:`Ime podjetja` med korakom :ref:`dostave <ecommerce/checkout/"
"delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce provides multiple ways to configure, :doc:`present <../../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>`, and sell different product options to "
"customers while organizing products by category for a better overview and "
"smoother navigation."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce ponuja več načinov za konfiguracijo, :doc:`predstavitev "
"<../../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>` in prodajo različnih možnosti "
"izdelkov strankam ter organizacijo izdelkov po kategorijah za boljši pregled "
"in lažjo navigacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:12
msgid "Product variants"
msgstr "Različice izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:14
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` are different versions of the same product, created by "
"combining :ref:`attributes <products/variants/attributes>` like color, size, "
"material, etc., which can lead to differences in price and/or availability."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Različice izdelka </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` so različne verzije istega izdelka, ustvarjene s "
"kombiniranjem :ref:`atributov <products/variants/attributes>`, kot so barva, "
"velikost, material itd., kar lahko privede do razlik v ceni in/ali "
"razpoložljivosti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:18
msgid "To configure product variants for a product:"
msgstr "Za konfiguracijo različic izdelka za izdelek:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:20
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:185
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:92
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:16
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:21
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Product Variants` feature."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in omogočite "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Različice izdelka`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:23
msgid ""
"Access the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab."
msgstr ""
"Odprite :ref:`obrazec izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-form>` in pojdite "
"na zavihek :guilabel:`Atributi in različice`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the relevant attribute and its "
"values. Repeat this step for each additional attribute."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in izberite ustrezen atribut ter njegove "
"vrednosti. Ponovite ta korak za vsak dodaten atribut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:28
msgid ""
"The product variants are created automatically (or not) based on "
"the :ref:`attribute's configuration <products/variants/attributes>`."
msgstr ""
"Različice izdelka se ustvarijo samodejno (ali ne) na "
"podlagi :ref:`konfiguracije atributa <products/variants/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:32
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:100
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "Lastnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:39
msgid ""
"Attributes refer to the characteristics of a product, such as its color or "
"material. Each attribute includes a set of values."
msgstr ""
"Atributi se nanašajo na značilnosti izdelka, kot so njegova barva ali "
"material. Vsak atribut vključuje nabor vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:None
msgid "Attributes and variants of your product"
msgstr "Atributi in različice vašega izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:45
msgid ""
"Once your attributes are :ref:`created <products/variants/attributes>`, set "
"the following options on the attribute form to control where and/or how they "
"appear on the website:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so vaši atributi :ref:`ustvarjeni <products/variants/attributes>`, "
"nastavite naslednje možnosti v obrazcu atributa, da nadzirate, kje in/ali "
"kako se prikazujejo na spletni strani:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`eCommerce Filter`: Set the field to :guilabel:`Visible` to make "
"the attribute available in the shop's filter section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`eCommerce Filter`: Nastavite polje na :guilabel:`Visible`, da bo "
"atribut na voljo v razdelku filtrov trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Product Cards`: Set the field to :guilabel:`Visible` "
"or :guilabel:`Hover` to display attributes on the product card on the shop "
"page. These options are only available when :ref:`variants are created "
"instantly for the attribute <products/variants/attributes>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`On Product Cards`: Nastavite polje na :guilabel:`Visible` "
"ali :guilabel:`Hover`, da se atributi prikažejo na kartici izdelka na strani "
"trgovine. Ti možnosti sta na voljo samo, ko so :ref:`variante za atribut "
"ustvarjene takoj <products/variants/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:54
msgid ""
"When the field is set to :guilabel:`Visible`, the :guilabel:`Show "
"Thumbnails` option can be toggled to show a product variant image instead of "
"the attribute values."
msgstr ""
"Ko je polje nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Visible`, je mogoče preklopiti "
"možnost :guilabel:`Show Thumbnails`, da se namesto vrednosti atributov "
"prikaže slika variante izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:57
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add a variant picture on the product card on the shop "
"page. To do so, go to the product form, click the :icon:`fa-"
"sitemap` :guilabel:`Variants` :ref:`smart button <products/variants/variants-"
"smart-button>`, select a variant, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)` icon to add a picture for each variant. Make sure "
"that the :ref:`Show Thumbnails <ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>` "
"option is enabled on the attribute form."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako je mogoče dodati sliko variante na kartico izdelka na strani "
"trgovine. To storite tako, da greste v obrazec izdelka, kliknete :icon:`fa-"
"sitemap` :guilabel:`Variants` :ref:`pametno gumb <products/variants/variants-"
"smart-button>`, izberete varianto in kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`, da dodate sliko za vsako varianto. Prepričajte "
"se, da je možnost :ref:`Show Thumbnails <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>` omogočena v obrazcu atributa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:None
msgid "Variant thumbnails on product card."
msgstr "Sličice variant na kartici izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:69
msgid "Attribute categories"
msgstr "Kategorije atributov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:71
msgid ""
"To group similar attributes under the same section when :ref:`comparing "
"products <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-comparison>`, "
"select the relevant :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` or create a new one. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internal link)` icon next to "
"the category name to:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite podobne atribute združiti v isti razdelek pri :ref:`primerjavi "
"izdelkov <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-comparison>`, "
"izberite ustrezno :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` ali ustvarite novo. "
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internal link)` poleg "
"imena kategorije, da:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:76
msgid "Rename the category."
msgstr "Preimenujete kategorijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:77
msgid "Change its :guilabel:`Sequence`."
msgstr "Spremenite njeno :guilabel:`Sequence`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:78
msgid ""
"Reorder the :guilabel:`Related Attributes` to define the order in which they "
"are displayed in the comparison summary."
msgstr ""
"Prerazporedite :guilabel:`Related Attributes`, da določite vrstni red, v "
"katerem so prikazani v povzetku primerjave."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:80
msgid "Add attributes to the category by clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr "Dodajte atribute v kategorijo s klikom na :guilabel:`Add a line`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:None
msgid "Comparison summary page with attribute categories."
msgstr "Stran s povzetkom primerjave s kategorijami atributov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:88
msgid "E-commerce categories"
msgstr "E-trgovske kategorije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:90
msgid ""
"E-commerce categories are used to organize products into groups, making it "
"easier for customers to browse the online store."
msgstr ""
"E-trgovske kategorije se uporabljajo za organizacijo izdelkov v skupine, kar "
"strankam olajša brskanje po spletni trgovini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Category quick access in the toolbar."
msgstr "Hiter dostop do kategorije v orodni vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:96
msgid ""
"To create e-commerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce "
"--> eCommerce Categories`, and click :guilabel:`New`. On the category form, "
"add a :guilabel:`Name`, optionally enter a :guilabel:`Parent` category, "
"restrict it to a specific :guilabel:`Website`, and write "
"a :guilabel:`Description`, if needed. You can also add a :guilabel:`Cover "
"Image` for the category."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje e-trgovskih kategorij pojdite na :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> eCommerce Categories` in kliknite :guilabel:`New`. V obrazcu "
"kategorije dodajte :guilabel:`Name`, po želji vnesite nadrejeno kategorijo "
"v :guilabel:`Parent`, omejite jo na določeno :guilabel:`Website` in po "
"potrebi napišite :guilabel:`Description`. Lahko tudi dodate :guilabel:`Cover "
"Image` za kategorijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:102
msgid ""
"To use :guilabel:`eCommerce categories`, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select the product you wish to modify, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` "
"section, and select the :guilabel:`Categories` it belongs to."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo :guilabel:`eCommerce categories` pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, izberite izdelek, ki "
"ga želite spremeniti, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Sales`, pomaknite se do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` in izberite :guilabel:`Categories`, v "
"katere spada."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:107
msgid "A single product can belong to multiple e-commerce categories."
msgstr "En sam izdelek lahko spada v več e-trgovskih kategorij."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:108
msgid ""
"Define how to :ref:`display categories <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` on "
"the shop page."
msgstr ""
"Določite, kako :ref:`prikazati kategorije <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` na "
"strani trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:109
msgid ""
"Categories that do not contain any products are not visible on the shop page."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije, ki ne vsebujejo nobenih izdelkov, niso vidne na strani trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:112
msgid ":doc:`products`"
msgstr ":doc:`products`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Using customer accounts for an e-commerce enables you to :ref:`manage "
"customers <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, control access to "
"the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
"the :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, or "
"the :doc:`customer portal </applications/general/users/user_portals/"
"portal_access>`, and support both :doc:`B2B and B2C operations <b2b_b2c>`."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba računov strank za e-trgovino vam omogoča, da :ref:`upravljate "
"stranke <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, nadzorujete dostop "
"do :ref:`trgovine <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>`, :ref:`zaključka nakupa <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>` ali :doc:`portala za stranke </applications/general/users/"
"user_portals/portal_access>` ter podpirate :doc:`operacije B2B in B2C "
"<b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:12
msgid ""
"After logging in, customers can access their :doc:`customer portal </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>` by clicking their username in the "
"top-right corner of the screen and selecting :guilabel:`My Account`. From "
"there, they can view all their documents in one place, such as quotations, "
"orders, invoices, and more."
msgstr ""
"Po prijavi lahko stranke dostopajo do svojega :doc:`portala za stranke </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>` tako, da kliknejo svoje "
"uporabniško ime v zgornjem desnem kotu zaslona in izberejo :guilabel:`Moj "
"račun`. Od tam si lahko ogledajo vse svoje dokumente na enem mestu, kot so "
"ponudbe, naročila, računi in več."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Customer account access"
msgstr "Dostop do računa stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:21
msgid ""
"The customer account page can be customized with building blocks and other "
"features through the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Stran z računom stranke je mogoče prilagoditi z gradbenimi bloki in drugimi "
"funkcijami prek :doc:`urejevalnika spletne strani </applications/websites/"
"website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:27
msgid "Customer account creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje računa stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:29
msgid ""
"You can choose whether customer accounts and document access are available "
"to everyone or restricted to invited users only. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`General` section. Under :guilabel:`Customer Account`, select "
"one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, ali so računi strank in dostop do dokumentov na voljo vsem "
"ali omejeni samo na povabljene uporabnike. Pojdite v :menuselection:`Spletno "
"mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in se pomaknite do "
"oddelka :guilabel:`Splošno`. Pod :guilabel:`Račun stranke` izberite eno od "
"naslednjih možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On invitation`: Customers can only create an account if the "
"website owner sends them an invitation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Na povabilo`: Stranke lahko ustvarijo račun samo, če jim lastnik "
"spletnega mesta pošlje povabilo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Free sign up`: Every website visitor can create an account and "
"sign in. They will get access to the :doc:`portal </applications/general/"
"users/user_portals>` by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prosta registracija`: Vsak obiskovalec spletne strani lahko "
"ustvari račun in se prijavi. Privzeto bodo dobili dostop do :doc:`portala </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:41
msgid "To send an email invitation to a customer:"
msgstr "Če želite stranki poslati e-poštno povabilo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:43
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`."
msgstr "Pojdite v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> Stranke`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:44
msgid ""
"Select a customer or click :guilabel:`New` to create one, ensuring "
"an :guilabel:`Email` address is set."
msgstr ""
"Izberite stranko ali kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite novo, pri čemer "
"se prepričajte, da je nastavljen :guilabel:`E-poštni naslov`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:46
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon next to the record's "
"name at the top-left and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` poleg imena zapisa v "
"zgornjem levem kotu in izberite :guilabel:`Dodeli dostop do portala`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:48
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up, click :guilabel:`Grant "
"Access` to send the invitation."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Upravljanje dostopa do portala` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Dodeli dostop`, da pošljete povabilo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:52
msgid ""
"To invite multiple customers at once, switch to the customers :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`List` view, select several customers, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button, and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite povabiti več strank hkrati, preklopite na pogled :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`Seznam` strank, izberite več strank, kliknite "
"gumb :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Dodeli dostop "
"do portala`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:56
msgid ""
"Once done, the customer(s) receive an email confirming their account "
"creation, including instructions on setting a password and activating their "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Ko je postopek končan, stranka(-e) prejmejo e-poštno sporočilo s potrditvijo "
"ustvarjanja računa, vključno z navodili za nastavitev gesla in aktivacijo "
"računa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:60
msgid ""
"When selecting the :guilabel:`Free sign up`, a clickable :guilabel:`Don't "
"have an account?` link appears under the login form on the website."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete :guilabel:`Brezplačna registracija`, se pod prijavnim obrazcem "
"na spletnem mestu prikaže povezava :guilabel:`Nimate računa?`, na katero je "
"mogoče klikniti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:62
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`On invitation` option is especially useful for :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` businesses that prefer to keep :ref:`prices "
"hidden <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` on the website and grant access only "
"to invited customers."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Na povabilo` je še posebej uporabna za :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` podjetja, ki želijo :ref:`skriti cene <ecommerce/"
"prices/hide-prices>` na spletnem mestu in dodeliti dostop samo povabljenim "
"strankam."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:67
msgid ""
"It is possible to configure a website form with a :guilabel:`Create a "
"Customer` :ref:`action <website/building_blocks/action>` to automatically "
"create a customer record in the backend when filled in."
msgstr ""
"Možno je nastaviti spletni obrazec z :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"stranko` :ref:`dejanjem <website/building_blocks/action>`, da se ob "
"izpolnitvi samodejno ustvari zapis stranke v zalednem sistemu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:74
msgid "Access restriction"
msgstr "Omejitev dostopa"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:76
msgid ""
"Once a customer account is created, it is still possible to adjust the "
"access rights either globally or for individual users:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je strankina račun ustvarjen, je še vedno mogoče prilagoditi pravice "
"dostopa bodisi globalno bodisi za posamezne uporabnike:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:79
msgid ""
":doc:`Revoke access or re-invite a customer </applications/general/users/"
"user_portals/portal_access>` using the related buttons in "
"the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Prekličite dostop ali ponovno povabite stranko </applications/general/"
"users/user_portals/portal_access>` z uporabo povezanih gumbov v pojavnem "
"oknu :guilabel:`Upravljanje dostopa do portala`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:82
msgid ""
"Restrict :ref:`access to the shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`;"
msgstr ""
"Omejitev :ref:`dostopa do trgovine <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"Decide whether customers need to create an account to :ref:`complete the "
"checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."
msgstr ""
"Odločite, ali morajo stranke ustvariti račun, da :ref:`dokončajo nakup "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:87
msgid ""
"It is also possible to define the types of documents customers have access "
"to. To do so, click your username in the upper-right corner of the website, "
"select :guilabel:`My Account` and open the :doc:`website builder </"
"applications/websites/website/web_design>`. On the :guilabel:`Style` tab, "
"enable or disable access to specific documents as needed."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je tudi določiti vrste dokumentov, do katerih imajo stranke dostop. "
"To storite tako, da kliknete svoje uporabniško ime v zgornjem desnem kotu "
"spletne strani, izberete :guilabel:`Moj račun` in odprete :doc:`graditelj "
"spletne strani </applications/websites/website/web_design>`. Na "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Slog` po potrebi omogočite ali onemogočite dostop do "
"določenih dokumentov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:95
msgid "Shop access"
msgstr "Dostop do trgovine"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:97
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the entire online shop for users who are not logged-"
"in, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section and under :guilabel:`Ecommerce Access`, "
"select :guilabel:`Logged in users`. Select :guilabel:`All users` if the shop "
"should be visible to every website visitor."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omejiti dostop do celotne spletne trgovine za uporabnike, ki niso "
"prijavljeni, pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`, pomaknite se do odseka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in "
"pod :guilabel:`Dostop do e-trgovine` izberite :guilabel:`Prijavljeni "
"uporabniki`. Izberite :guilabel:`Vsi uporabniki`, če naj bo trgovina vidna "
"vsem obiskovalcem spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:103
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the shop's pricing, use :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/"
"prices/pricelists>` with :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`."
msgstr ""
"Za omejitev dostopa do cen trgovine uporabite :ref:`cenike <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` s :ref:`skupinami držav <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:109
msgid "Checkout access"
msgstr "Dostop do blagajne"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:111
msgid ""
"To allow customers to checkout as guests or force them to sign in/create an "
"account, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, and configure "
"the :guilabel:`Sign in/up at checkout` setting. The following options are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite strankam omogočiti nakup kot gostje ali jih prisiliti k prijavi/"
"ustvarjanju računa, pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in konfigurirajte "
"nastavitev :guilabel:`Prijava/registracija ob nakupu`. Na voljo so naslednje "
"možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:116
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Optional`: Customers can check out as guests and register later "
"via the order confirmation email to track their order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izbirno`: Kupci lahko zaključijo nakup kot gostje in se "
"registrirajo pozneje prek e-poštnega sporočila s potrditvijo naročila, da "
"spremljajo svoje naročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Disabled`: Customers can checkout as guests without creating an "
"account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Onemogočeno`: stranke lahko dokončajo nakup kot gostje, brez "
"ustvarjanja računa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory`: Customers must sign in or create an account at "
"the :ref:`Order summary <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` step to complete "
"their purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obvezno`: Stranke se morajo prijaviti ali ustvariti račun "
"v :ref:`koraku Pregled naročila <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`, da "
"dokončajo nakup."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:123
msgid ""
"Settings are specific to each website, allowing you to configure a B2C "
"website with guest checkout and a B2B website that requires customers to "
"sign in."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve so specifične za vsako spletno mesto, kar vam omogoča nastavitev "
"B2C spletnega mesta z gostujočo blagajno in B2B spletnega mesta, ki zahteva "
"prijavo strank."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:125
msgid ""
"To use the :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"wishlists>` feature, customers must create an account to save their favorite "
"items for later."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo funkcije :ref:`seznama želja <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` morajo stranke ustvariti račun, da lahko "
"shranijo svoje priljubljene izdelke za pozneje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:131
msgid "Multi-website account"
msgstr "Večspletni račun"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:133
msgid ""
"When managing multiple websites, it is possible to make customer accounts "
"available across *all* websites, allowing each customer to use a single "
"account. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, in the :guilabel:`General` section, enable the :guilabel:`Shared "
"Customer Accounts` option."
msgstr ""
"Pri upravljanju več spletnih mest je mogoče račune strank narediti dostopne "
"na *vseh* spletnih mestih, kar omogoča, da vsaka stranka uporablja en sam "
"račun. To storite tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, v odseku :guilabel:`Splošno` omogočite "
"možnost :guilabel:`Skupni računi strank`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:139
msgid ""
"When operating both :ref:`B2B and B2C online shops <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>`, it is recommended to use separate websites for each "
"business model."
msgstr ""
"Pri upravljanju :ref:`B2B in B2C spletnih trgovin <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>` se priporoča uporaba ločenih spletnih mest za vsak "
"poslovni model."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo offers multiple options to configure prices on the e-commerce. For "
"example, you can apply :ref:`prices per unit <ecommerce/prices/price-per-"
"unit>`, offer :ref:`discounts <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`, and set "
"up :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ponuja več možnosti za konfiguriranje cen na spletni trgovini. Na "
"primer, lahko uporabite :ref:`cene na enoto <ecommerce/prices/price-per-"
"unit>`, ponudite :ref:`popuste <ecommerce/prices/discounts>` in "
"nastavite :ref:`cenike <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:12
msgid "Taxes"
msgstr "Davki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:14
msgid ""
"To add a tax on a product, you can either set a tax in the :guilabel:`Sales "
"Taxes` field of the product form or use :doc:`fiscal positions </"
"applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izdelku dodati davek, lahko nastavite davek v "
"polju :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` obrazca izdelka ali uporabite :doc:`davčne "
"režime </applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:19
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:20
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:24
msgid ""
"Choosing the displayed price tax usually depends on a country's regulations "
"or the type of customers (:doc:`B2B vs. B2C <b2b_b2c>`). To select the type "
"of price displayed, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, select the website, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` "
"section, and under :guilabel:`Display Product Prices` select between:"
msgstr ""
"Izbira prikazane davčne cene običajno je odvisna od predpisov države ali "
"vrste strank (:doc:`B2B v primerjavi z B2C <b2b_b2c>`). Za izbiro vrste "
"prikazane cene pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --"
"> Nastavitve`, izberite spletno stran, se pomaknite do "
"odseka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in pod :guilabel:`Prikaži cene izdelkov` "
"izberite med:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Excluded`: the price displayed on the website is tax-"
"excluded, and the tax is computed at the :ref:`order summary <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>` step;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tax Excluded`: cena, prikazana na spletnem mestu, je brez davka, "
"davek pa se izračuna v koraku :ref:`povzetka naročila <ecommerce/checkout/"
"review_order>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Included`: the price displayed on the website is tax-included."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tax Included`: cena, prikazana na spletnem mestu, vključuje davek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:34
msgid ""
"This setting is website-specific and can therefore be configured "
"independently for every website in the database."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev je specifična za spletno mesto in jo zato lahko nastavite "
"neodvisno za vsako spletno mesto v bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:38
msgid ""
"Switch the :ref:`Tax indication <ecommerce_design/product_page/"
"customization>` toggle on in the website editor to explicitly indicate if "
"the price is `Tax excluded` or `Tax included` on the :doc:`product page "
"<../../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page>`."
msgstr ""
"V urejevalniku spletne strani vklopite stikalo :ref:`Navedba davka "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/customization>`, da izrecno navedete, ali je "
"cena \"brez davka\" ali \"z davkom\" na :doc:`strani izdelka <../../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:41
msgid ""
"Enable specific :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` in "
"the :ref:`delivery step <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` during the checkout "
"using the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite posebna :ref:`polja B2B <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` "
"v :ref:`koraku dostave <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` med plačilom z "
"uporabo :doc:`urejevalnika spletnega mesta </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:48
msgid "Price per unit"
msgstr "Cena na enoto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:50
msgid ""
"To display a :doc:`price per unit </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"product_management/configure/uom>` alongside the sales price on the product "
"page, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite na strani izdelka prikazati :doc:`ceno na enoto </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/uom>` poleg "
"prodajne cene, sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:54
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, and enable :guilabel:`Product Reference "
"Price`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"pomaknite se do razdelka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in "
"omogočite :guilabel:`Product Reference Price`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:56
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the product form <ecommerce/products/product-creation>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pojdite na obrazec izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-creation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:57
msgid ""
"Set the product's :guilabel:`Sales Price` and select the unit "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Units`)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :guilabel:`Sales Price` izdelka in izberite enoto "
"(npr. :guilabel:`Units`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:58
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Base Unit Count` field, enter the number of units in the "
"product, then select the relevant unit from the dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Base Unit Count` vnesite število enot v izdelku, nato pa "
"izberite ustrezno enoto s spustnega seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:62
msgid ""
"Imagine you want to sell a 2-liter bucket of paint for $60, i.e., $30 per "
"liter."
msgstr ""
"Predstavljajte si, da želite prodati 2-litrsko vedro barve za 60 $, torej 30 "
"$ na liter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:0
msgid "Cost per unit pricing on the product form."
msgstr "Cena na enoto na obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:67
msgid ""
"The price per units, in this case per liter, is shown next to the sales "
"price on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Cena na enoto, v tem primeru na liter, je prikazana poleg prodajne cene na "
"strani izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:0
msgid "Unit pricing on the product page."
msgstr "Cena na enoto na strani izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:74
msgid "The price per unit may be mandatory in some countries."
msgstr "Cena na enoto je v nekaterih državah lahko obvezna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:77
msgid ""
":doc:`/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"uom`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"uom`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:82
msgid "Pricelists"
msgstr "Ceniki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:84
msgid ""
"Pricelists in Odoo allow to manage flexible pricing rules and to offer "
"different prices and discounts based on currencies, time periods, purchase "
"volumes, :ref:`customers' location <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, and/or "
"customer type. To enable pricelists for eCommerce, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, enable :guilabel:`Pricelists`, "
"and :guilabel:`Save`. Then, click :guilabel:`Pricelists` or go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Pricelists` and :ref:`configure "
"<sales/products/pricelist-configuration>` the relevant pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Ceniki v Odoo omogočajo upravljanje prožnih cenovnih pravil ter ponujanje "
"različnih cen in popustov glede na valute, časovna obdobja, obsege "
"nakupov, :ref:`lokacijo strank <ecommerce/prices/geoip>` in/ali tip stranke. "
"Za omogočitev cenikov za e-trgovino pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran "
"--> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`e-Trgovina`, omogočite :guilabel:`Cenike` "
"in :guilabel:`Shranite`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ceniki` ali pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> e-Trgovina --> Ceniki` "
"in :ref:`konfigurirajte <sales/products/pricelist-configuration>` ustrezne "
"cenike."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:93
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Ecommerce` tab, configure options specific to online "
"sales, such as assigning a :guilabel:`Website` to a pricelist, allowing "
"customers to :ref:`select it <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`, and/"
"or adding an :ref:`E-commerce Promotional Code <ecommerce/prices/promotional-"
"code>`."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`e-trgovina` konfigurirajte možnosti, specifične za "
"spletno prodajo, kot je dodelitev :guilabel:`Spletne strani` ceniku, "
"dovolitev strankam, da ga :ref:`izberejo <ecommerce/prices/selectable-"
"pricelists>`, in/ali dodajanje :ref:`Promocijske kode za e-trgovino "
"<ecommerce/prices/promotional-code>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are using several websites and you want to use the same pricelist on "
"several of them, you need to duplicate the pricelist for each website. If "
"you do not assign any website, the pricelist will not be used, unless it "
"is :ref:`selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate več spletnih strani in želite uporabiti isti cenik na več "
"njih, morate cenik podvojiti za vsako spletno stran. Če ne dodelite nobene "
"spletne strani, cenik ne bo uporabljen, razen če je :ref:`izbirni <ecommerce/"
"prices/selectable-pricelists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:103
msgid ""
"Pricelists can also be :ref:`assigned to a specific customer <sales/products/"
"customer-pricelist-application>`."
msgstr ""
"Cenike je mogoče tudi :ref:`dodeliti določeni stranki <sales/products/"
"customer-pricelist-application>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:107
msgid ""
"When pricelists are enabled in the Sales app, they are automatically enabled "
"in the eCommerce app, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Ko so ceniki omogočeni v aplikaciji Prodaja, so samodejno omogočeni v "
"aplikaciji e-Trgovina in obratno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:109
msgid ""
"In the list of pricelists, order the pricelists by priority: the first takes "
"precedence over the second, the second over the third, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu cenikov razvrstite cenike po prednosti: prvi ima prednost pred "
"drugim, drugi pred tretjim in tako naprej."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:111
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create specific pricelists for :ref:`variants "
"<products/variants/configure-variants>`."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je tudi ustvariti posebne cenike za :ref:`različice <products/"
"variants/configure-variants>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:115
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:120
msgid "Selectable pricelists"
msgstr "Izbirni ceniki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:122
msgid ""
"Selectable pricelists are useful, for example, when selling products "
"in :doc:`multiple currencies </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"prices/currencies>` and allow customers to choose a pricelist using the "
"catalog's pricelist selector located next to the :ref:`search bar <ecommerce/"
"catalog/toolbar-and-filters>`."
msgstr ""
"Cenike, ki jih je mogoče izbrati, je smiselno uporabiti na primer pri "
"prodaji izdelkov v :doc:`več valutah </applications/sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/currencies>` in omogočajo strankam, da izberejo cenik "
"s pomočjo izbirnika cenika kataloga, ki se nahaja poleg :ref:`iskalne "
"vrstice <ecommerce/catalog/toolbar-and-filters>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:None
msgid "Pricelist selector on the e-commerce."
msgstr "Izbirnik cenika na spletni trgovini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:130
msgid "To make a pricelist selectable, enable :guilabel:`Selectable`."
msgstr "Za nastavitev cenika kot izbirnega omogočite :guilabel:`Izbirno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:133
msgid ""
"If a pricelist is designated as :guilabel:`Selectable`, and is not assigned "
"to a specific website, then the pricelist is selectable on **all** websites."
msgstr ""
"Če je cenik označen kot :guilabel:`Izbirni` in ni dodeljen določenemu "
"spletnemu mestu, je cenik na voljo za izbiro na **vseh** spletnih mestih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:135
msgid ""
"If a pricelist does *not* appear in the selector, it may be due to the "
"following situations:"
msgstr ""
"Če se cenik *ne* prikaže v izbirniku, je to morda posledica naslednjih "
"situacij:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:137
msgid ""
"Only one pricelist is defined as :guilabel:`Selectable` and "
"the :ref:`contact has a pricelist assigned <sales/products/customer-"
"pricelist-application>`."
msgstr ""
"Samo en cenik je določen kot :guilabel:`Izbirni` in :ref:`ima stik dodeljen "
"cenik <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:139
msgid ""
"Multiple selectable pricelists exist, but only those matching the "
"customer's :ref:`country group <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` are shown. "
"It is strongly recommended to disable the :guilabel:`Selectable` option when "
"using pricelists with country groups on the e-commerce."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več cenikov, ki jih je mogoče izbrati, vendar so prikazani samo "
"tisti, ki ustrezajo :ref:`državi skupine <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` "
"stranke. Močno priporočamo, da onemogočite možnost :guilabel:`Možno "
"izbrati`, ko na spletni trgovini uporabljate cenike s skupinami držav."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:145
msgid ":ref:`sales/products/currencies/currency-specific-pricelists`"
msgstr ":ref:`sales/products/currencies/currency-specific-pricelists`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:150
msgid "GeoIP & country groups"
msgstr "GeoIP in skupine držav"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:152
msgid ""
"It is possible to display a specific pricelist based on the visitor's "
"location and IP address by assigning :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/"
"country-groups>` to pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je prikazati določen cenik glede na lokacijo in IP naslov obiskovalca "
"z dodelitvijo :ref:`skupin držav <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` cenikom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:157
msgid ""
"To do so, :ref:`navigate to the relevant pricelist form <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` and select the appropriate :guilabel:`Country Groups`. Create "
"or edit as many pricelists for specific regions as needed. For instance, "
"select :guilabel:`European Union` to apply the pricelist to all EU member "
"states."
msgstr ""
"Za to :ref:`pojdite na ustrezni obrazec cenika <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` in izberite ustrezne :guilabel:`Skupine držav`. Ustvarite ali "
"uredite toliko cenikov za določene regije, kot je potrebno. Na primer, "
"izberite :guilabel:`Evropska unija`, da uporabite cenik za vse članice EU."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:162
msgid ""
"To create a new country group, click :guilabel:`Search more` in the dropdown "
"list, then :guilabel:`New`. Add a :guilabel:`Group Name` and select the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Countries`. Use :ref:`Custom filters <search/custom-"
"filters>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove skupine držav kliknite :guilabel:`Išči več` v spustnem "
"seznamu, nato :guilabel:`Novo`. Dodajte :guilabel:`Naziv skupine` in "
"izberite ustrezne :guilabel:`Države`. Po potrebi uporabite :ref:`Filtre po "
"meri <search/custom-filters>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:167
msgid "Each country group must contain at least one country."
msgstr "Vsaka skupina držav mora vsebovati vsaj eno državo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:170
msgid ""
"Use the following filter if you want to add all non-EU countries to the "
"country group."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite naslednji filter, če želite v skupino držav dodati vse države, ki "
"niso članice EU."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:172
msgid "`Country Groups` + `is not equal to` + `European Union`"
msgstr "`Skupine držav` + `ni enako` + `Evropska unija`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:0
msgid "Filter for country group creation."
msgstr "Filter za ustvarjanje skupine držav."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:178
msgid ""
"When using GeoIP to determine the appropriate pricelist, **all** pricelists "
"used on the e-commerce must have a country group assigned."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi GeoIP za določitev ustreznega cenika morajo imeti **vsi** "
"ceniki, ki se uporabljajo na spletni trgovini, dodeljeno skupino držav."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:180
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended to disable the :guilabel:`Selectable` option when "
"using pricelists with country groups. Indeed, all pricelists with the "
"relevant country group are automatically applied to the catalog but if one "
"of them is marked as :ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-"
"pricelists>`, the others will disappear as soon as customers select the "
"selectable pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Močno priporočamo, da onemogočite možnost :guilabel:`Izbirno`, ko "
"uporabljate cenike s skupinami držav. Vsi ceniki z ustrezno skupino držav se "
"namreč samodejno uporabijo v katalogu, če pa je eden od njih označen "
"kot :ref:`Izbirno <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`, bodo ostali "
"izginili takoj, ko stranke izberejo izbirni cenik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:187
msgid "Imagine you create three pricelists:"
msgstr "Predstavljajte si, da ustvarite tri cenike:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:189
msgid "`EU regular prices` with the `EU` country group assigned"
msgstr "`EU navadne cene` z dodeljeno skupino držav `EU`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:190
msgid "`EU prices with discounts` with the `EU` country group assigned"
msgstr "`EU cene s popusti` z dodeljeno skupino držav `EU`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:191
msgid "`US prices` with the `US` country group assigned"
msgstr "`US cene` z dodeljeno skupino držav `US`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:193
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Selectable` option is enabled for `EU regular prices` and "
"`US prices`, and the customer is from the European Union, only the "
"pricelists `EU regular prices` and `EU prices with discounts` will be "
"available. However, since the `EU prices with discount` list is not "
"selectable, it will disappear once the customer selects the `EU regular "
"prices` list and prices will be displayed based on the `EU regular prices` "
"pricelist on the catalog."
msgstr ""
"Če je možnost :guilabel:`Izbirno` omogočena za `EU navadne cene` in `US "
"cene`, in je stranka iz Evropske unije, bosta na voljo samo cenika `EU "
"navadne cene` in `EU cene s popusti`. Ker pa seznam `EU cene s popusti` ni "
"izbirljiv, bo izginil, ko stranka izbere seznam `EU navadne cene`, in cene "
"bodo prikazane na podlagi cenika `EU navadne cene` v katalogu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:201
msgid "Pricelist application"
msgstr "Uporaba cenika"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:203
msgid ""
"On the e-commerce, the *default* pricelist is automatically selected for "
"public, non-logged in users when no country group is assigned. "
"If :ref:`GeoIP and country groups <ecommerce/prices/geoip>` are used, public "
"users see the pricelist of their country group by default. :ref:`Logged-in "
"users <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` with :ref:`assigned "
"pricelists <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>` see the assigned "
"pricelist by default **if it is assigned to the website** they are visiting. "
"If not, the website's default pricelist is applied (i.e., the first "
"available pricelist assigned to the website and without a country group, "
"following the sequence order)."
msgstr ""
"Na spletni trgovini je za javne, neprijavljene uporabnike, ki nimajo "
"dodeljene skupine držav, samodejno izbran *privzeti* cenik. Če se "
"uporabljajo :ref:`GeoIP in skupine držav <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, javni "
"uporabniki privzeto vidijo cenik svoje skupine držav. :ref:`Prijavljeni "
"uporabniki <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` z :ref:`dodeljenimi "
"ceniki <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>` privzeto vidijo "
"dodeljeni cenik, **če je dodeljen spletni strani**, ki jo obiskujejo. Če ni, "
"se uporabi privzeti cenik spletne strani (tj. prvi razpoložljivi cenik, "
"dodeljen spletni strani in brez skupine držav, po vrstnem redu zaporedja)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:212
msgid ""
"Assigned pricelists take precedence over country-based pricelists, when "
"applicable, unless the assigned pricelist is linked to a different country "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Dodeljeni ceniki imajo prednost pred ceniki na podlagi države, kadar je to "
"primerno, razen če je dodeljeni cenik povezan z drugo skupino držav."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:216
msgid ""
"A customer from the United States visits the website. They do not have a "
"portal account. The :guilabel:`United States` pricelist is applied."
msgstr ""
"Stranka iz Združenih držav obišče spletno mesto. Nima računa na portalu. "
"Uporabljen je cenik :guilabel:`Združene države`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:219
msgid ""
"A different visitor, also from the United States, has the :guilabel:`Loyal "
"Customer Discount` pricelist assigned in their contact form. This assignment "
"takes precedence over the country group assignation, so the :guilabel:`Loyal "
"Customer Discount` is applied."
msgstr ""
"Drug obiskovalec, prav tako iz Združenih držav, ima v svojem kontaktnem "
"obrazcu dodeljen cenik :guilabel:`Popust za zveste stranke`. Ta dodelitev "
"ima prednost pred dodelitvijo skupine držav, zato se "
"uporabi :guilabel:`Popust za zveste stranke`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:0
msgid "An example of various pricelists assigned to a website."
msgstr "Primer različnih cenikov, dodeljenih spletnemu mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:230
msgid "Discounts"
msgstr "Popusti"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:233
msgid "Discounts programs"
msgstr "Programi popustov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:235
msgid ""
"To enable :doc:`discount programs </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"loyalty_discount>` for your e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` "
"section, and enable the :guilabel:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` feature."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti :doc:`programe popustov </applications/sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>` za svojo spletno trgovino, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se "
"pomaknite navzdol do odseka :guilabel:`eCommerce` in omogočite "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Popusti, zvestoba in darilne kartice`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:240
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure <sales/products/loyalty-programs>` the discount program, "
"make sure the :guilabel:`Website` option is enabled, and add the "
"relevant :ref:`Pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` "
"and :guilabel:`Website` on the program form, if needed."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konfigurirajte <sales/products/loyalty-programs>` program popustov, "
"prepričajte se, da je možnost :guilabel:`Spletna stran` omogočena, in po "
"potrebi dodajte ustrezni :ref:`Cenik <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` "
"in :guilabel:`Spletno stran` na obrazec programa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:247
msgid "Permanent product discount"
msgstr "Stalni popust izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:249
msgid ""
"If the price of a specific product has been permanently reduced, the "
"strikethrough strategy is commonly used. This involves showing the new "
"discounted price, with the original price crossed out alongside it."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila cena določenega izdelka trajno znižana, se običajno uporablja "
"strategija prečrtavanja. To vključuje prikaz nove znižane cene, poleg katere "
"je prikazana prečrtana prvotna cena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:None
msgid "Price strikethrough."
msgstr "Prečrtana cena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:256
msgid ""
"To display a permanently discounted price, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce`, enable the :guilabel:`Comparison Price` option, "
"and :guilabel:`Save`. Then, :ref:`go to the product form <ecommerce/products/"
"product-creation>`, enter the new (discounted) price in the :guilabel:`Sales "
"Price` field and the original one (strikethrough) in the :guilabel:`Compare "
"to Price` field."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz trajno znižane cene pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite navzdol "
"do :guilabel:`eCommerce`, omogočite možnost :guilabel:`Primerjalna cena` "
"in :guilabel:`Shrani`. Nato :ref:`pojdite na obrazec izdelka <ecommerce/"
"products/product-creation>`, vnesite novo (znižano) ceno v "
"polje :guilabel:`Prodajna cena` in izvirno (prečrtano) v "
"polje :guilabel:`Primerjaj s ceno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:264
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Compare to Price` field must contain a price that is higher "
"than the :guilabel:`Sales Price` for the original price to appear with a "
"strikethrough."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Primerjaj s ceno` mora vsebovati ceno, ki je višja "
"od :guilabel:`Prodajne cene`, da se prvotna cena prikaže s prečrtanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:268
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Compare to Price` is not displayed if discounted pricelists "
"apply. If you want to use the :guilabel:`Compare to price` with another "
"discount, configure a pricelist with a :ref:`promotional code <ecommerce/"
"prices/promotional-code>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Primerjaj s ceno` se ne prikaže, če se uporabijo ceniki s "
"popusti. Če želite uporabiti :guilabel:`Primerjaj s ceno` z drugim popustom, "
"konfigurirajte cenik s :ref:`promocijsko kodo <ecommerce/prices/promotional-"
"code>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:273
msgid "Discounted pricelists"
msgstr "Ceniki s popusti"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:275
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create :ref:`pricelists with discounts <sales/"
"products/price-rules>`. To do so, :ref:`create a pricelist <sales/products/"
"pricelist-configuration>` and :ref:`configure the discount <sales/products/"
"price-rules>`."
msgstr ""
"Možno je tudi ustvariti :ref:`cenike s popusti <sales/products/price-"
"rules>`. Za to :ref:`ustvarite cenik <sales/products/pricelist-"
"configuration>` in :ref:`konfigurirajte popust <sales/products/price-rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:279
msgid ""
"If a :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` contains "
"a :ref:`Discount <sales/products/price-rules>` price type, the price is "
"striked through for applicable customers, even if the :ref:`Comparison Price "
"<ecommerce/prices/permanent-discounts>` feature has not been enabled."
msgstr ""
"Če :ref:`cenik <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` vsebuje vrsto "
"cene :ref:`Popust <sales/products/price-rules>`, je cena prečrtana za "
"ustrezne stranke, tudi če funkcija :ref:`Primerjalna cena <ecommerce/prices/"
"permanent-discounts>` ni bila omogočena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:285
msgid ""
"If using pricelists with :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, the "
"discounted pricelist must be assigned the same country group as the one used "
"for the non-discounted pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate cenike s :ref:`skupinami držav <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, "
"mora biti ceniki s popusti dodeljena ista skupina držav, kot se uporablja za "
"cenik brez popusta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:291
msgid "E-commerce promotional code"
msgstr "Promocijska koda e-trgovine"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:293
msgid ""
"To offer a discounted pricelist for customers with a specific discount code, "
"access the relevant :ref:`pricelist form <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce` tab, and add an :guilabel:`E-commerce "
"Promotional Code`, e.g., `SUMMERSALE10%`. Then, go to the :guilabel:`Sales "
"Prices` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, and :ref:`configure the discount "
"<sales/products/price-rules>`. When a customer inserts the code during "
"the :ref:`checkout process <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`, this discount "
"is granted according to the :guilabel:`Sales Prices` configuration."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ponuditi cenik s popustom za stranke s posebno kodo za popust, "
"odprite ustrezen :ref:`obrazec cenika <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`, "
"pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Spletna trgovina` in "
"dodajte :guilabel:`Promocijsko kodo za e-trgovino`, npr. `SUMMERSALE10%`. "
"Nato pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Prodajne cene`, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"vrstico` in :ref:`konfigurirajte popust <sales/products/price-rules>`. Ko "
"stranka med :ref:`procesom blagajne <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` vnese "
"kodo, je ta popust dodeljen v skladu s konfiguracijo :guilabel:`Prodajnih "
"cen`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:302
msgid ""
"Make sure that the :ref:`Promo Code <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` "
"option in the website editor is enabled and, if using :ref:`country groups "
"<ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`, that the discounted pricelist has the "
"same country group assigned as the non-discounted pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je možnost :ref:`Promocijska koda <ecommerce/checkout/"
"review_order>` v urejevalniku spletne strani omogočena in, če "
"uporabljate :ref:`skupine držav <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`, da ima "
"cenik s popustom dodeljeno enako skupino držav kot cenik brez popusta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:310
msgid "Hide prices"
msgstr "Skrij cene"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:312
msgid ""
"Some businesses, such as :ref:`B2B shops <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` or "
"companies that sell luxury or custom items, often prefer to showcase their "
"products online without displaying their prices."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera podjetja, kot so :ref:`trgovine B2B <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` ali "
"podjetja, ki prodajajo luksuzne ali izdelane po meri, pogosto raje "
"predstavijo svoje izdelke na spletu brez prikazovanja cen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:315
msgid ""
"To hide product prices on the e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, enable :guilabel:`Prevent Sale of Zero Priced "
"Product` in the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, and enter a redirect URL in "
"the :guilabel:`Button URL` field. The :guilabel:`Add to Cart` button on the "
"product page is then replaced by a :guilabel:`Contact us` button, which can "
"be :ref:`customized <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-sale>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite skriti cene izdelkov na spletni trgovini, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, "
"omogočite :guilabel:`Prepreči prodajo izdelka z ničelno ceno` v "
"odseku :guilabel:`eCommerce` in vnesite preusmeritveni URL v "
"polje :guilabel:`URL gumba`. Gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj v košarico` na strani "
"izdelka se nato zamenja z gumbom :guilabel:`Kontaktirajte nas`, ki ga je po "
"potrebi mogoče :ref:`prilagoditi <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-sale>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:321
msgid ""
"After enabling this feature, either set the price to `0` for all desired "
"products or create a :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` with all "
"product prices set to `0`. Ensure the pricelist is assigned to the correct "
"website and is listed first among the website's pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Po omogočitvi te funkcije bodisi nastavite ceno na `0` za vse želene izdelke "
"ali ustvarite :ref:`cenik <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` z vsemi cenami "
"izdelkov, nastavljenimi na `0`. Prepričajte se, da je cenik dodeljen "
"pravilni spletni strani in je naveden prvi med cenniki spletne strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:326
msgid ""
"Ensure no pricelist used on the e-commerce has been marked "
"as :guilabel:`Selectable` to prevent accidentally displaying the zero-priced "
"pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Poskrbite, da noben cenik, ki se uporablja na spletni trgovini, ni označen "
"kot :guilabel:`Možno izbrati`, da preprečite nenamerno prikazovanje cenika z "
"ničelno ceno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:328
msgid ""
"To hide prices from public visitors while keeping them visible to logged-in "
"customers, create a zero-priced pricelist to be used for non-logged-in "
"customers and :ref:`assign <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>` "
"a regular pricelist (with actual prices) to customers with :doc:`portal "
"access <../../../general/users/user_portals/portal_access>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite cene skriti pred javnimi obiskovalci, hkrati pa jih ohraniti vidne "
"za prijavljene stranke, ustvarite cenik z ničelno ceno za neprijavljene "
"stranke in :ref:`dodelite <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>` "
"običajen cenik (z dejanskimi cenami) strankam z :doc:`dostopom do portala "
"<../../../general/users/user_portals/portal_access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce allows you to :ref:`create products <ecommerce/products/"
"product-creation>` and manage their :ref:`visibility <ecommerce/products/"
"publish-products>` on the website. Products can be :ref:`configured "
"<ecommerce/products/product-configuration>` in various ways, including "
"adding :ref:`product images and videos <ecommerce/products/images>`, "
"creating :ref:`product combinations <ecommerce/products/combos>`, "
"implementing :ref:`cross-selling and upselling strategies <ecommerce/"
"products/cross_upselling>`, attaching :ref:`digital files <ecommerce/"
"products/digital-files>`, :ref:`translating <ecommerce/products/"
"translation>` product information, :ref:`managing stock <ecommerce/products/"
"stock-management>`, and setting :ref:`packaging options <ecommerce/products/"
"stock-management/packagings>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce omogoča :ref:`ustvarjanje izdelkov <ecommerce/products/"
"product-creation>` in upravljanje njihove :ref:`vidnosti <ecommerce/products/"
"publish-products>` na spletni strani. Izdelke je mogoče :ref:`konfigurirati "
"<ecommerce/products/product-configuration>` na različne načine, vključno z "
"dodajanjem :ref:`slik in videoposnetkov izdelkov <ecommerce/products/"
"images>`, ustvarjanjem :ref:`kombinacij izdelkov <ecommerce/products/"
"combos>`, izvajanjem :ref:`strategij navzkrižne in nadgradne prodaje "
"<ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`, prilaganjem :ref:`digitalnih datotek "
"<ecommerce/products/digital-files>`, :ref:`prevajanjem <ecommerce/products/"
"translation>` informacij o izdelkih, :ref:`upravljanjem zalog <ecommerce/"
"products/stock-management>` in nastavitvijo :ref:`možnosti pakiranja "
"<ecommerce/products/stock-management/packagings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:18
msgid "Product creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:20
msgid ""
"To create a product from the frontend, go to the Website app, "
"click :guilabel:`New` :icon:`fa-caret-down` in the top-right corner, then "
"select :guilabel:`Product`. Enter the :guilabel:`Product Name`, and other "
"relevant details such as the :guilabel:`Barcode`, :guilabel:`Sales Price`, "
"default :guilabel:`Sales Taxes`, and a :ref:`Website Category <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`, then add an image. Once you "
"click :guilabel:`Save`, you are redirected to the product page where you "
"can :ref:`customize it <ecommerce_design/product_page/customization>` using "
"the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/web_design>`. Once "
"you are finished, click :guilabel:`Save`. To configure additional "
"advanced :ref:`product details <ecommerce/products/product-configuration>`, "
"click :guilabel:`Product` in the top-right corner to access the backend "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje izdelka iz sprednjega vmesnika pojdite v aplikacijo Spletna "
"stran, kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` :icon:`fa-caret-down` v zgornjem desnem "
"kotu, nato izberite :guilabel:`Izdelek`. Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime izdelka` in "
"druge ustrezne podrobnosti, kot so :guilabel:`Črtna "
"koda`, :guilabel:`Prodajna cena`, privzeti :guilabel:`Prodajni davki` "
"in :ref:`Spletna kategorija <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>`, "
"nato dodajte sliko. Ko kliknete :guilabel:`Shrani`, ste preusmerjeni na "
"stran izdelka, kjer ga lahko :ref:`prilagodite <ecommerce_design/"
"product_page/customization>` z uporabo :doc:`urejevalnika spletne strani </"
"applications/websites/website/web_design>`. Ko končate, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`. Za konfiguracijo dodatnih "
"naprednih :ref:`podrobnosti izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-"
"configuration>` kliknite :guilabel:`Izdelek` v zgornjem desnem kotu za "
"dostop do obrazca izdelka v zalednem vmesniku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:32
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create a product from the backend by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`. Then:"
msgstr ""
"Izdelek je mogoče ustvariti tudi iz zalednega vmesnika tako, da pojdete "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> eCommerce --> Izdelki`. Nato:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:35
msgid "Configure a new product by clicking :guilabel:`New`, or"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte nov izdelek s klikom na :guilabel:`Novo` ali"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:36
msgid ""
":doc:`Import product data </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"products/import>` using XLSX or CSV files by clicking the :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`gear`) icon next to :guilabel:`Products`, then :ref:`Import "
"records <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Uvozite podatke o izdelkih </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"products/import>` z uporabo datotek XLSX ali CSV s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-"
"cog` (:guilabel:`zobnik`) poleg :guilabel:`Izdelki`, nato :ref:`Uvozi zapise "
"<essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:41
msgid ""
":doc:`Create new products using the Barcode Lookup database </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Ustvarite nove izdelke z uporabo podatkovne zbirke Barcode Lookup </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:43
msgid ""
":doc:`Configure the Gelato connector in Odoo to synchronize the product "
"catalog and automate order fulfillment with Gelato </applications/sales/"
"sales/gelato>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Konfigurirajte Gelato povezovalnik v Odoo za sinhronizacijo kataloga "
"izdelkov in avtomatizacijo izpolnjevanja naročil z Gelato </applications/"
"sales/sales/gelato>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:47
msgid "Product visibility"
msgstr "Vidnost izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:51
msgid ""
"To publish a product, access the product page on the website and switch the "
"toggle from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Za objavo izdelka odprite stran izdelka na spletni strani in preklopite "
"stikalo z :guilabel:`Neobjavljeno` na :guilabel:`Objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:55
msgid ""
"To access the product page from the product form in the backend, click "
"the :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do strani izdelka iz obrazca izdelka v zalednem vmesniku kliknite "
"pametno tipko :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Pojdi na spletno stran`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:57
msgid ""
"To publish products from the backend, navigate to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab "
"of the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` section and toggle the :guilabel:`Is "
"Published` switch on."
msgstr ""
"Za objavo izdelkov iz zalednega vmesnika pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja` v :ref:`obrazcu izdelka <ecommerce/products/"
"product-form>`, nato pojdite v razdelek :guilabel:`Spletna trgovina` in "
"preklopite stikalo :guilabel:`Je objavljeno` na vklopljeno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:61
msgid "To publish multiple products at once, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za objavo več izdelkov hkrati sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:63
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`."
msgstr "Pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> e-Trgovina --> Izdelki`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:64
msgid ""
"Remove the :guilabel:`Published` filter and switch to the :guilabel:`List` "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite filter :guilabel:`Objavljeno` in preklopite na "
"pogled :guilabel:`Seznam`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:65
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) icon on the far "
"right of the view and enable :guilabel:`Is Published`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`spustno stikalo`) na skrajni "
"desni strani pogleda in omogočite :guilabel:`Je objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:67
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Is Published` column to re-order it by *published* or "
"*unpublished* products."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite stolpec :guilabel:`Je objavljeno`, da ga ponovno razvrstite po "
"*objavljenih* ali *neobjavljenih* izdelkih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:69
msgid "Select the products to publish by ticking their box on the far left."
msgstr ""
"Izberite izdelke za objavo tako, da označite njihovo polje na skrajni levi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:70
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Is Published` column, tick the box for any of the selected "
"products, then :guilabel:`Update` to publish them."
msgstr ""
"V stolpcu :guilabel:`Je objavljeno` označite polje za katerega koli od "
"izbranih izdelkov, nato :guilabel:`Posodobi`, da jih objavite."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:76
msgid ""
"When managing multiple websites, the availability of a product on each "
"website can be set from the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`. Navigate to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, then in "
"the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` section, select the :guilabel:`Website` where "
"the product should be available. Leave the field blank to make the product "
"available on *all* websites. You can make a product available on either "
"*one* website or *all* websites, but selecting only *some* websites is not "
"possible. To sell the product on multiple specific websites without making "
"it available on all of them, **duplicate** the product for each website and "
"assign the corresponding website to each duplicate."
msgstr ""
"Pri upravljanju več spletnih strani je mogoče razpoložljivost izdelka na "
"vsaki spletni strani nastaviti iz :ref:`obrazca izdelka <ecommerce/products/"
"product-form>`. Pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja`, nato v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Spletna trgovina` izberite :guilabel:`Spletno stran`, "
"kjer naj bo izdelek na voljo. Pustite polje prazno, da bo izdelek na voljo "
"na *vseh* spletnih straneh. Izdelek lahko omogočite bodisi na *eni* spletni "
"strani bodisi na *vseh* spletnih straneh, vendar izbira samo *nekaterih* "
"spletnih strani ni mogoča. Za prodajo izdelka na več določenih spletnih "
"straneh, ne da bi bil na voljo na vseh, **podvojite** izdelek za vsako "
"spletno stran in dodelite ustrezno spletno stran vsaki kopiji."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:88
msgid "Product configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:92
msgid ""
"To add general information to a product, navigate to :menuselection:`Website "
"--> eCommerce --> Products` and select the relevant product. You can "
"configure various options, such as choosing a :doc:`product type </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"type>`, adding :doc:`variants and categories <categories_variants>`, or "
"defining :doc:`prices <prices>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati splošne informacije o izdelku, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> Izdelki` in izberite "
"ustrezni izdelek. Nastavite lahko različne možnosti, kot so "
"izbira :doc:`vrste izdelka </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"product_management/configure/type>`, dodajanje :doc:`variant in kategorij "
"<categories_variants>` ali določanje :doc:`cen <prices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:99
msgid ""
"Additionally, add an e-commerce-specific product description to be displayed "
"below the product name on the frontend :doc:`product page <../"
"ecommerce_design/product_page>`. To do so, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce description` section, and write a "
"description. Use Odoo's :doc:`rich-text editor </applications/essentials/"
"html_editor>` to customize the content."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega dodajte opis izdelka, specifičen za e-trgovino, ki se bo "
"prikazoval pod imenom izdelka na uporabniški strani :doc:`izdelka <../"
"ecommerce_design/product_page>`. To storite tako, da odprete "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja`, se pomaknete navzdol do "
"odseka :guilabel:`Ecommerce opis` in napišete opis. Za prilagoditev vsebine "
"uporabite Odoojev :doc:`urejevalnik obogatenega besedila </applications/"
"essentials/html_editor>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:106
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button to access "
"the frontend product page and :doc:`customize <../ecommerce_design/"
"product_page>` it using the :doc:`website editor <../../website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite pametni gumb :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Pojdi na spletno mesto`, "
"da odprete uporabniško stran izdelka in jo :doc:`prilagodite <../"
"ecommerce_design/product_page>` z uporabo :doc:`urejevalnika spletnega mesta "
"<../../website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:109
msgid ""
"Product descriptions can also be generated using :doc:`AI </applications/"
"productivity/ai>`. To do so, type `/` in the :guilabel:`Ecommerce "
"description` section and select :guilabel:`AI` to open the :doc:`AI agent </"
"applications/productivity/ai/agents>`."
msgstr ""
"Opise izdelkov lahko ustvarite tudi z uporabo :doc:`umetne inteligence </"
"applications/productivity/ai>`. To storite tako, da v "
"odseku :guilabel:`Ecommerce opis` vnesete `/` in izberete :guilabel:`AI`, da "
"odprete :doc:`agenta UI </applications/productivity/ai/agents>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:116
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:17
msgid "Product images and videos"
msgstr "Slike in videoposnetki izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:118
msgid ""
"To add media items, such as images and videos, navigate to the :ref:`product "
"form <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. "
"In the :guilabel:`Ecommerce Media` section, click :guilabel:`Add Media`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Select a media` pop-up window:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati predstavnostne elemente, kot so slike in videoposnetki, "
"pojdite v :ref:`obrazec izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-form>` in "
"odprite zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja`. V odseku :guilabel:`Ecommerce Media` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj medije`. V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Izberite "
"medij`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:122
msgid ""
"To add an image, select an image, click :guilabel:`Add URL` "
"or :guilabel:`Upload an image` in the :guilabel:`Images` tab."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati sliko, izberite sliko, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj URL` "
"ali :guilabel:`Naloži sliko` v zavihku :guilabel:`Slike`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:124
msgid ""
"To add a video, navigate to the :guilabel:`Videos` tab, paste a video URL, "
"or :ref:`embed HTML code <website/building_blocks/embed_code>`. Then, enable "
"the relevant :ref:`video options <website/elements/videos>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati videoposnetek, pojdite v zavihek :guilabel:`Videoposnetki`, "
"prilepite URL videoposnetka ali :ref:`vdelaj kodo HTML <website/"
"building_blocks/embed_code>`. Nato omogočite ustrezne :ref:`možnosti "
"videoposnetka <website/elements/videos>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:128
msgid "Once the media is selected, click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr "Ko je medij izbran, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:131
msgid ""
":ref:`Customize product images and videos <ecommerce/product_page/image-"
"customization>` using the :doc:`website editor <../../website/web_design>` "
"from the frontend."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Prilagodite slike in videoposnetke izdelkov <ecommerce/product_page/"
"image-customization>` z uporabo :doc:`urejevalnika spletnega mesta <../../"
"website/web_design>` z uporabniške strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:137
msgid "Product combos"
msgstr "Kombinacije izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:139
msgid ""
":ref:`Product combinations <pos/products/combos>` allow users to configure a "
"set of related products to buy as a bundle. To :ref:`configure combos <pos/"
"products/combo-choices>`, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Combo Choices`. Once finished and published, customers can choose the combo "
"when adding the product to the cart. Depending on the configuration, certain "
"items may incur an additional charge."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Kombinacije izdelkov <pos/products/combos>` omogočajo uporabnikom, da "
"konfigurirajo nabor povezanih izdelkov za nakup kot paket. "
"Za :ref:`konfiguracijo kombinacij <pos/products/combo-choices>` pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> Izbirne kombinacije`. Ko "
"je končano in objavljeno, lahko stranke izberejo kombinacijo pri dodajanju "
"izdelka v košarico. Odvisno od konfiguracije lahko za določene artikle "
"nastanejo dodatni stroški."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:None
msgid "Add the combo product to the cart."
msgstr "Dodajte kombinirani izdelek v košarico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:152
msgid "Cross-selling & Upselling"
msgstr "Navzkrižna prodaja in nadgradnja prodaje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:154
msgid ""
"Cross-selling and upselling are sales techniques used to present customers "
"with additional or higher-tier products and services from the :doc:`catalog "
"<../../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>`. Cross-selling focuses on "
"recommending accessory or :doc:`optional products </applications/sales/sales/"
"sales_quotations/optional_products>` alongside the item being purchased "
"during ordering and checkout. Upselling, on the other hand, encourages "
"customers to choose a higher-priced or upgraded alternative product."
msgstr ""
"Navzkrižna prodaja in nadgradnja prodaje sta prodajni tehniki, s katerima "
"strankam predstavimo dodatne izdelke in storitve ali izdelke višjega razreda "
"iz :doc:`kataloga <../../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>`. Navzkrižna "
"prodaja se osredotoča na priporočanje dodatnih ali :doc:`izbirnih izdelkov </"
"applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products>` poleg izdelka, "
"ki se kupuje, med naročanjem in plačilom. Nadgradnja prodaje po drugi strani "
"stranke spodbuja, da izberejo dražjo ali nadgrajeno alternativo izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:161
msgid ""
"To configure these product suggestions, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select the relevant product, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, and add the desired products in the "
"corresponding :guilabel:`Optional products`, :guilabel:`Accessory Products`, "
"and/or :guilabel:`Alternative products` fields."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti ta predloga izdelkov, pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno "
"mesto --> eCommerce --> Izdelki`, izberite ustrezni izdelek, odprite "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja` in dodajte želene izdelke v ustrezna "
"polja :guilabel:`Izbirni izdelki`, :guilabel:`Dodatni izdelki` in/"
"ali :guilabel:`Alternativni izdelki`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:168
msgid "Optional products"
msgstr "Izbirni izdelki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:170
msgid ""
"Optional products are suggested when the customer clicks the :guilabel:`Add "
"to cart` button to buy a specific product."
msgstr ""
"Izbirni izdelki so predlagani, ko stranka klikne gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj v "
"košarico`, da kupi določen izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid "Optional products cross-selling."
msgstr "Navzkrižna prodaja izbirnih izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:176
msgid "Accessory products"
msgstr "Dodatni izdelki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:178
msgid ""
"Accessory products appear in the :guilabel:`Suggested accessories` section "
"during the :guilabel:`Order summary` step, just prior to proceeding to "
"checkout."
msgstr ""
"Dodatni izdelki se prikažejo v odseku :guilabel:`Predlagane dodatke` med "
"korakom :guilabel:`Povzetek naročila`, tik preden nadaljujete na plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid "Suggested accessories at checkout during cart review"
msgstr "Predlagani dodatki ob zaključku nakupa med pregledom košarice"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:185
msgid ""
"To hide this section, open the :doc:`website editor <../../website/"
"web_design>`, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Suggested Accessories` switch off."
msgstr ""
"Če želite skriti ta odsek, odprite :doc:`urejevalnik spletnega mesta <../../"
"website/web_design>`, pojdite v zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in izklopite "
"stikalo :guilabel:`Predlagani dodatki`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:188
msgid "Alternative products"
msgstr "Alternativni izdelki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:190
msgid ""
"Alternative products are displayed at the bottom of the :doc:`product page "
"<../ecommerce_design/product_page>` under the :guilabel:`Alternative "
"Products` heading."
msgstr ""
"Alternativni izdelki so prikazani na dnu :doc:`strani izdelka <../"
"ecommerce_design/product_page>` pod naslovom :guilabel:`Alternativni "
"izdelki`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid "The alternative products section of an product page."
msgstr "Razdelek z alternativnimi izdelki na strani izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:197
msgid ""
"To customize this block, open the :doc:`website editor <../../website/"
"web_design>`, click the block on the page, and :doc:`adapt the heading and "
"text <../../website/web_design/elements>` if necessary. Go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, scroll to the :guilabel:`Alternative Products` "
"section, and modify the options as needed."
msgstr ""
"Za prilagoditev tega bloka odprite :doc:`urejevalnik spletnega mesta <../../"
"website/web_design>`, kliknite blok na strani in po "
"potrebi :doc:`prilagodite naslov in besedilo <../../website/web_design/"
"elements>`. Pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog`, pomaknite se do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Alternativni izdelki` in po potrebi spremenite možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:206
msgid "Digital files"
msgstr "Digitalne datoteke"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:208
msgid ""
"It is possible to link digital files, such as certificates, eBooks, or user "
"manuals, to the products. To do so, go to the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` and click the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Documents` smart button. Then, click :guilabel:`Upload` to "
"upload a file directly, or for additional options, click :guilabel:`New`. "
"Choose the :guilabel:`Type` of attachment:"
msgstr ""
"Digitalne datoteke, kot so certifikati, e-knjige ali navodila za uporabo, je "
"mogoče povezati z izdelki. To storite tako, da odprete :ref:`obrazec izdelka "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>` in kliknete pametni gumb :icon:`fa-file-"
"text-o` :guilabel:`Dokumenti`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži`, da naložite "
"datoteko neposredno, ali za dodatne možnosti kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. "
"Izberite :guilabel:`Vrsto` priloge:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:214
msgid ":guilabel:`File`: :guilabel:`Upload your file`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datoteka`: :guilabel:`Naložite svojo datoteko`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:215
msgid ":guilabel:`URL`: Insert the link to the file or media item."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL`: Vstavite povezavo do datoteke ali predstavnostnega elementa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:216
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cloud Storage` (if applicable): Insert a link to your cloud "
"storage to store the file on the :doc:`cloud storage </applications/general/"
"integrations/cloud_storage>` platform instead of the database’s server."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oblačno shranjevanje` (če je na voljo): Vstavite povezavo do "
"svojega oblačnega shranjevanja, da shranite datoteko na "
"platformo :doc:`oblačnega shranjevanja </applications/general/integrations/"
"cloud_storage>` namesto na strežnik zbirke podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:220
msgid "These documents can be made available:"
msgstr "Ti dokumenti so lahko na voljo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:222
msgid ""
"On the product page (before checkout): Set the :guilabel:`Sales visibility` "
"field to :guilabel:`Hidden` and enable :guilabel:`Publish on website`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani izdelka (pred blagajno): Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Vidnost v "
"prodaji` na :guilabel:`Skrito` in omogočite :guilabel:`Objavi na spletnem "
"mestu`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:224
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`customer portal </applications/general/users/user_portals>` on "
"the confirmed sales order (after checkout): Set the :guilabel:`Sales "
"visibility` field to :guilabel:`On confirmed order` and "
"disable :guilabel:`Publish on website`."
msgstr ""
"V :doc:`portalu za stranke </applications/general/users/user_portals>` na "
"potrjenem prodajnem nalogu (po blagajni): Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Vidnost "
"v prodaji` na :guilabel:`Ob potrjenem nalogu` in "
"onemogočite :guilabel:`Objavi na spletnem mestu`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:229
msgid ""
"In :ref:`Kanban <studio/views/multiple-records/kanban>` view, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`dropdown menu`) in the top-right "
"corner of the document card to :guilabel:`Edit`, :guilabel:`Delete`, "
"or :guilabel:`Download` the document."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu :ref:`Kanban <studio/views/multiple-records/kanban>` "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`spustni meni`) v zgornjem desnem "
"kotu kartice dokumenta, da :guilabel:`Uredite`, :guilabel:`Izbrišete` "
"ali :guilabel:`Prenesete` dokument."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:236
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Prevod"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:238
msgid ""
"If a website is available in multiple languages, product information can be "
"translated directly on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`. Fields that support multiple languages are identifiable by their "
"language abbreviation (e.g., `EN`) next to the field, such as "
"the :guilabel:`Product name`, :ref:`Out-of-Stock Message <ecommerce/products/"
"stock-management>`, the :ref:`E-Commerce Description <ecommerce/products/"
"description>`, :ref:`ribbon or badge <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"product-highlight>` names, :doc:`categories and variants "
"<categories_variants>` names, etc."
msgstr ""
"Če je spletno mesto na voljo v več jezikih, je informacije o izdelku mogoče "
"prevesti neposredno na :ref:`obrazcu izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`. Polja, ki podpirajo več jezikov, so prepoznavna po jezikovni "
"okrajšavi (npr. `EN`) poleg polja, kot so :guilabel:`Ime "
"izdelka`, :ref:`Sporočilo o razprodanosti <ecommerce/products/stock-"
"management>`, :ref:`Opis za e-trgovino <ecommerce/products/description>`, "
"imena :ref:`trak ali značk <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"highlight>`, imena :doc:`kategorij in različic <categories_variants>` itd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:247
msgid ""
"Having untranslated content on a web page may be detrimental to the user "
"experience and :doc:`SEO </applications/websites/website/structure/seo>`. To "
"avoid this, use the :ref:`Translate <translate/translate>` feature to "
"translate any remaining untranslated content on the page."
msgstr ""
"Neprevedena vsebina na spletni strani lahko škodi uporabniški izkušnji "
"in :doc:`SEO </applications/websites/website/structure/seo>`. Da bi se temu "
"izognili, uporabite funkcijo :ref:`Prevedi <translate/translate>`, da "
"prevedete vso preostalo neprevedeno vsebino na strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:253
msgid ""
":doc:`Website languages and translations </applications/websites/website/"
"configuration/translate>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Jeziki in prevodi spletnega mesta </applications/websites/website/"
"configuration/translate>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:130
msgid "Stock management"
msgstr "Upravljanje zalog"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:262
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Inventory app </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` must be "
"installed to handle stock-related settings and operations."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija :doc:`Zaloga </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` mora "
"biti nameščena za upravljanje nastavitev in operacij, povezanih z zalogo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:265
msgid ""
"To configure stock-related e-commerce options, go to :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` "
"section, then to the :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` subsection. The "
"following settings are available:"
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev možnosti e-trgovine, povezanih z zalogo, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se "
"pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`eCommerce`, nato do "
"podrazdelka :guilabel:`Privzete nastavitve zaloge`. Na voljo so naslednje "
"nastavitve:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:269
msgid ""
"If multiple :doc:`warehouses </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>` exist, select the "
"relevant one from the :guilabel:`Warehouse` dropdown menu to set it as the "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja več :doc:`skladišč </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>`, izberite ustrezno iz "
"spustnega menija :guilabel:`Skladišče`, da ga nastavite kot privzeto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:273
msgid ""
"Next to :guilabel:`Out-of-Stock`, enable :guilabel:`Continue Selling` to "
"allow customers to place orders even when the product is out of stock. Keep "
"this option disabled to prevent customers from ordering products that are "
"out of stock."
msgstr ""
"Poleg :guilabel:`Razprodano` omogočite :guilabel:`Nadaljuj s prodajo`, da "
"strankam omogočite oddajo naročil tudi, ko je izdelek razprodan. To možnost "
"pustite onemogočeno, da strankam preprečite naročanje izdelkov, ki so "
"razprodani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:276
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Show Available Quantity` option to display the "
"remaining available quantity on the product page when it drops below a "
"defined threshold. The available quantity is calculated based on "
"the :guilabel:`On hand` quantity minus the quantity already :doc:`reserved </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"reservation_methods>` for outgoing transfers."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite možnost :guilabel:`Prikaži razpoložljivo količino`, da na strani "
"izdelka prikažete preostalo razpoložljivo količino, ko pade pod določen "
"prag. Razpoložljiva količina se izračuna na podlagi količine :guilabel:`Na "
"zalogi` minus količina, ki je že :doc:`rezervirana </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/reservation_methods>` za "
"odhodni prenos."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:282
msgid ""
"These settings apply to *all* products, but can be adapted for individual "
"products if needed. To do so, go to the product form and make sure "
"the :ref:`Track inventory option <inventory/product_management/tracking-"
"inventory>` is enabled. Then, navigate to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab and, "
"under the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` section, enable or disable the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Sell when Out-of-Stock` and :guilabel:`Show Available "
"Qty` options. You can also compose an :guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` or "
"create an :ref:`out-of-stock ribbon or badge <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/product-highlight>`."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve veljajo za *vse* izdelke, vendar jih je mogoče po potrebi "
"prilagoditi za posamezne izdelke. To storite tako, da odprete obrazec "
"izdelka in se prepričate, da je omogočena možnost :ref:`Sledenje zalogam "
"<inventory/product_management/tracking-inventory>`. Nato pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja` in v razdelku :guilabel:`Spletna trgovina` "
"omogočite ali onemogočite ustrezne možnosti :guilabel:`Prodaj, ko je "
"razprodano` in :guilabel:`Prikaži razpoložljivo količino`. Lahko tudi "
"sestavite :guilabel:`Sporočilo o razprodanosti` ali ustvarite :ref:`trak ali "
"značko za razprodanost <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"highlight>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:291
msgid ""
"Modifying the general :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` settings does not "
"automatically modify the related option(s) on the product form for existing "
"products; it only affects products created after the feature is enabled/"
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje splošnih nastavitev :guilabel:`Privzete nastavitve zaloge` ne "
"spremeni samodejno povezanih možnosti na obrazcu izdelka za obstoječe "
"izdelke; vpliva samo na izdelke, ustvarjene po omogočanju/onemogočanju "
"funkcije."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:294
msgid ""
"To display the stock level on the product page, the :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"field on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>` must be "
"set to :guilabel:`Goods` or :guilabel:`Combo`."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz ravni zaloge na strani izdelka mora biti polje :guilabel:`Vrsta "
"izdelka` na :ref:`obrazcu izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-form>` "
"nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Blago` ali :guilabel:`Kombinacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:297
msgid ""
"A :icon:`fa-envelope-o` (:guilabel:`envelope`) :guilabel:`Get notified when "
"back in stock` button appears on the product page when an item is out of "
"stock. Customers can click the link to enter their email address and receive "
"a notification once the item is back in stock."
msgstr ""
"Ko je artikel razprodan, se na strani izdelka prikaže gumb :icon:`fa-"
"envelope-o` (:guilabel:`ovojnica`) :guilabel:`Obvesti me, ko bo spet na "
"zalogi`. Stranke lahko kliknejo povezavo, vnesejo svoj e-poštni naslov in "
"prejmejo obvestilo, ko bo artikel spet na zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:301
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`Click & Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>` feature is "
"enabled, the product availability is displayed on the product page based on "
"the stock in the warehouse defined on the related :doc:`delivery method </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>` form."
msgstr ""
"Če je funkcija :ref:`Klikni in prevzemi <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>` "
"omogočena, se razpoložljivost izdelka prikaže na strani izdelka na podlagi "
"zaloge v skladišču, določenem na povezanem obrazcu :doc:`načina dostave </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:308
msgid ""
"Currently, the `Boko Chair` is not available in any warehouses. However, "
"customers can click the :icon:`fa-envelope-o` "
"(:guilabel:`envelope`) :guilabel:`Get notified when back in stock` link to "
"receive a notification as soon as the product becomes available again. "
"An :guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` can also be added to inform customers "
"that the item will be replenished."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno `Boko Chair` ni na voljo v nobenem skladišču. Stranke pa lahko "
"kliknejo povezavo :icon:`fa-envelope-o` "
"(:guilabel:`ovojnica`) :guilabel:`Prejmi obvestilo, ko bo spet na zalogi`, "
"da prejmejo obvestilo, takoj ko bo izdelek spet na voljo. Mogoče je dodati "
"tudi :guilabel:`Sporočilo o razprodanosti`, da obvestite stranke, da bo "
"artikel dopolnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:0
msgid ""
"Example of a product that is out of stock, but which will be available again."
msgstr "Primer izdelka, ki ni na zalogi, a bo spet na voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:318
msgid ""
"If a unique reference is needed for inventory management, install "
"the :doc:`Manufacturing app </applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing>` "
"and create :doc:`kit bills of materials </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"manufacturing/advanced_configuration/kit_shipping>`. Each kit links its "
"published \"virtual\" products to the main reference tracked in Inventory. "
"This ensures that any item sold on the website is converted into the "
"corresponding stocked item in the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Če je za upravljanje zalog potrebna edinstvena referenca, "
"namestite :doc:`aplikacijo Proizvodnja </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"manufacturing>` in ustvarite :doc:`kompleta kosovnic </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/advanced_configuration/kit_shipping>`. Vsak "
"komplet poveže svoje objavljene \"virtualne\" izdelke z glavno referenco, ki "
"se spremlja v Zalogi. S tem zagotovite, da se kateri koli artikel, prodan na "
"spletni strani, pretvori v ustrezni artikel na zalogi v naročilu dobave."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:328
msgid "Packagings"
msgstr "Embalaže"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:330
msgid ""
"To offer different product pack sizes to customers on the e-commerce, "
"configure product :doc:`packagings </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/product_management/configure/packaging>`. Then go to "
"the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. Under :guilabel:`Upsell & cross-sell`, add as "
"many package types as needed in the :guilabel:`Packagings` field. The "
"available package types are displayed on the e-commerce :doc:`product page "
"<../ecommerce_design/product_page>`."
msgstr ""
"Za ponudbo različnih velikosti pakiranja izdelka strankam na spletni "
"trgovini konfigurirajte :doc:`pakiranja </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/product_management/configure/packaging>` izdelka. Nato pojdite "
"na :ref:`obrazec izdelka <ecommerce/products/product-form>` in odprite "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja`. Pod :guilabel:`Dodatna in navzkrižna prodaja` "
"dodajte v polje :guilabel:`Pakiranja` toliko vrst pakiranja, kot jih "
"potrebujete. Razpoložljive vrste pakiranja so prikazane na :doc:`strani "
"izdelka <../ecommerce_design/product_page>` spletne trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:None
msgid "Product packages on the e-commerce page."
msgstr "Paketi izdelkov na strani e-trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:342
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add packagings to a specific :ref:`product variant "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`. To do so, go to the "
"product form, click the :icon:`fa-sitemap` :guilabel:`Variants` :ref:`smart "
"button <products/variants/variants-smart-button>`, and select the relevant "
"product variant. Under :guilabel:`Sales`, add as many package types as "
"needed in the :guilabel:`Packagings` field."
msgstr ""
"Embalažo je mogoče dodati tudi določeni :ref:`varianti izdelka <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/product-variants>`. To storite tako, da greste na "
"obrazec izdelka, kliknete gumb :icon:`fa-"
"sitemap` :guilabel:`Variante` :ref:`v pametnem meniju <products/variants/"
"variants-smart-button>` in izberete ustrezno varianto izdelka. "
"Pod :guilabel:`Prodaja` dodajte toliko vrst paketov, kot jih potrebujete, v "
"polje :guilabel:`Embalaže`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:9
msgid ""
"Customize the design of the :doc:`product pages <../ecommerce/"
"ecommerce_design/product_page>`, structure the :doc:`product catalog <../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>` and use :doc:`additional features <../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features>` to improve the customer's "
"shopping experience."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite obliko :doc:`strani izdelkov <../ecommerce/ecommerce_design/"
"product_page>`, strukturirajte :doc:`katalog izdelkov <../ecommerce/"
"ecommerce_design/catalog>` in uporabite :doc:`dodatne funkcije <../ecommerce/"
"ecommerce_design/additional_features>`, da izboljšate nakupovalno izkušnjo "
"stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:16
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:27
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:63
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:3
msgid "Product page"
msgstr "Stran izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:16
msgid ""
"Design the product pages by showcasing product details and additional "
"information, customizing product images and videos, and adding content and "
"design elements using building blocks."
msgstr ""
"Oblikujte strani izdelkov s predstavitvijo podrobnosti o izdelku in dodatnih "
"informacij, prilagajanjem slik in videoposnetkov izdelkov ter dodajanjem "
"vsebine in elementov oblikovanja z uporabo gradbenih blokov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:3
msgid "Product catalog"
msgstr "Katalog izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:23
msgid ""
"Organize the product catalog by customizing the layout, using categories, "
"and adding building blocks, and filtering options."
msgstr ""
"Organizirajte katalog izdelkov s prilagajanjem postavitve, uporabo kategorij "
"ter dodajanjem gradbenih blokov in možnosti filtriranja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:30
msgid ""
"Enable additional features, such as the wishlist and product comparison, and "
"highlight products using ribbons."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite dodatne funkcije, kot sta seznam želja in primerjava izdelkov, ter "
"poudarite izdelke z uporabo trakov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce provides additional features for online shops, including "
"a :ref:`product comparison <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"comparison>` tool, a :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"wishlists>`, and :ref:`product highlight options <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/product-highlight>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce zagotavlja dodatne funkcije za spletne trgovine, vključno z "
"orodjem za :ref:`primerjavo izdelkov <ecommerce/products/additional_features/"
"product-comparison>`, :ref:`seznamom želja <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` in :ref:`možnostmi označevanja izdelkov "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:13
msgid "Product comparison"
msgstr "Primerjava izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:15
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Add to compare`) button allows website "
"visitors to compare products based on their :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/attributes>`. Customers can click this button to select "
"the products they wish to compare, then click :guilabel:`Compare` in the pop-"
"up window at the bottom of the page to see the comparison summary."
msgstr ""
"Gumb :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Dodaj za primerjavo`) obiskovalcem "
"spletnega mesta omogoča primerjavo izdelkov glede na njihove :ref:`atribute "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>`. Stranke lahko kliknejo ta gumb, "
"da izberejo izdelke, ki jih želijo primerjati, nato pa "
"kliknejo :guilabel:`Primerjaj` v pojavnem oknu na dnu strani, da vidijo "
"povzetek primerjave."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:None
msgid "Product comparison window"
msgstr "Okno za primerjavo izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:59
msgid ""
"This button can be enabled independently in different sections of the "
"website:"
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb je mogoče omogočiti neodvisno v različnih razdelkih spletnega mesta:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:29
msgid ""
"Go to a product page, open the website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Products Details` section, and toggle "
"the :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` button. Once done, it becomes "
"available on each product page that has attributes."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na stran izdelka, odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta, pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Slog`, se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Podrobnosti "
"izdelkov` in preklopite gumb :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Primerjaj`. Ko "
"je to opravljeno, postane na voljo na vsaki strani izdelka, ki ima atribute."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:69
msgid "Catalog page"
msgstr "Stran kataloga"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:36
msgid ""
"To display the :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) button on "
"the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`, open the website "
"editor, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the :icon:`fa-paint-"
"brush` (:guilabel:`paint brush`) icon next to :guilabel:`Product Design`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Actions` section, toggle the :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Compare`) button, and choose between :guilabel:`Inline` "
"and :guilabel:`On Hover`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati gumb :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Primerjaj`) "
"na :ref:`strani trgovine <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`, odprite "
"urejevalnik spletnega mesta, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-paint-brush` (:guilabel:`čopič`) poleg :guilabel:`Oblika "
"izdelka`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Dejanja` preklopite gumb :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Primerjaj`) in izberite med :guilabel:`V vrstici` "
"in :guilabel:`Ob prehodu`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:44
msgid "You can only compare a maximum of four products at a time."
msgstr "Hkrati lahko primerjate največ štiri izdelke."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:47
msgid ""
"Define :ref:`attribute categories <ecommerce/categories_variants/attribute-"
"categories>` to group similar attributes under the same section when "
"comparing products."
msgstr ""
"Določite :ref:`kategorije atributov <ecommerce/categories_variants/attribute-"
"categories>`, da združite podobne atribute v isti razdelek pri primerjavi "
"izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:53
msgid "Wishlist"
msgstr "Seznam želja"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:55
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Add to wishlist`) button allows customers "
"to add products to their wishlist, i.e., save them for later. It is enabled "
"by default and available on each product page."
msgstr ""
"Gumb :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Dodaj na seznam želja`) strankam "
"omogoča, da dodajo izdelke na svoj seznam želja, tj. jih shranijo za "
"pozneje. Omogočen je privzeto in na voljo na vsaki strani izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:65
msgid ""
"Go to a product page, open the website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Products Details` section, and toggle "
"the :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Wishlist` button. Once done, it becomes "
"available on each product page."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na stran izdelka, odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta, pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Slog`, se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Podrobnosti "
"izdelkov` in preklopite gumb :icon:`fa-heart` :guilabel:`Seznam želja`. Ko "
"je to opravljeno, postane na voljo na vsaki strani izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:71
msgid ""
"To display the :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button on "
"the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`, open the website "
"editor, go to :guilabel:`Style`, and click the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` "
"(:guilabel:`paint brush`) icon next to :guilabel:`Product Design`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Actions` section, toggle the :icon:`fa-heart` "
"(:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button and choose between :guilabel:`Fixed` "
"and :guilabel:`Fixed - On Hover`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati gumb :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Seznam želja`) "
"na :ref:`strani trgovine <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`, odprite "
"urejevalnik spletnega mesta, pojdite v :guilabel:`Slog` in kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-paint-brush` (:guilabel:`čopič`) poleg :guilabel:`Oblika "
"izdelka`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Dejanja` preklopite gumb :icon:`fa-heart` "
"(:guilabel:`Seznam želja`) in izberite med :guilabel:`Pritrjeno` "
"in :guilabel:`Pritrjeno - ob prehodu`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:78
msgid "Header"
msgstr "Glava"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:80
msgid ""
"To display the :icon:`fa-heart` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) icon in the header, "
"open the website editor, click the header, navigate to the :guilabel:`Show/"
"Hide Elements` section, and toggle the :icon:`fa-heart` "
"(:guilabel:`Wishlist`) icon next to :guilabel:`Show Empty`. If it is not "
"enabled, the wishlist icon only appears when an item has been added to the "
"wishlist. The number of items in the wishlist is also displayed next to the "
"icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati ikono :icon:`fa-heart` (:guilabel:`Seznam želja`) v "
"glavi, odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta, kliknite glavo, se pomaknite do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Prikaži/skrij elemente` in preklopite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"heart` (:guilabel:`Seznam želja`) poleg :guilabel:`Prikaži prazno`. Če ni "
"omogočena, se ikona seznama želja prikaže šele, ko je bil na seznam dodan "
"izdelek. Število izdelkov na seznamu želja je prav tako prikazano poleg "
"ikone."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:87
msgid "Wishlist page"
msgstr "Stran z željo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:89
msgid ""
"It is possible to customize the layout of the :guilabel:`My Wishlist` page. "
"To do so, open the website editor while on the wishlist page, and in "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab under the :guilabel:`Wishlist Page` section, "
"choose a :guilabel:`Products Design`. Depending on the selected design, "
"adapt the layout according to :guilabel:`Desktop` or :guilabel:`Mobile` "
"devices. Click the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` (:guilabel:`paint brush`) icon "
"next to :guilabel:`Products Design` to access more customization options."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je prilagoditi postavitev strani :guilabel:`Moj seznam želja`. Za to "
"odprite urejevalnik spletnega mesta na strani seznama želja in v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Slog` v razdelku :guilabel:`Stran seznama želja` "
"izberite :guilabel:`Oblikovanje izdelkov`. Glede na izbrano oblikovanje "
"prilagodite postavitev za naprave :guilabel:`Namizje` "
"ali :guilabel:`Mobilnik`. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-paint-brush` "
"(:guilabel:`čopič`) poleg :guilabel:`Oblikovanje izdelkov` za dostop do več "
"možnosti prilagajanja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:97
msgid ""
"Customers can move products from their cart to their wishlist by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save for later` button in the :guilabel:`Order "
"summary` :ref:`checkout step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko premaknejo izdelke iz košarice na seznam želja s klikom na "
"gumb :guilabel:`Shrani za pozneje` v :guilabel:`Povzetek "
"naročila` :ref:`koraku blagajne <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:100
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`My Wishlist` page, customers can move products from their "
"wishlist to the cart."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Moj seznam želja` lahko stranke premaknejo izdelke s "
"seznama želja v košarico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:106
msgid "Product highlight"
msgstr "Poudarek izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:108
msgid ""
"The eCommerce app allows you to highlight products to increase their "
"visibility. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Product Ribbons`. You can either use one of the preconfigured ribbons "
"(:guilabel:`Sold out`, :guilabel:`Sale`, :guilabel:`Out of stock` "
"or :guilabel:`New!`) or create a :guilabel:`New` one. Add a ribbon name, and "
"select the method to :guilabel:`Assign` it:"
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija eCommerce vam omogoča, da označite izdelke za povečanje njihove "
"vidnosti. Za to pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> "
"Trakovi izdelkov`. Lahko uporabite enega od vnaprej konfiguriranih trakov "
"(:guilabel:`Razprodano`, :guilabel:`Akcija`, :guilabel:`Ni na zalogi` "
"ali :guilabel:`Novo!`) ali ustvarite :guilabel:`Novega`. Dodajte ime traku "
"in izberite metodo za :guilabel:`Dodelitev`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:114
msgid ":guilabel:`Manually`: assign the ribbon manually."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ročno`: dodelite trak ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Sale`: the ribbon is displayed when the product is on sale, "
"e.g., when using a :ref:`comparison price <ecommerce/prices/permanent-"
"discounts>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Na akciji`: trak se prikaže, ko je izdelek na akciji, npr. pri "
"uporabi :ref:`primerjalne cene <ecommerce/prices/permanent-discounts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`When New`: the ribbon is displayed when a new product is added. "
"Specify the number of :guilabel:`days after publication` it should be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ko je novo`: trak se prikaže, ko je dodan nov izdelek. Določite "
"število :guilabel:`dni po objavi`, ko naj bo prikazan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`when out of stock`: the ribbon is displayed when the product is "
"currently no longer available."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ko ni na zalogi`: trak se prikaže, ko izdelek trenutno ni več na "
"voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:122
msgid ""
"Choose its :guilabel:`Position`, either :guilabel:`Left` "
"or :guilabel:`Right`, and a :guilabel:`Style`, either :guilabel:`Ribbon` "
"or :guilabel:`Badge`. Define the :guilabel:`Text Color` and "
"the :guilabel:`Background Color`. Then :guilabel:`Save`. The ribbon is now "
"available for all the e-commerce products."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Položaj`, bodisi :guilabel:`Levo` ali :guilabel:`Desno`, "
"in :guilabel:`Slog`, bodisi :guilabel:`Trak` ali :guilabel:`Značka`. "
"Določite :guilabel:`Barvo besedila` in :guilabel:`Barvo ozadja`. "
"Nato :guilabel:`Shrani`. Trak je zdaj na voljo za vse izdelke spletne "
"trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:None
msgid "Product with badge"
msgstr "Izdelek z značko"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:131
msgid "There are other ways to create a new product ribbon:"
msgstr "Obstajajo drugi načini za ustvarjanje novega traku izdelka:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:133
msgid ""
"Access the product form, and under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, change or "
"create the ribbon in the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field."
msgstr ""
"Odprite obrazec izdelka in v zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja` spremenite ali "
"ustvarite trak v polju :guilabel:`Trak`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:135
msgid ""
"Edit/create ribbons from the :doc:`website editor <../../website/"
"web_design>`. To do so, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Product Details` section. Click the green :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`Create`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field or "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`Ribbon` label. The :guilabel:`Assign` feature is not "
"available for configuration in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Urejanje/ustvarjanje trakov iz :doc:`urejevalnika spletnega mesta <../../"
"website/web_design>`. Za to pojdite v zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in pojdite v "
"razdelek :guilabel:`Podrobnosti izdelka`. Kliknite zeleno ikono :icon:`fa-"
"plus` (:guilabel:`Ustvari`) poleg polja :guilabel:`Trak` ali ikono :icon:`fa-"
"pencil-square-o` (:guilabel:`Uredi`) poleg oznake :guilabel:`Trak`. "
"Funkcija :guilabel:`Dodelitev` ni na voljo za konfiguracijo v urejevalniku "
"spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:0
msgid "Create a new ribbon in the website editor"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novega traku v urejevalniku spletnega mesta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:145
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add ribbons for specific :ref:`product variants "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select a product. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button, choose a variant, and add a "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Variant Ribbon` field of the :guilabel:`Sales` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Trake je mogoče dodati tudi za določene :ref:`različice izdelkov <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/product-variants>`. To storite tako, da pojdete "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> e-trgovina --> Izdelki` in izberete "
"izdelek. Kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Različice`, izberite različico in "
"dodajte trak v polje :guilabel:`Trak različice` v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Prodaja`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:5
msgid ""
"The e-commerce catalog displays products for customers to browse. It is "
"organized using :ref:`product categories <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"categories>`, available :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/product-variants>`, sorting options, and navigation "
"paths. Essentially, the e-commerce catalog is the shop page of your website."
msgstr ""
"Katalog spletne trgovine prikazuje izdelke, ki jih lahko stranke brskajo. "
"Organiziran je z uporabo :ref:`kategorij izdelkov <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`, razpoložljivih :ref:`različic izdelkov "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`, možnosti razvrščanja in "
"navigacijskih poti. V bistvu je katalog spletne trgovine stran trgovine na "
"vašem spletnem mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:10
msgid ""
"The product catalog features a :ref:`toolbar and some filters <ecommerce/"
"catalog/toolbar-and-filters>` in the sidebar (or slide-out menu), along with "
"a dedicated :ref:`product listing area <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. "
"Additionally, the shop and category pages' :ref:`layout <ecommerce/catalog/"
"customize-layout>`, as well as the :ref:`e-commerce footer <ecommerce/"
"catalog/footer>`, can be customized, and you can add :ref:`building blocks "
"<ecommerce/catalog/catalog-blocks>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"Katalog izdelkov vsebuje :ref:`orodno vrstico in nekaj filtrov <ecommerce/"
"catalog/toolbar-and-filters>` v strnski vrstici (ali drsnem meniju) skupaj z "
"namens­kim :ref:`področjem za seznam izdelkov <ecommerce/catalog/product-"
"listing>`. Poleg tega je mogoče prilagoditi :ref:`postavitev <ecommerce/"
"catalog/customize-layout>` strani trgovine in kategorij ter :ref:`nogo "
"spletne trgovine <ecommerce/catalog/footer>`, po potrebi pa lahko dodate "
"tudi :ref:`gradnike <ecommerce/catalog/catalog-blocks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:17
msgid ""
"To customize the catalog, go to the shop page, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the "
"upper-right corner, select the section you want to change, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"Za prilagoditev kataloga pojdite na stran trgovine, v zgornjem desnem kotu "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi`, izberite razdelek, ki ga želite spremeniti, in "
"pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:23
msgid "Toolbar and filters"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica in filtri"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:25
msgid ""
"The toolbar and sidebar (or slide-out menu) provide advanced filtering tools "
"to help customers search and navigate the product catalog "
"using :ref:`categories <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` and :ref:`attributes "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica in stranska vrstica (ali drsni meni) zagotavljata napredna "
"orodja za filtriranje, ki strankam pomagajo iskati in krmariti po katalogu "
"izdelkov z uporabo :ref:`kategorij <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` "
"in :ref:`atributov <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you do not want to display a toolbar or sidebar, disable all related "
"options in the website editor, :ref:`hide attributes <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/attributes>`, and make sure to only assign one pricelist "
"to the website."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite prikazovati orodne vrstice ali stranske vrstice, onemogoči­te "
"vse povezane možnosti v urejevalniku spletnega mesta, :ref:`skrijte atribute "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>` in poskrbite, da spletn­emu mestu "
"dodelite samo en cenik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:37
msgid "Categories"
msgstr "Kategorije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:39
msgid ""
"To create a :ref:`category <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>` quick "
"access in the toolbar or general access in the sidebar, click "
"the :guilabel:`Top` and/or :guilabel:`Sidebar` button next "
"to :guilabel:`Categories`, and choose a :guilabel:`Style` for them. When "
"the :guilabel:`Sidebar` is selected, the option :guilabel:`Collapse Category "
"Recursive` appears, allowing you to collapse the category in the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje :ref:`kategorije <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>` "
"s hitrim dostopom v orodni vrstici ali splošnim dostopom v stranski vrstici "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Vrh` in/ali :guilabel:`Stranska vrstica` "
"poleg :guilabel:`Kategorije` ter izberite :guilabel:`Slog`. Ko je "
"izbrana :guilabel:`Stranska vrstica`, se prikaže "
"možnost :guilabel:`Rekurzivno strni kategorijo`, ki omogoča strnitev "
"kategorije v stranski vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:49
msgid ""
"The category filters located in the sidebar are not affected by "
"the :guilabel:`Filters` setting."
msgstr ""
"Filtri kategorij v stranski vrstici niso odvisni od "
"nastavitve :guilabel:`Filtri`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:54
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:56
msgid ""
"It is possible to display a search bar or sort-by options in the toolbar of "
"the shop page by clicking the :guilabel:`Sort By` and/or :guilabel:`Search` "
"buttons next to the :guilabel:`Toolbar` label. Toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Floating` switch on to always display the search bar, "
"the :ref:`pricelist selector <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` (if any), and "
"sort-by options at the bottom of the window, even when scrolling, and select "
"a :guilabel:`Default Sort` option."
msgstr ""
"V orodni vrstici strani trgovine je mogoče prikazati iskalno vrstico ali "
"možnosti razvrščanja s klikom na gumba :guilabel:`Razvrsti po` in/"
"ali :guilabel:`Iskanje` poleg oznake :guilabel:`Orodna vrstica`. Vklopite "
"stikalo :guilabel:`Plavajoče`, da bodo iskalna vrstica, :ref:`izbirnik "
"cenika <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` (če obstaja) in možnosti razvrščanja "
"vedno prikazani na dnu okna tudi med pomikanjem, ter izberite "
"možnost :guilabel:`Privzeto razvrščanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:63
msgid ""
"The default sort applies to *all* :ref:`categories <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto razvrščanje velja za *vse* :ref:`kategorije <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:68
msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Filtri"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:70
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Filters` field to:"
msgstr "Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Filtri` na:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Sidebar`: to display filters in the side panel;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stranska vrstica`: za prikaz filtrov v stranskem panelu;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Off-screen menu`: to display filters in a slide-out menu that "
"opens when clicking the :icon:`fa-sliders` :guilabel:`Filters` button in the "
"toolbar;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izvlečni meni`: za prikaz filtrov v izvlečnem meniju, ki se odpre "
"s klikom na gumb :icon:`fa-sliders` :guilabel:`Filtri` v orodni vrstici;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:75
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide`: to hide filters entirely."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skrij`: za popolno skritje filtrov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:77
msgid "By default, two :guilabel:`Filters` are enabled:"
msgstr "Privzeto sta omogočena dva :guilabel:`filtra`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price`: Use the switch to display a :guilabel:`Price Range` bar, "
"which allows customers to filter products according to a specific price "
"range by dragging adjustable handles."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cena`: uporabite stikalo za prikaz vrstice :guilabel:`Cenovni "
"razpon`, ki strankam omogoča filtriranje izdelkov glede na določen cenovni "
"razpon z vlečenjem nastavljivih ročic."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Toggle the switch to display product :guilabel:`Tags` on "
"the shop page, and allow customers to filter products using those tags by "
"going to the :guilabel:`Tags` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oznake`: vklopite stikalo za prikaz :guilabel:`oznak` izdelkov na "
"strani trgovine in omogočite strankam filtriranje izdelkov s temi oznakami "
"tako, da greste v razdelek :guilabel:`Oznake`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:87
msgid ""
"To create product tags on your e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Product Tags`, and click :guilabel:`New`. Add "
"a :guilabel:`Tag` name, toggle the :guilabel:`Visible to customers` switch, "
"and select a :guilabel:`Color`. Optionally, add an image. Then go to the "
"product form, and assign the relevant tags where needed."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje oznak izdelkov v vaši spletni trgovini pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> eCommerce --> Oznake izdelkov` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Dodajte ime :guilabel:`oznake`, vklopite "
"stikalo :guilabel:`Vidno strankam` in izberite :guilabel:`barvo`. Po želji "
"dodajte sliko. Nato odprite obrazec izdelka in kjer je potrebno dodelite "
"ustrezne oznake."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:92
msgid ""
"For :doc:`rental products <../../../sales/rental>`, you can also add "
"a :guilabel:`Rental Date` option to display a date range calendar to check "
"their availability over a specific period."
msgstr ""
"Za :doc:`najemne izdelke <../../../sales/rental>` lahko dodate tudi "
"možnost :guilabel:`Datum najema`, ki prikaže koledar z razponom datumov za "
"preverjanje njihove razpoložljivosti v določenem obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:100
msgid ""
"When you offer :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-"
"variants>` with different :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>`, those options appear in the sidebar or slide-out menu when "
"filters are shown. The menu automatically adapts to the number of attribute "
"sections:"
msgstr ""
"Ko ponujate :ref:`različice izdelkov <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-"
"variants>` z različnimi :ref:`atributi <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>`, se te možnosti prikažejo v stranski vrstici ali izvlečnem "
"meniju, ko so prikazani filtri. Meni se samodejno prilagodi številu "
"razdelkov atributov:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:105
msgid "**Up to 4 attributes**: all the attribute values are displayed."
msgstr "**Do 4 atribute**: prikazane so vse vrednosti atributov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:106
msgid "**More than 4 attributes**: the sections are automatically collapsed."
msgstr "**Več kot 4 atribute**: razdelki so samodejno strnjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:109
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Radio` and :guilabel:`Select` :ref:`display types <products/"
"variants/attributes>`, a :guilabel:`View More` button appears when there are "
"more than **8** values, and a search field when the number of values exceeds "
"**20**."
msgstr ""
"Za :guilabel:`Radio` in :guilabel:`Select` :ref:`vrste prikaza <products/"
"variants/attributes>` se prikaže gumb :guilabel:`Prikaži več`, ko je "
"vrednosti več kot **8**, in iskalno polje, ko število vrednosti presega "
"**20**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:112
msgid ""
"At least two attribute values are required for the filter to be visible."
msgstr "Za vidnost filtra sta potrebni vsaj dve vrednosti atributa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:113
msgid ""
"The attribute filters located in the sidebar or slide-out menu are affected "
"by the :guilabel:`Filters` setting."
msgstr ""
"Na filtre atributov, ki se nahajajo v stranski vrstici ali drsnem meniju, "
"vpliva nastavitev :guilabel:`Filtri`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:117
msgid ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:118
msgid ":doc:`../../ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:123
msgid "Product listing area"
msgstr "Območje seznama izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:127
msgid ""
"Define the number of products to display on your shop pages by configuring "
"the :guilabel:`Size` displayed per page and line, and specify the number of "
"columns for :guilabel:`Mobile` devices."
msgstr ""
"Določite število izdelkov, ki naj bodo prikazani na straneh vaše trgovine, "
"tako da konfigurirate :guilabel:`Velikost`, prikazano na stran in vrstico, "
"ter določite število stolpcev za :guilabel:`Mobilne` naprave."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:131
msgid ""
"The number of products displayed on a page may affect performance and page "
"loading speed."
msgstr ""
"Število izdelkov, prikazanih na strani, lahko vpliva na zmogljivost in "
"hitrost nalaganja strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:133
msgid ""
"In addition, you can manually change a product’s position on the shop page "
"or product category page. To do so, click a specific product, change "
"its :guilabel:`Size`, and :guilabel:`Re-order` it using the arrows in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` section of the :guilabel:`Style` tab. The :icon:`fa-"
"angle-double-left` (:guilabel:`double left arrow`) and :icon:`fa-angle-"
"double-right` (:guilabel:`double right arrow`) buttons allow you to move the "
"product to the extreme left or right, and the :icon:`fa-angle-left` "
"(:guilabel:`single left arrow`) and :icon:`fa-angle-right` "
"(:guilabel:`single right arrow`) buttons allow you to move it one row to the "
"left or right. You can also choose or create a :ref:`ribbon or badge "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>` to highlight a "
"specific product."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko ročno spremenite položaj izdelka na strani trgovine ali "
"strani kategorije izdelkov. To storite tako, da kliknete določen izdelek, "
"spremenite njegovo :guilabel:`Velikost` in ga :guilabel:`Preuredite` s "
"puščicami v razdelku :guilabel:`Izdelek` zavihka :guilabel:`Slog`. "
"Gumba :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` (:guilabel:`dvojna leva puščica`) "
"in :icon:`fa-angle-double-right` (:guilabel:`dvojna desna puščica`) vam "
"omogočata premik izdelka popolnoma na levo ali desno, gumba :icon:`fa-angle-"
"left` (:guilabel:`enojná leva puščica`) in :icon:`fa-angle-right` "
"(:guilabel:`enojna desna puščica`) pa vam omogočata premik za eno vrstico na "
"levo ali desno. Izberete ali ustvarite lahko tudi :ref:`trak ali značko "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>`, da poudarite "
"določen izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:144
msgid ""
"It is also possible to change the products' positions on the shop page by "
"going to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, switching to "
"the list view, and dragging and dropping the products within the list."
msgstr ""
"Pozicije izdelkov na strani trgovine je mogoče spremeniti tudi tako, da "
"greste na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> e-Trgovina --> Izdelki`, "
"preklopite na pogled seznama in povlečete ter spustite izdelke znotraj "
"seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:151
msgid "Product card design"
msgstr "Oblikovanje kartice izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:153
msgid ""
"To customize the product cards' design, choose a :guilabel:`Products "
"Design`, click the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` :guilabel:`(paint brush)` icon "
"next to it to:"
msgstr ""
"Za prilagoditev oblikovanja kartic izdelkov izberite :guilabel:`Oblikovanje "
"izdelkov`, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-paint-brush` :guilabel:`(čopič)` poleg "
"nje za:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:156
msgid "Choose a :guilabel:`Preset` layout;"
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Vnaprej nastavljeno` postavitev;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:157
msgid "Adapt the :guilabel:`General` design;"
msgstr "Prilagodite :guilabel:`Splošno` oblikovanje;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:158
msgid ""
"Customize the :guilabel:`Text & content` (e.g., show "
"a :guilabel:`Description`, and :guilabel:`Ratings`);"
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite :guilabel:`Besedilo in vsebino` (npr. prikažite :guilabel:`Opis` "
"in :guilabel:`Ocene`);"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:160
msgid ""
"Customize the :guilabel:`Images`' layout (e.g., enable :guilabel:`Secondary "
"Image` to show a second image when hovering over the product image on the "
"shop or category page);"
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite postavitev :guilabel:`Slik` (npr. "
"omogočite :guilabel:`Sekundarno sliko`, da se pri lebdenju nad sliko izdelka "
"na strani trgovine ali kategorije prikaže druga slika);"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:162
msgid ""
"Enable some :guilabel:`Actions` (e.g., :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` :ref:`Add to "
"cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>`, :icon:`fa-exchange` :ref:`Compare "
"<ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-comparison>`, or :icon:`fa-"
"heart` :ref:`Wishlist <ecommerce/products/additional_features/wishlists>`) "
"and customize their placement."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite nekatera :guilabel:`Dejanja` (npr. :icon:`fa-shopping-"
"cart` :ref:`Dodaj v košarico <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>`, :icon:`fa-"
"exchange` :ref:`Primerjaj <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-"
"comparison>` ali :icon:`fa-heart` :ref:`Seznam želja <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>`) in prilagodite njihovo umestitev."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:168
msgid ""
"You can also add a :ref:`variant picture <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>` on the product card."
msgstr ""
"Na kartico izdelka lahko dodate tudi :ref:`sliko različice <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:174
msgid "Shop and category page design"
msgstr "Oblikovanje strani trgovine in kategorije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:176
msgid ""
"The design of the shop and individual category pages can be customized as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"Oblikovanje strani trgovine in posameznih kategorij je mogoče prilagoditi na "
"naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:178
msgid ""
"Choose whether the :guilabel:`Content Width` of the shop and category pages "
"should be :guilabel:`Regular` or :guilabel:`Full` width."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, ali naj bo :guilabel:`Širina vsebine` strani trgovine in "
"kategorij :guilabel:`Običajna` ali :guilabel:`Polna`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:180
msgid ""
"Define the headers: navigate to the relevant page, then change the header "
"directly on the page if needed. Toggle the :guilabel:`Show Title` and/or "
"the :guilabel:`Center Content` switches. For product category pages, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Show Description` switch to show the :ref:`category "
"description <ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Določite glave: pomaknite se na ustrezno stran in nato po potrebi spremenite "
"glavo neposredno na strani. Preklopite stikali :guilabel:`Prikaži naslov` in/"
"ali :guilabel:`Centriraj vsebino`. Za strani kategorij izdelkov preklopite "
"stikalo :guilabel:`Prikaži opis`, da prikažete :ref:`opis kategorije "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:184
msgid ""
"Use :doc:`building blocks <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>` to add "
"content in the top/bottom section of the page, either for the entire shop "
"page or for a specific category. In the latter case, the block appears "
"*only* when filtering by that category. To do so, move the block to the far "
"top or bottom section to display it on the general shop page or to the area "
"below the category's name at the top or beneath the product list to display "
"it only when filtering by that specific category."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :doc:`gradnike <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>`, da "
"dodate vsebino v zgornji/spodnji del strani, bodisi za celotno stran "
"trgovine bodisi za določeno kategorijo. V slednjem primeru se blok prikaže "
"*samo* pri filtriranju po tej kategoriji. To storite tako, da premaknete "
"blok popolnoma na vrh ali dno, da se prikaže na splošni strani trgovine, ali "
"na območje pod imenom kategorije na vrhu ali pod seznamom izdelkov, da se "
"prikaže samo pri filtriranju po tej določeni kategoriji."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:0
msgid "Place building block in the header or footer."
msgstr "Postavite gradbeni blok v glavo ali nogo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:195
msgid ""
"Adding content to an e-commerce category page helps improve the :doc:`SEO "
"<../../website/structure/seo>` strategy. Using keywords linked to the "
"products or the e-commerce categories can also increase organic traffic. "
"Additionally, each category has its own specific URL that can be pointed to "
"and is indexed by search engines."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje vsebine na stran kategorije e-trgovine pomaga izboljšati "
"strategijo :doc:`SEO <../../website/structure/seo>`. Uporaba ključnih besed, "
"povezanih z izdelki ali kategorijami e-trgovine, lahko prav tako poveča "
"organski promet. Poleg tega ima vsaka kategorija svoj specifični URL, na "
"katerega je mogoče kazati in ga indeksirajo iskalniki."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:199
msgid ""
"E-commerce categories can also be added as :ref:`mega menu items <website/"
"header_footer/mega-menus>` for quick access."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije e-trgovine je mogoče dodati tudi kot :ref:`elemente mega menija "
"<website/header_footer/mega-menus>` za hiter dostop."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:201
msgid ""
"It is also possible to customize individual :doc:`product pages "
"<product_page>`."
msgstr ""
"Možno je tudi prilagoditi posamezne :doc:`strani izdelkov <product_page>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:206
msgid "Catalog blocks"
msgstr "Bloki kataloga"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:208
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Catalog` :doc:`building blocks </applications/websites/"
"website/web_design/building_blocks>` can be used, for example, to create "
"quick access to the shop page, showcase specific product categories, "
"highlight a specific product selection, or add a banner with general "
"information or promotions."
msgstr ""
"Gradbeni elementi :guilabel:`Katalog` :doc:`building blocks </applications/"
"websites/website/web_design/building_blocks>` se lahko na primer uporabijo "
"za ustvarjanje hitrega dostopa do strani trgovine, predstavitev določenih "
"kategorij izdelkov, poudarjanje specifične izbire izdelkov ali dodajanje "
"pasice s splošnimi informacijami ali promocijami."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:213
msgid ""
"Depending on the selected template, you can :ref:`customize <website/"
"building_blocks/edit>` the blocks in the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od izbrane predloge lahko :ref:`prilagodite <website/building_blocks/"
"edit>` bloke v zavihku :guilabel:`Slog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:0
msgid "Example of a catalog block for specific products"
msgstr "Primer kataloškega bloka za specifične izdelke"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:220
msgid ""
"For example, this specific :guilabel:`Catalog` block template displays a "
"selection of products and can be customized to:"
msgstr ""
"Na primer, ta specifični blok predloge :guilabel:`Katalog` prikazuje izbiro "
"izdelkov in ga je mogoče prilagoditi za:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:223
msgid "Adapt the block's design."
msgstr "Prilagoditev oblikovanja bloka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:224
msgid ""
"Select a :guilabel:`Cards Design`, and :ref:`configure <ecommerce/catalog/"
"products-design>` it using the :icon:`fa-paint-brush` :guilabel:`(paint "
"brush)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Obliko kartic` in jo :ref:`konfigurirajte <ecommerce/"
"catalog/products-design>` z uporabo ikone :icon:`fa-paint-"
"brush` :guilabel:`(čopič)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:226
msgid ""
"Define which items are shown in the block by selecting the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Filter` option, e.g., :guilabel:`Newest Products` to "
"show the latest arrivals."
msgstr ""
"Določite, kateri elementi so prikazani v bloku, tako da izberete ustrezno "
"možnost :guilabel:`Filter`, npr. :guilabel:`Najnovejši izdelki` za prikaz "
"zadnjih prispelih izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:228
msgid ""
"Select a specific product category in the :guilabel:`Category` dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"Izberite določeno kategorijo izdelka v spustnem "
"seznamu :guilabel:`Kategorija`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:229
msgid ""
"Filter products by toggling the :guilabel:`Tags` and/or :guilabel:`Show "
"variants` options."
msgstr ""
"Filtrirajte izdelke tako, da vklopite možnosti :guilabel:`Oznake` in/"
"ali :guilabel:`Prikaži različice`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:234
msgid "E-commerce-specific website footer"
msgstr "Noga spletne strani, specifična za e-trgovino"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:236
msgid ""
"The :ref:`website footer <website/header_footer/footer-design>` can also be "
"configured to use the e-commerce-specific template. Then, add the "
"relevant :ref:`links <website/elements/links>`, and adapt the footer's text "
"and layout as needed in the website editor. The :doc:`available payment "
"methods </applications/finance/payment_providers>` are also shown in this "
"footer. To adapt their display, go to the :guilabel:`Supported Payment "
"Methods` section in the website editor."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Noga spletne strani <website/header_footer/footer-design>` je lahko "
"prav tako konfigurirana za uporabo predloge, specifične za e-trgovino. Nato "
"dodajte ustrezne :ref:`povezave <website/elements/links>` in prilagodite "
"besedilo in postavitev noge po potrebi v urejevalniku spletne strani. V tej "
"nogi so prikazani tudi :doc:`razpoložljivi načini plačila </applications/"
"finance/payment_providers>`. Za prilagoditev njihovega prikaza pojdite na "
"razdelek :guilabel:`Podprti načini plačila` v urejevalniku spletne strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog.rst:243
msgid "It is not possible to create a customized footer per category."
msgstr "Ni mogoče ustvariti prilagojene noge za posamezno kategorijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:5
msgid ""
"The e-commerce product pages showcase all product details and media items "
"related to the relevant products. It is possible to customize "
"the :ref:`images and videos section <ecommerce/product_page/image-"
"customization>`, choose :ref:`which product information to display "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/customization>`, show specific :ref:`buttons "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/buttons>`, customize the :ref:`attribute "
"details section <ecommerce_design/product_page/attributes>`, "
"enable :ref:`additional organizational features <ecommerce_design/"
"product_page/page-features>`, and add content using :ref:`building blocks "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/building_blocks>`."
msgstr ""
"Strani izdelkov e-trgovine prikazujejo vse podrobnosti in medijske elemente, "
"povezane z ustreznimi izdelki. Možno je prilagoditi :ref:`razdelek slik in "
"videoposnetkov <ecommerce/product_page/image-customization>`, "
"izbrati :ref:`katere informacije o izdelku prikazati <ecommerce_design/"
"product_page/customization>`, prikazati določene :ref:`gumbe "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/buttons>`, prilagoditi :ref:`razdelek s "
"podrobnostmi atributov <ecommerce_design/product_page/attributes>`, "
"omogočiti :ref:`dodatne organizacijske funkcije <ecommerce_design/"
"product_page/page-features>` in dodati vsebino z uporabo :ref:`gradnikov "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/building_blocks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:19
msgid ""
"After :ref:`adding media items on the product form <ecommerce/products/"
"images>` or upon :ref:`product creation in the frontend <ecommerce/products/"
"product-creation>`, customize them on the frontend product pages. To do so, "
"navigate to the relevant product page in the online shop, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"Po :ref:`dodajanju medijskih elementov na obrazec izdelka <ecommerce/"
"products/images>` ali ob :ref:`ustvarjanju izdelka v uporabniškem vmesniku "
"<ecommerce/products/product-creation>` jih prilagodite na straneh izdelka v "
"uporabniškem vmesniku. To storite tako, da se pomaknete na ustrezno stran "
"izdelka v spletni trgovini, kliknete :guilabel:`Uredi` v zgornjem desnem "
"kotu in odprete zavihek :guilabel:`Slog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:25
msgid ""
"To access the relevant product page from the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` in the backend, click the :icon:`fa-"
"globe` :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button at the top of the form."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do ustrezne strani izdelka iz :ref:`obrazca izdelka <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` v zalednem sistemu kliknite pametni gumb :icon:`fa-"
"globe` :guilabel:`Pojdi na spletno mesto` na vrhu obrazca."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:29
msgid ""
"To manage individual media items, click the item on the product page and "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Image` section of the website editor. You can "
"then :guilabel:`Replace` or :guilabel:`Remove` the image or video "
"and :guilabel:`Re-order` the items. Use the :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` "
"(:guilabel:`left double arrow`) or :icon:`fa-angle-double-right` "
"(:guilabel:`right double arrow`) to move the media to the first or last "
"position, and the :icon:`fa-angle-left` (:guilabel:`left arrow`) "
"or :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`right arrow`) to move them by one "
"position."
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje posameznih medijskih elementov kliknite element na strani "
"izdelka in se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Slika` urejevalnika spletnega "
"mesta. Nato lahko :guilabel:`Zamenjate` ali :guilabel:`Odstranite` sliko ali "
"videoposnetek in :guilabel:`Preuredite` elemente. Uporabite :icon:`fa-angle-"
"double-left` (:guilabel:`dvojna puščica levo`) ali :icon:`fa-angle-double-"
"right` (:guilabel:`dvojna puščica desno`) za premik medija na prvo ali "
"zadnje mesto ter :icon:`fa-angle-left` (:guilabel:`puščica levo`) "
"ali :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`puščica desno`) za premik za eno "
"mesto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:37
msgid ""
"To adjust the layout of the images and videos section, go "
"to :guilabel:`Images Area` and define the images' size "
"and :guilabel:`Position`. Then, navigate to the :guilabel:`Images` section, "
"and use the following options to customize this section:"
msgstr ""
"Za prilagoditev postavitve razdelka slik in videoposnetkov pojdite "
"na :guilabel:`Območje slik` in določite velikost slik "
"ter :guilabel:`Položaj`. Nato se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Slike` in "
"uporabite naslednje možnosti za prilagoditev tega razdelka:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Main image`: Click :guilabel:`Replace` to change the main product "
"image."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Glavna slika`: kliknite :guilabel:`Zamenjaj` za spremembo glavne "
"slike izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:44
msgid "It is not possible to use a video as the main media item."
msgstr "Videoposnetka ni mogoče uporabiti kot glavnega medijskega elementa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Media`: :guilabel:`Add More` images or videos (including "
"via URL) or :guilabel:`Remove all` media items."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodatni mediji`: :guilabel:`Dodajte več` slik ali videoposnetkov "
"(tudi prek URL-ja) ali :guilabel:`Odstranite vse` medijske elemente."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Display`: Choose between the following layouts when you use more "
"than one media item:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prikaz`: izberite med naslednjimi postavitvami, ko uporabljate "
"več kot en medijski element:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Carousel`: This option allows visitors to navigate from one image "
"to the next using the :icon:`fa-angle-left` (:guilabel:`left arrow`) "
"or :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`right arrow`). "
"Show :guilabel:`Thumbnails` on the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-left` "
"(:guilabel:`Left`) or at the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Bottom`) "
"and adapt the corner :guilabel:`Roundness` of the images."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrtiljak`: ta možnost obiskovalcem omogoča premikanje od ene "
"slike do naslednje z uporabo :icon:`fa-angle-left` (:guilabel:`puščica "
"levo`) ali :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`puščica desno`). "
"Prikažite :guilabel:`Sličice` na :icon:`fa-long-arrow-left` "
"(:guilabel:`Levo`) ali pri :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Spodaj`) "
"in prilagodite :guilabel:`Zaobljenost` kotov slik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Grid`: This layout displays media items in a square layout. "
"Adjust the number of :guilabel:`Columns` and define the :guilabel:`Spacing` "
"between the images in the grid, if necessary."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mreža`: ta postavitev prikazuje medijske elemente v kvadratni "
"postavitvi. Po potrebi prilagodite število :guilabel:`Stolpcev` in "
"določite :guilabel:`Razmik` med slikami v mreži."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto-crop`: Choose a size to cut/trim images to match the page "
"layout. This is useful when designing the :guilabel:`Mobile` :ref:`layout "
"<website/visibility/mobile-and-computer>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samodejno obrezovanje`: izberite velikost za rezanje/prirezovanje "
"slik, da se ujemajo s postavitvijo strani. To je uporabno pri "
"oblikovanju :guilabel:`mobilne` :ref:`postavitve <website/visibility/mobile-"
"and-computer>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:62
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Zoom on click`: Enable image zoom when visitors click an image."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Povečava ob kliku`: omogočite povečavo slike, ko obiskovalci "
"kliknejo sliko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:67
msgid "Page layout and product information display"
msgstr "Postavitev strani in prikaz informacij o izdelku"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:69
msgid ""
"To customize the layout of the product pages, access any product page, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, and navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab. Then, go to the :guilabel:`Page Width` setting "
"and choose either the :guilabel:`Regular` or :guilabel:`Full-width` option."
msgstr ""
"Za prilagoditev postavitve strani izdelkov odprite katero koli stran "
"izdelka, kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` v zgornjem desnem kotu in se pomaknite "
"do zavihka :guilabel:`Slog`. Nato pojdite na nastavitev :guilabel:`Širina "
"strani` in izberite možnost :guilabel:`Običajno` ali :guilabel:`Celotna "
"širina`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:74
msgid ""
"You can choose a different width for the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/"
"customize-layout>`."
msgstr ""
"Za :ref:`stran trgovine <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>` lahko izberete "
"drugačno širino."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:76
msgid ""
"Select which product information appears on product pages using the options "
"available in the :guilabel:`Product Details` section. You can "
"configure :ref:`buttons <ecommerce_design/product_page/buttons>`, "
"define :ref:`how attributes are displayed <ecommerce_design/product_page/"
"attributes>`, organize the page using :ref:`page customization features "
"<ecommerce_design/product_page/page-features>`, and add content "
"using :ref:`building blocks <ecommerce_design/product_page/building_blocks>`."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, katere informacije o izdelku se prikazujejo na straneh izdelkov z "
"uporabo možnosti, ki so na voljo v razdelku :guilabel:`Podrobnosti o "
"izdelku`. Lahko konfigurirate :ref:`gumbe <ecommerce_design/product_page/"
"buttons>`, določite :ref:`kako so prikazani atributi <ecommerce_design/"
"product_page/attributes>`, organizirate stran z uporabo :ref:`funkcij "
"prilagajanja strani <ecommerce_design/product_page/page-features>` in dodate "
"vsebino z uporabo :ref:`gradnikov <ecommerce_design/product_page/"
"building_blocks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:44
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:163
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:88
msgid ""
"Customize the buttons displayed on product pages using the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite gumbe, prikazane na straneh izdelkov, z naslednjimi možnostmi:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:90
msgid ":guilabel:`Purchase Style`: Define the layout of the buttons."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Slog nakupa`: določite postavitev gumbov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Purchase Options`: (De)activate the :ref:`Buy Now <ecommerce/"
"checkout/buy-now>` button and/or the :guilabel:`Quantity` selector."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Možnosti nakupa`: (de)aktivirajte gumb :ref:`Kupi zdaj <ecommerce/"
"checkout/buy-now>` in/ali izbirnik :guilabel:`Količina`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Actions`: Enable the :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` and the :ref:`product comparison <ecommerce/"
"products/additional_features/product-comparison>` features."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dejanja`: Omogoči funkciji :ref:`seznam želja <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` in :ref:`primerjava izdelkov <ecommerce/"
"products/additional_features/product-comparison>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:102
msgid ""
"Choose how product :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"attributes>` are displayed in the :guilabel:`Specification` section of the "
"product page:"
msgstr ""
"Izberi, kako so :ref:`atributi <ecommerce/categories_variants/attributes>` "
"izdelka prikazani v razdelku :guilabel:`Specifikacija` na strani izdelka:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:105
msgid ":guilabel:`None`: Do not show the details."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Brez`: Ne prikazuj podrobnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:106
msgid ":guilabel:`Bottom of Page`: Show the details at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Na dnu strani`: Prikaži podrobnosti na dnu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`In accordion`: Show a foldable table directly under the ordering "
"options."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`V harmoniki`: Prikaži zložljivo tabelo neposredno pod možnostmi "
"naročanja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:110
msgid ""
"The specification section is only displayed when :ref:`product variants "
"<ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>` are enabled, and at least "
"one attribute has been defined for the product."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek s specifikacijami je prikazan samo, ko so omogočene :ref:`različice "
"izdelkov <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>` in je za izdelek "
"opredeljen vsaj en atribut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:115
msgid ""
"Create :ref:`attribute categories <ecommerce/categories_variants/attribute-"
"categories>` to better structure this section."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari :ref:`kategorije atributov <ecommerce/categories_variants/attribute-"
"categories>`, da boš bolje strukturiral ta razdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:117
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Image` :ref:`attribute display type <products/variants/"
"attributes>` to show images of product variants on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi :guilabel:`Slika` :ref:`tip prikaza atributa <products/variants/"
"attributes>`, da prikažeš slike različic izdelkov na strani izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:123
msgid "Page organization options and additional features"
msgstr "Možnosti organizacije strani in dodatne funkcije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:125
msgid ""
"Toggle the following options on/off to enable or disable features across all "
"product pages:"
msgstr ""
"Vklopi ali izklopi naslednje možnosti, da omogočiš ali onemogoči funkcije na "
"vseh straneh izdelkov:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:127
msgid ":guilabel:`Separators`: Organize the page and improve visual clarity."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ločila`: Organiziraj stran in izboljšaj vidno jasnost."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Indication`: Indicate whether the price is :ref:`VAT included "
"or excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Navedba davka`: Navedi, ali je cena :ref:`z vključenim ali "
"izključenim DDV <ecommerce/prices/taxes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Display the tags created in the :ref:`backend <ecommerce/"
"catalog/filters>` on product pages and enable customers to filter products "
"by those tags."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oznake`: Prikaži oznake, ustvarjene v :ref:`zaledju <ecommerce/"
"catalog/filters>`, na straneh izdelkov in omogoči strankam filtriranje "
"izdelkov po teh oznakah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Terms and Conditions`: Display a link to your :doc:`terms and "
"conditions </applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"terms_conditions>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pogoji poslovanja`: Prikaži povezavo do tvojih :doc:`pogojev "
"poslovanja </applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"terms_conditions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reviews`: Allow :doc:`logged-in portal users </applications/"
"general/users/user_portals>` to submit product reviews. To add a review, "
"users must navigate to the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` section at the "
"bottom of the page and click the :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`plus`) icon. "
"They can then select a rating using the :icon:`fa-star-o` (:guilabel:`star`) "
"icons and leave a comment. The :icon:`fa-star` (:guilabel:`star`) rating is "
"displayed directly under the product name."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ocene`: Dovoli :doc:`prijavljenim uporabnikom portala </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>`, da oddajo ocene izdelkov. Če "
"želijo dodati oceno, morajo uporabniki poiskati razdelek :guilabel:`Ocene "
"strank` na dnu strani in klikniti ikono :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`plus`). "
"Nato lahko izberejo oceno z ikonami :icon:`fa-star-o` (:guilabel:`zvezdica`) "
"in pustijo komentar. Ocena :icon:`fa-star` (:guilabel:`zvezdica`) je "
"prikazana neposredno pod imenom izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Search Bar`: Display a search bar that can be shown or hidden "
"independently from the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/toolbar>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Iskalna vrstica`: Prikaži iskalno vrstico, ki jo je mogoče "
"prikazati ali skriti neodvisno od :ref:`strani trgovine <ecommerce/catalog/"
"toolbar>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:142
msgid ""
":ref:`Ribbon <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>` (or "
"badge): Highlight a specific product."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Trak <ecommerce/products/additional_features/product-highlight>` (ali "
"značka): Označi določen izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:146
msgid ""
"It is possible to enable additional features and display information "
"previously configured in the backend:"
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je omogočiti dodatne funkcije in prikazati informacije, ki so bile "
"predhodno konfigurirane v zaledju:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:149
msgid ""
":ref:`Click & Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`: Show the order "
"pick-up location and delivery availability on the product page, and allow "
"customers to select the desired pick-up point."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Click & Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`: Prikažite "
"lokacijo prevzema naročila in razpoložljivost dostave na strani izdelka ter "
"dovolite strankam, da izberejo želeno prevzemno točko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:152
msgid ""
":ref:`Description <ecommerce/products/description>`: Display an e-commerce-"
"specific product description right under the product name."
msgstr ""
