msgstr ":doc:`../website/structure/seo`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:17
msgid "Data monitoring"
msgstr "Spremljanje podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:19
msgid ""
"The eCommerce reporting view allows you to monitor and analyze the "
"performance of your online sales. To access it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Reporting --> eCommerce`. "
"The :guilabel:`eCommerce Dashboard` helps monitor everything related to the "
"online shop, e.g., sales performance by product or category. By default, the "
"graph shows data for :guilabel:`Confirmed Orders` and the current month."
msgstr ""
"Pogled poročanja o e-trgovini vam omogoča spremljanje in analizo uspešnosti "
"vaše spletne prodaje. Za dostop pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> "
"Poročanje --> eCommerce`. :guilabel:`Nadzorna plošča eCommerce` pomaga "
"spremljati vse, kar je povezano s spletno trgovino, npr. uspešnost prodaje "
"po izdelku ali kategoriji. Privzeto graf prikazuje podatke "
"za :guilabel:`Potrjena naročila` in tekoči mesec."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Measures` :icon:`fa-caret-down` button to select the "
"metric to analyze, such as :guilabel:`Discount %`, :guilabel:`Qty "
"Invoiced`, :guilabel:`Untaxed Total` (default), or :guilabel:`Volume`. You "
"can also switch between :ref:`pivot <studio/views/reporting/pivot>` "
"and :ref:`graph <studio/views/reporting/graph>` views, and create a "
"spreadsheet by clicking :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Mere` :icon:`fa-caret-down`, da izberete metriko za "
"analizo, kot je :guilabel:`Popust %`, :guilabel:`Količina na "
"računu`, :guilabel:`Neobdavčen seštevek` (privzeto) ali :guilabel:`Obseg`. "
"Preklapljate lahko tudi med pogledi :ref:`pivot <studio/views/reporting/"
"pivot>` in :ref:`graf <studio/views/reporting/graph>` ter ustvarite "
"preglednico s klikom na :guilabel:`Vstavi v preglednico`."

