#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:213
msgid ""
"Track all karma-related activity and add or remove karma manually "
"by :ref:`enabling developer mode <developer-mode>` and going "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Gamification Tools --> Karma Tracking`."
msgstr ""
"Sledite vsem dejavnostim, povezanim s karmo, in ročno dodajte ali odstranite "
"karmo tako, da :ref:`omogočite način za razvijalce <developer-mode>` in "
"greste na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Orodja za igrifikacijo --> Sledenje "
"karmi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:220
msgid "Gamification"
msgstr "Igrificiranje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:222
msgid ""
"Ranks and badges can be used to encourage participation. Ranks are based on "
"the total :ref:`karma points <forum/karma>`, while badges can be granted "
"manually or automatically by completing challenges."
msgstr ""
"Rang in značke je mogoče uporabiti za spodbujanje sodelovanja. Rangi "
"temeljijo na skupnih :ref:`točkah karme <forum/karma>`, medtem ko se značke "
"lahko podelijo ročno ali samodejno z dokončanjem izzivov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:229
msgid "Ranks"
msgstr "Ranki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:231
msgid ""
"To create new ranks or modify the default ones, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Forum: Ranks` and "
"click :guilabel:`New` or select an existing rank."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novih rangov ali spreminjanje privzetih pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Forum: Rangi` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` ali izberite obstoječi rang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:234
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`Rank Name`, the :guilabel:`Required Karma` points to "
"reach it, its :guilabel:`Description`, a :guilabel:`Motivational` message to "
"encourage users to reach it, and an image."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`Ime ranga`, :guilabel:`Zahtevano karmo` točk za dosego, "
"njegov :guilabel:`Opis`, :guilabel:`Motivacijsko` sporočilo za spodbujanje "
"uporabnikov, da ga dosežejo, in sliko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Default forum ranks"
msgstr "Privzeti rangi foruma"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:244
msgid "Badges"
msgstr "Priponke"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:246
msgid ""
"To create new badges or modify the default ones, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Forum: Badges` and "
"click :guilabel:`New` or select an existing badge."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novih značk ali spreminjanje privzetih pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Forum: Značke` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` ali izberite obstoječo značko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:249
msgid "Enter the badge name and description, add an image, and configure it."
msgstr "Vnesite ime in opis značke, dodajte sliko ter jo konfigurirajte."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:252
msgid "Assign manually"
msgstr "Ročna dodelitev"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:254
msgid ""
"If the badge should be granted manually, select which users can grant them "
"by selecting one of the following :guilabel:`Allowance to Grant` options:"
msgstr ""
"Če naj se značka podeli ročno, izberite, kateri uporabniki jo lahko "
"podelijo, tako da izberete eno od naslednjih možnosti :guilabel:`Dovoljenje "
"za podelitev`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Everyone`: all non-portal users (since badges are granted from "
"the backend)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vsi`: vsi uporabniki, ki niso uporabniki portala (ker se značke "
"podelijo iz zalednega sistema)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:258
msgid ""
":guilabel:`A selected list of users`: users selected "
"under :guilabel:`Authorized Users`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izbran seznam uporabnikov`: uporabniki, izbrani "
"pod :guilabel:`Pooblaščeni uporabniki`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:259
msgid ""
":guilabel:`People having some badges`: users who have been granted the "
"badges selected under :guilabel:`Required Badges`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Osebe, ki imajo določene značke`: uporabniki, ki so prejeli "
"značke, izbrane pod :guilabel:`Zahtevane značke`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:262
msgid ""
"It is possible to restrict how many times per month each user can grant the "
"badge by enabling :guilabel:`Monthly Limited Sending` and entering "
"a :guilabel:`Limitation Number`."
msgstr ""
"Možno je omejiti, kolikokrat na mesec lahko vsak uporabnik podeli značko, "
"tako da omogočite :guilabel:`Mesečno omejeno pošiljanje` in "
"vnesete :guilabel:`Številko omejitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:266
msgid "Assign automatically"
msgstr "Samodejno dodeljevanje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:268
msgid ""
"If the badge should be granted **automatically** when certain conditions are "
"met, select :guilabel:`No one, assigned through challenges` "
"under :guilabel:`Allowance to Grant`."
msgstr ""
"Če naj se značka podeli **samodejno**, ko so izpolnjeni določeni pogoji, "
"izberite :guilabel:`Nihče, dodeljena prek izzivov` pod :guilabel:`Dovoljenje "
"za podelitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:271
msgid ""
"Next, determine how the badge should be granted by clicking :guilabel:`Add` "
"under the :guilabel:`Rewards for challenges` section. Select a challenge to "
"add it or create one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Nato določite, kako naj se značka podeli, tako da kliknete :guilabel:`Dodaj` "
"pod razdelkom :guilabel:`Nagrade za izzive`. Izberite izziv, da ga dodate, "
"ali ustvarite novega s klikom na :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:276
msgid ""
"It is possible to give the badge a :guilabel:`Forum Badge Level` "
"(:guilabel:`Bronze`, :guilabel:`Silver`, :guilabel:`Gold`) to give it more "
"or less importance."
msgstr ""
"Znački je mogoče dodeliti :guilabel:`Raven značke foruma` "
"(:guilabel:`Bronasta`, :guilabel:`Srebrna`, :guilabel:`Zlata`), da ji podate "
"večji ali manjši pomen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Default forum badges"
msgstr "Privzete značke foruma"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:287
msgid "Users can use tags to filter forum posts."
msgstr "Uporabniki lahko uporabljajo oznake za filtriranje objav na forumu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:289
msgid ""
"To manage tags, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Forum: "
"Tags`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a tag and select the "
"related :guilabel:`Forum`."
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje oznak pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Forum: Oznake`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite "
"oznako, in izberite povezan :guilabel:`Forum`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:293
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Tags` section on the forum's sidebar to filter all "
"questions assigned to the selected tag. Click :guilabel:`View all` to "
"display all tags."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite razdelek :guilabel:`Oznake` v stranski vrstici foruma, da "
"filtrirate vsa vprašanja, dodeljena izbrani oznaki. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži vse`, da prikažete vse oznake."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:295
msgid ""
"New tags can be created when posting a new message, provided the user has "
"enough :ref:`karma points <forum/karma-related-rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Nove oznake je mogoče ustvariti pri objavljanju novega sporočila, če ima "
"uporabnik dovolj :ref:`karmatičnih točk <forum/karma-related-rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:301
msgid "Use a forum"
msgstr "Uporaba foruma"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:304
msgid ""
"Access to many functionalities depends on a user's :ref:`karma points <forum/"
"karma-related-rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Dostop do mnogih funkcionalnosti je odvisen od "
"uporabnikovih :ref:`karmatičnih točk <forum/karma-related-rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:310
msgid "Post questions"
msgstr "Objavljanje vprašanj"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:312
msgid ""
"To create a new post, access the forum's front end, click :guilabel:`New "
"Post`, and fill in the following:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove objave odprite vmesnik foruma, kliknite :guilabel:`Nova "
"objava` in izpolnite naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:315
msgid ":guilabel:`Title`: add the question or the topic of the post."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Naslov`: dodajte vprašanje ali temo objave."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:316
msgid ":guilabel:`Description`: add a description for the question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opis`: dodajte opis vprašanja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:317
msgid ":guilabel:`Tags`: add up to five :ref:`tags <forum/tags>`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Oznake`: dodajte do pet :ref:`oznak <forum/tags>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:319
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Post Your Question`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Objavi svoje vprašanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:324
msgid "Interact with posts"
msgstr "Interakcija z objavami"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:326
msgid "Different actions are possible on a post."
msgstr "Pri objavi je možnih več dejanj."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:328
msgid ""
"Mark a question as **favorite** by clicking the star button (:guilabel:`☆`)."
msgstr ""
"Označite vprašanje kot **priljubljeno** s klikom na gumb z zvezdico "
"(:guilabel:`☆`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:329
msgid ""
"Follow a post and get **notifications** (by email or within Odoo) when it is "
"answered by clicking the bell button (:guilabel:`🔔`)."
msgstr ""
"Sledite objavi in prejemajte **obvestila** (po e-pošti ali v Odooju), ko je "
"nanjo odgovorjeno, s klikom na gumb z zvoncem (:guilabel:`🔔`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:331
msgid ""
"**Vote** *for* (up arrow :guilabel:`▲`) or *against* (down "
"arrow :guilabel:`▼`) a question or answer."
msgstr ""
"**Glasujte** *za* (puščica navzgor :guilabel:`▲`) ali *proti* (puščica "
"navzdol :guilabel:`▼`) vprašanju ali odgovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:333
msgid ""
"Mark an answer as **best** by clicking the check mark button "
"(:guilabel:`✔`). This option is only available if the :guilabel:`Forum Mode` "
"is set to :guilabel:`Questions`."
msgstr ""
"Označite odgovor kot **najboljši** s klikom na gumb s kljukico "
"(:guilabel:`✔`). Ta možnost je na voljo samo, če je :guilabel:`Način foruma` "
"nastavljen na :guilabel:`Vprašanja`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:335
msgid ":guilabel:`Answer` a question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odgovori` na vprašanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:336
msgid ""
"**Comment** on a question or answer by clicking the speech bubble button "
"(:guilabel:`💬`)."
msgstr ""
"**Komentirajte** vprašanje ali odgovor s klikom na gumb govornega oblačka "
"(:guilabel:`💬`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:337
msgid ""
"**Share** a question on Facebook, Twitter, or LinkedIn by clicking the "
"*share nodes* button."
msgstr ""
"**Delite** vprašanje na Facebooku, Twitterju ali LinkedInu s klikom na gumb "
"*vozlišč za deljenje*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:339
msgid "Click the ellipsis button (:guilabel:`...`) to:"
msgstr "Kliknite gumb tri pike (:guilabel:`...`):"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:341
msgid ":guilabel:`Edit` a question or answer."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uredi` vprašanje ali odgovor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:342
msgid ":guilabel:`Close` a question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Zapri` vprašanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete` a question, answer, or comment. It is possible "
"to :guilabel:`Undelete` questions afterward."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izbriši` vprašanje, odgovor ali komentar. Vprašanja je mogoče "
"naknadno :guilabel:`Obnoviti`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:345
msgid ":guilabel:`Flag` a question or answer as offensive."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Označi` vprašanje ali odgovor kot žaljivo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:346
msgid ":guilabel:`Convert` a comment into an answer."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pretvori` komentar v odgovor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:347
msgid ""
":guilabel:`View` the related :ref:`Helpdesk ticket <helpdesk/forum>`, if any."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prikaži` povezan :ref:`zahtevek službe za pomoč <helpdesk/"
"forum>`, če obstaja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Posts actions"
msgstr "Dejanja objav"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:353
msgid ""
"By default, 150 karma points are required to view another user's profile. "
"This value can be configured when creating a new website."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je za ogled profila drugega uporabnika potrebnih 150 karmic točk. "
"To vrednost je mogoče konfigurirati pri ustvarjanju novega spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:359
msgid "Moderate a forum"
msgstr "Moderiranje foruma"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:361
msgid ""
"On the forum's front end, the sidebar's :guilabel:`Moderation tools` section "
"gathers the essential moderator functionalities."
msgstr ""
"Na vmesniku foruma razdelek :guilabel:`Orodja za moderiranje` v stranski "
"vrstici zbira bistvene funkcije moderatorja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Forum sidebar moderation tools"
msgstr "Orodja za moderiranje v stranski vrstici foruma"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:367
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To Validate`: access all questions and answers waiting for "
"validation before being displayed to non-moderator users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Za potrditev`: dostop do vseh vprašanj in odgovorov, ki čakajo na "
"potrditev pred prikazom uporabnikom, ki niso moderatorji."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Question to validate"
msgstr "Vprašanje za potrditev"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:374
msgid ""
"A question is pending if a user does not have the required karma. The user "
"is not able to post questions or answers while awaiting validation. Only one "
"pending question per user is allowed per forum."
msgstr ""
"Vprašanje je na čakanju, če uporabnik nima potrebnih karmic točk. Uporabnik "
"ne more objavljati vprašanj ali odgovorov med čakanjem na potrditev. Na "
"forumu je dovoljeno samo eno čakajoče vprašanje na uporabnika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:378
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Flagged`: access all questions and answers that have been flagged "
"as offensive. Click :guilabel:`Accept` to remove the offensive flag "
"or :guilabel:`Offensive` to confirm it, then select a reason and "
"click :guilabel:`Mark as offensive`. The post is then hidden from users "
"without moderation rights, and 100 karma points are deducted from the "
"offending user's tally."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Označeno`: dostop do vseh vprašanj in odgovorov, ki so bili "
"označeni kot žaljivi. Kliknite :guilabel:`Sprejmi`, da odstranite oznako "
"žaljivo, ali :guilabel:`Žaljivo`, da jo potrdite, nato izberite razlog in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Označi kot žaljivo`. Objava je nato skrita pred "
"uporabniki brez pravic moderatorja in od števca žaljivega uporabnika se "
"odšteje 100 karmic točk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Offensive reason selection"
msgstr "Izbira razloga za žaljivo vsebino"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:386
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Closed`: access all questions that have been closed. It is "
"possible to :guilabel:`Delete` or :guilabel:`Reopen` them. To close a "
"question, open it, click the ellipsis button (:guilabel:`...`), "
"then :guilabel:`Close`, select a :guilabel:`Close Reason`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Close post`. The post is then hidden from users without "
"moderation rights."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zaprto`: dostop do vseh vprašanj, ki so bila zaprta. Možno jih "
"je :guilabel:`Izbrisati` ali :guilabel:`Ponovno odpreti`. Za zaprtje "
"vprašanja ga odprite, kliknite gumb s tremi pikami (:guilabel:`...`), "
"nato :guilabel:`Zapri`, izberite :guilabel:`Razlog za zaprtje` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Zapri objavo`. Objava je nato skrita pred uporabniki "
"brez pravic moderiranja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:392
msgid ""
"When selecting :guilabel:`Spam or advertising` or :guilabel:`Contains "
"offensive or malicious remarks` as the reason, 100 karma points are deducted "
"from the poster's tally."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete :guilabel:`Neželena pošta ali oglaševanje` "
"ali :guilabel:`Vsebuje žaljive ali zlonamerne opombe` kot razlog, se od "
"skupnega števila točk karma avtorja odšteje 100 točk karma."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:396
msgid ""
"Create and edit close reasons by going to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Forum: Close Reasons`. Select :guilabel:`Basic` "
"as :guilabel:`Reason Type` if the reason should be used when closing a "
"question, and :guilabel:`Offensive` if it should be used for flagged posts."
msgstr ""
"Razloge za zaprtje ustvarite in uredite tako, da greste "
"na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Forum: Razlogi za "
"zaprtje`. Izberite :guilabel:`Osnovno` kot :guilabel:`Vrsta razloga`, če naj "
"se razlog uporabi pri zapiranju vprašanja, in :guilabel:`Žaljivo`, če naj se "
"uporabi za označene objave."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:399
msgid ""
"Manage all posts by going to :menuselection:`Website  --> Configuration --> "
"Forum: Forums`, selecting the forum, and clicking the :guilabel:`Posts` "
"smart button. By clicking the :guilabel:`Actions` button, it is possible "
"to :guilabel:`Export`, :guilabel:`Archive`, :guilabel:`Unarchive`, "
"or :guilabel:`Delete` one or multiple posts."
msgstr ""
"Upravljajte vse objave tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Forum: Forumi`, izberete forum in kliknete pametni "
"gumb :guilabel:`Objave`. S klikom na gumb :guilabel:`Dejanja` je "
"možno :guilabel:`Izvoziti`, :guilabel:`Arhivirati`, :guilabel:`Razarhivirati` "
"ali :guilabel:`Izbrisati` eno ali več objav."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:5
msgid "Live Chat"
msgstr "Pogovor v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** allows users to communicate with website visitors in real-"
"time. With **Live Chat**, leads can be qualified for their sales potential, "
"support questions can be answered in real time, and issues can be directed "
"to the appropriate team for further investigation or follow up. **Live "
"Chat** also provides the opportunity for instant feedback from customers."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Klepet v živo** uporabnikom omogoča komunikacijo z obiskovalci "
"spletnega mesta v realnem času. S **Klepetom v živo** je mogoče potencialne "
"stranke kvalificirati glede na njihov prodajni potencial, na vprašanja "
"podpore je mogoče odgovoriti v realnem času, težave pa je mogoče usmeriti "
"ustrezni ekipi za nadaljnjo preiskavo ali nadaljnje ukrepanje. **Klepet v "
"živo** omogoča tudi takojšnje povratne informacije strank."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:13
msgid "Enable Live Chat"
msgstr "Omogočanje klepeta v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:15
msgid "The **Live Chat** application can be installed multiple ways:"
msgstr "Aplikacijo **Klepet v živo** je mogoče namestiti na več načinov:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:17
msgid ""
"Go to the :menuselection:`Apps application`, search `Live Chat`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacije`, poiščite `Live Chat` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Namesti`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:18
msgid ""
"Go to the :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams` "
"list view, select a team, and on the team's settings page, click the "
"checkbox next to :guilabel:`Live Chat`, under the :guilabel:`Channels` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Služba za pomoč --> Konfiguracija --> Ekipe "
"službe za pomoč`, izberite ekipo in na strani z nastavitvami ekipe označite "
"potrditveno polje poleg :guilabel:`Klepet v živo` v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Kanali`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:21
msgid ""
"In the :menuselection:`Website` app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` section, check the "
"box next to :guilabel:`Livechat`, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji :menuselection:`Spletna stran` pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`E-pošta in trženje`, označite polje "
"poleg :guilabel:`Livechat` in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:0
msgid "View of the settings page and the live chat feature for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Pogled strani z nastavitvami in funkcijo klepeta v živo za Odoo Klepet v "
"živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:29
msgid ""
"After the **Live Chat** application is installed, a live chat *Channel* is "
"created, by default."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aplikacija **Klepet v živo** nameščena, je privzeto ustvarjen *Kanal* "
"za klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:32
msgid "Create live chat channels"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje kanalov za klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:34
msgid ""
"To create a new live chat *Channel*, go to the :menuselection:`Live Chat "
"app`. Then, click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank channel detail form. Enter "
"the name of the new channel in the :guilabel:`Channel Name` field."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega *Kanala* za klepet v živo pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Klepet v živo`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da "
"odprete prazen obrazec s podrobnostmi kanala. V polje :guilabel:`Ime kanala` "
"vnesite ime novega kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:38
msgid ""
"To configure the remaining tabs on the channel detail form (:ref:`Operators "
"<livechat/operators-tab>`, :ref:`Options <livechat/options-"
"tab>`, :ref:`Channel Rules <livechat/channel-rules-tab>`, and :ref:`Widget "
"<livechat/widget-tab>`), follow the steps below."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo preostalih zavihkov v obrazcu s podrobnostmi kanala "
"(:ref:`Operaterji <livechat/operators-tab>`, :ref:`Možnosti <livechat/"
"options-tab>`, :ref:`Pravila kanala <livechat/channel-rules-tab>` "
"in :ref:`Pripomoček <livechat/widget-tab>`) sledite spodnjim korakom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of a live chat channel form for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled obrazca kanala za klepet v živo za Odoo Klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:46
msgid ""
"The channel detail form for any channel can be accessed by navigating back "
"to the :guilabel:`Website Live Chat Channels` dashboard, via the "
"breadcrumbs. Find the Kanban card for the appropriate live chat channel, "
"hover over it, and then click on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon to open the drop-down menu. "
"Click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel detail form."
msgstr ""
"Do obrazca s podrobnostmi kanala za kateri koli kanal lahko dostopate tako, "
"da se prek drobtinskih povezav vrnete na nadzorno ploščo :guilabel:`Kanali "
"za klepet v živo spletnega mesta`. Poiščite Kanban kartice ustreznega kanala "
"za klepet v živo, se pomaknite nanjo in nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpično tri pike)`, da odprete spustni meni. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj kanal`, da odprete obrazec s podrobnostmi "
"kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:55
msgid "Operators tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Operaterji"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:57
msgid ""
"*Operators* are the users who act as agents and respond to live chat "
"requests from customers. When a user is added as an operator in a live chat "
"channel, they can receive chats from website visitors wherever they are in "
"the database. Chat windows open in the bottom-right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"*Operaterji* so uporabniki, ki delujejo kot agenti in se odzivajo na zahteve "
"za klepet v živo strank. Ko je uporabnik dodan kot operater v kanalu za "
"klepet v živo, lahko prejema klepete obiskovalcev spletnega mesta ne glede "
"na to, kje v zbirki podatkov se nahaja. Okna za klepet se odprejo v spodnjem "
"desnem kotu zaslona."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "A live chat pop-up window in an Odoo database."
msgstr "Pojavno okno za klepet v živo v zbirki podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:64
msgid ""
"On the channel detail form, click the :guilabel:`Operators` tab. The user "
"who originally created the live chat channel has been added as an operator "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu s podrobnostmi kanala kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Operaterji`. "
"Uporabnik, ki je prvotno ustvaril kanal za klepet v živo, je bil privzeto "
"dodan kot operater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:68
msgid ""
"Current operators can be edited, or removed, by clicking on their respective "
"boxes in the :guilabel:`Operators` tab, which reveals a "
"separate :guilabel:`Open: Operators` pop-up. In that pop-up, adjust any "
"information, as needed. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`, or "
"click :guilabel:`Remove` to remove that operator from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Obstoječe operaterje lahko urejate ali odstranite tako, da kliknete na "
"njihova polja v zavihku :guilabel:`Operaterji`, kar odpre ločeno pojavno "
"okno :guilabel:`Odpri: Operaterji`. V tem pojavnem oknu po potrebi "
"prilagodite podatke. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani` ali "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Odstrani`, da odstranite operaterja iz kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:73
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add` to reveal an :guilabel:`Add: Operators` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`, da se odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Dodaj: "
"Operaterji`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:75
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, scroll to find the desired users, or enter their name "
"in the search bar. Then, tick the checkbox next to the users to be added, "
"and click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu se pomaknite do želenih uporabnikov ali vnesite njihovo ime "
"v iskalno vrstico. Nato označite potrditveno polje poleg uporabnikov, ki jih "
"želite dodati, in kliknite :guilabel:`Izberi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:78
msgid ""
"New operators can be created and added to the list directly from this pop-up "
"window, as well, by clicking :guilabel:`New`, and filling out "
"the :guilabel:`Create Operators` form. When the form is complete, "
"click :guilabel:`Save & Close`, or :guilabel:`Save & New` for multiple "
"record creations."
msgstr ""
"Nove operaterje lahko ustvarite in dodate na seznam neposredno iz tega "
"pojavnega okna tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite "
"obrazec :guilabel:`Ustvari operaterje`. Ko je obrazec izpolnjen, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri` ali :guilabel:`Shrani in novo` za "
"ustvarjanje več zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:83
msgid ""
"Creating a new user can impact the status of an Odoo subscription, as the "
"total number of users in a database counts towards the billing rate. Proceed "
"with caution before creating a new user. If a user already exists, adding "
"them as an operator will **not** alter the subscription or billing rate for "
"a database."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje novega uporabnika lahko vpliva na status naročnine na Odoo, saj "
"se skupno število uporabnikov v podatkovni zbirki upošteva pri obračunu. "
"Pred ustvarjanjem novega uporabnika bodite previdni. Če uporabnik že "
"obstaja, ga dodajanje kot operaterja **ne** bo spremenilo naročnine ali "
"obračuna za podatkovno zbirko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:93
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` tab on the live chat channel detail form contains "
"the visual and text settings for the live chat window."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Možnosti` v obrazcu s podrobnostmi kanala za klepet v "
"živo vsebuje vizualne in besedilne nastavitve za okno klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:99
msgid "Livechat button"
msgstr "Gumb za klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:101
msgid ""
"The *Livechat Button* is the icon that appears in the bottom-right corner of "
"the website."
msgstr ""
"*Gumb za klepet v živo* je ikona, ki se pojavi v spodnjem desnem kotu "
"spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:103
msgid ""
"Change the text in the :guilabel:`Notification text` field to update the "
"greeting displayed in the text bubble when the live chat button appears on "
"the website."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite besedilo v polju :guilabel:`Besedilo obvestila`, da posodobite "
"pozdrav, prikazan v besedilnem oblačku, ko se gumb za klepet v živo pojavi "
"na spletnem mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:106
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Livechat Button Color` alters the color of the live chat "
"button as it appears on the website. To change the color, click on a color "
"bubble to open the color selection window, then click and drag the circle "
"along the color gradient. Click out of the selection window once complete. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon to the right of the "
"color bubbles to reset the colors to the default selection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Barva gumba za klepet v živo` spremeni barvo gumba za klepet v "
"živo, kot se prikazuje na spletnem mestu. Za spremembo barve kliknite na "
"barvni mehurček, da odprete okno za izbiro barve, nato kliknite in povlecite "
"krog vzdolž barvnega gradients. Ko končate, kliknite izven okna za izbiro. "
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(osveži)` desno od barvnih "
"mehurčkov, da ponastavite barve na privzeto izbiro."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:113
msgid ""
"Color selection, for the button or header, can be made manually using a "
"slider or through RGB, HSL, or HEX color code entries from the pop-up color "
"selection window that appears when either of the color bubbles are clicked. "
"Different options are available, depending on the operating system."
msgstr ""
"Izbiro barve za gumb ali glavo lahko izvedete ročno z drsnikom ali z vnosi "
"barvnih kod RGB, HSL ali HEX iz pojavnega okna za izbiro barve, ki se "
"prikaže, ko kliknete na katerega od barvnih mehurčkov. Na voljo so različne "
"možnosti, odvisno od operacijskega sistema."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:119
msgid ""
"With the following settings, the live chat button appears on the website as "
"shown:"
msgstr ""
"Z naslednjimi nastavitvami se gumb za klepet v živo na spletnem mestu "
"prikaže, kot je prikazano:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Notification text`: \"Have a Question? Chat with us.\""
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Besedilo obvestila`: \"Imate vprašanje? Poklepetajte z nami.\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:122
msgid ":guilabel:`Livechat Button Color`: set to purple"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Barva gumba za klepet v živo`: nastavljena na vijolično"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:0
msgid "View of an Odoo website emphasizing the livechat button."
msgstr "Pogled spletnega mesta Odoo s poudarkom na gumbu za klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:128
msgid "Livechat window"
msgstr "Okno za klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:130
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Livechat Window` is the space where the live chat "
"conversation with website visitors takes place."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Okno za klepet v živo` je prostor, kjer poteka pogovor s klepetom "
"v živo z obiskovalci spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:133
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Welcome Message` to change the message a visitor sees "
"when they open a new chat session. This message appears as though it is sent "
"by a live chat operator, and acts as both a greeting and an invitation to "
"continue the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Uredite :guilabel:`Pozdravno sporočilo`, da spremenite sporočilo, ki ga "
"obiskovalec vidi, ko odpre novo sejo klepeta. To sporočilo se pojavi, kot da "
"ga je poslal operater klepeta v živo, in deluje kot pozdrav in povabilo k "
"nadaljevanju pogovora."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:137
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Chat Input Placeholder` to alter the text that appears "
"in the box where visitors type their replies. This message prompts the "
"visitor to initiate the chat."
msgstr ""
"Uredite :guilabel:`Nadomestno besedilo za vnos klepeta`, da spremenite "
"besedilo, ki se prikaže v polju, kjer obiskovalci vnesejo svoje odgovore. To "
"sporočilo spodbudi obiskovalca, da začne klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:140
msgid ""
"The *Channel Header* is the colored bar at the top of the chat window. "
"The :guilabel:`Channel Header Color` can be changed following the same steps "
"as the :ref:`Livechat button <livechat/livechat-button>`."
msgstr ""
"*Glava kanala* je barvna vrstica na vrhu pogovornega okna. "
"Barvo :guilabel:`glave kanala` lahko spremenite po enakih korakih "
"kot :ref:`gumb klepeta v živo <livechat/livechat-button>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:147
msgid "The live chat window with a purple channel header and placeholder text."
msgstr ""
"Okno klepeta v živo z vijoličasto glavo kanala in nadomestnim besedilom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:147
msgid ""
"The live chat window with a purple channel header and placeholder text that "
"reads, \"Say Something...\""
msgstr ""
"Okno klepeta v živo z vijoličasto glavo kanala in nadomestnim besedilom "
"»Povej nekaj...«"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:153
msgid "Channel Rules tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pravila kanala"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:155
msgid ""
"To configure which website user actions open the live chat window, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Channel Rules` tab on the live chat channel detail form."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati, katera uporabniška dejanja na spletnem mestu "
"odprejo okno klepeta v živo, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Pravila kanala` "
"na obrazcu s podrobnostmi kanala klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:158
msgid ""
"To create a new channel rule, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. This opens "
"the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo pravilo kanala, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`. "
"To odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Ustvari pravila`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of a channel's rules form for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled obrazca s pravili kanala za Odoo klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:165
msgid "Create new rules"
msgstr "Ustvarite nova pravila"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:167
msgid ""
"Fill out the fields on the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window as "
"instructed below, then click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite polja v pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari pravila`, kot je navedeno "
"spodaj, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:172
msgid "Live Chat Button"
msgstr "Gumb za klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:174
msgid ""
"The *Livechat Button* is the icon that appears in the bottom-right corner of "
"the website. Select from one of the following display options:"
msgstr ""
"*Gumb klepeta v živo* je ikona, ki se prikaže v spodnjem desnem kotu "
"spletnega mesta. Izberite eno od naslednjih možnosti prikaza:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:177
msgid ":guilabel:`Show`: displays the chat button on the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prikaži`: prikaže gumb klepeta na strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:178
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show with notification`: displays the chat button, as well as a "
"floating text bubble next to the button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prikaži z obvestilom`: prikaže gumb klepeta in plavajoč besedilni "
"oblaček ob gumbu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:180
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Open automatically`: displays the button, and automatically opens "
"the chat window after a specified amount of time (designated in "
"the :guilabel:`Open automatically timer` field, that appears when this "
"option is selected)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odpri samodejno`: prikaže gumb in samodejno odpre okno klepeta po "
"določenem času (določenem v polju :guilabel:`Časovnik samodejnega "
"odpiranja`, ki se prikaže, ko je izbrana ta možnost)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:183
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide`: hides the chat button on the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skrij`: skrije gumb klepeta na strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:185
msgid "Chatbot"
msgstr "Chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:187
msgid ""
"To include a :doc:`Chatbot <livechat/chatbots>` on this channel, select it "
"from the drop-down menu. If the chatbot should only be active when no "
"operators are active, check the box labeled :guilabel:`Enabled only if no "
"operator`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vključiti :doc:`klepetalnega robota <livechat/chatbots>` na tem "
"kanalu, ga izberite iz spustnega menija. Če naj bo klepetalec aktiven le, ko "
"noben operater ni aktiven, označite polje :guilabel:`Omogočeno le, če ni "
"operaterja`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:191
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator` field is **only** visible if a "
"chatbot is selected in the :guilabel:`Chatbot` field."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Omogočeno le, če ni operaterja` je **vidno samo**, če je v "
"polju :guilabel:`Klepetalec` izbran klepetalec."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:194
msgid "URL Regex"
msgstr "URL regularni izraz"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:196
msgid ""
"The *URL Regex* specifies the web pages where this rule should be applied. "
"In the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field, input the relative URL of the page where "
"the chat button should appear."
msgstr ""
"*Regex URL* določa spletne strani, kjer naj se to pravilo uporabi. V "
"polje :guilabel:`Regex URL` vnesite relativni URL strani, kjer naj se pojavi "
"gumb klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:200
msgid ""
"For example, to apply the rule to the URL, `https://mydatabse.odoo.com/"
"shop`, enter `/shop` to the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če želite uporabiti pravilo za URL `https://mydatabse.odoo.com/"
"shop`, vnesite `/shop` v polje :guilabel:`Regex URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:203
msgid ""
"To apply the rule to *all* pages on the database, enter `/` in "
"the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti pravilo za *vse* strani v zbirki podatkov, vnesite `/` v "
"polje :guilabel:`Regex URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:206
msgid "Open automatically timer"
msgstr "Samodejno odpri časovnik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:208
msgid ""
"This field designates the amount of time (in seconds) a page should be open "
"before the chat window opens. This field **only** appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Button` for this rule is set to :guilabel:`Open "
"automatically`."
msgstr ""
"To polje določa čas (v sekundah), koliko časa mora biti stran odprta, preden "
"se odpre okno klepeta. To polje se prikaže **samo**, če je :guilabel:`Gumb "
"klepeta v živo` za to pravilo nastavljen na :guilabel:`Odpri samodejno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:212
msgid "Country"
msgstr "Država"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:214
msgid ""
"If this channel should **only** be available to site visitors in specific "
"countries, add them to the :guilabel:`Country` field. If this field is left "
"blank, the channel is available to all site visitors, regardless of location."
msgstr ""
"Če naj bo ta kanal **samo** na voljo obiskovalcem spletnega mesta v "
"določenih državah, jih dodajte v polje :guilabel:`Država`. Če je to polje "
"prazno, je kanal na voljo vsem obiskovalcem spletnega mesta, ne glede na "
"lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:219
msgid ""
"In order to track the geographical location of visitors, *GeoIP* **must** be "
"installed on the database. While this feature is installed by default on "
"*Odoo Online* databases, *On-Premise* databases require "
"additional :doc:`setup steps </administration/on_premise/geo_ip>`."
msgstr ""
"Za sledenje geografski lokaciji obiskovalcev **mora** biti *GeoIP* nameščen "
"v bazi podatkov. Medtem ko je ta funkcija nameščena privzeto v bazah "
"podatkov *Odoo Online*, baze podatkov *On-Premise* zahtevajo "
"dodatne :doc:`korake nastavitve </administration/on_premise/geo_ip>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:226
msgid "Widget tab"
msgstr "Zavihek pripomočka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:228
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Widget` tab on the live chat channel detail form provides an "
"embeddable code snippet for external, non-Odoo websites. This code can be "
"added to a website to provide access to a live chat window."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Pripomoček` na obrazcu s podrobnostmi kanala klepeta v "
"živo ponuja vdelljivo izsečno kodo za zunanje spletne strani, ki niso Odoo. "
"To kodo lahko dodate na spletno mesto, da omogočite dostop do okna za klepet "
"v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:233
msgid ""
"The live chat widget can be added to websites created through Odoo by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Website app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Then, scroll to the :menuselection:`Email & Marketing` section. In "
"the :guilabel:`Channel` field, select the channel to add to the site. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save` to apply."
msgstr ""
"Pripomoček za klepet v živo lahko dodate na spletna mesta, ustvarjena prek "
"Odoo, tako da se pomaknete na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Spletno mesto --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. Nato se pomaknite do odseka :menuselection:`E-"
"pošta in trženje`. V polju :guilabel:`Kanal` izberite kanal, ki ga želite "
"dodati na spletno mesto. Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da uveljavite."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:238
msgid ""
"To add the widget to a website created on a third-party platform, click the "
"first :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon on the :guilabel:`Widget` "
"tab, and paste the code into the `<head>` tag on the site."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje pripomočka na spletno mesto, ustvarjeno na platformi tretje "
"osebe, kliknite prvo ikono :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(kopiraj)` na "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Pripomoček` in prilepite kodo v oznako `<head>` na "
"spletnem mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:242
msgid ""
"Likewise, to send a live chat session to a customer, click the "
"second :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon on "
"the :guilabel:`Widget` tab. This link can be sent directly to a customer. "
"When they click the link, they are redirected to a new chat window."
msgstr ""
"Podobno, če želite stranki poslati sejo klepeta v živo, kliknite drugo "
"ikono :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(kopiraj)` na "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Pripomoček`. To povezavo lahko pošljete neposredno "
"stranki. Ko kliknejo povezavo, so preusmerjeni v novo okno za klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of the widget tab for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled zavihka pripomočka za Odoo klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:250
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:251
msgid ":doc:`livechat/responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:252
msgid ":doc:`livechat/ratings`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/ratings`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:253
msgid ":doc:`livechat/chatbots`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/chatbots`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:254
msgid ":doc:`livechat/participate`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/participate`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:3
msgid "Chatbots"
msgstr "Chatbot-i"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *Chatbot* is a program designed to mimic a conversation with a live human. "
"Chatbots are assigned a script of pre-written steps to follow. The scripts "
"are designed to anticipate a visitor's potential response, and lead them "
"through a series of questions and answers the same way a live team member "
"would."
msgstr ""
"*Klepetalni robot* je program, zasnovan za posnemanje pogovora z živo osebo. "
"Klepetalni roboti imajo dodeljeno skripto vnaprej napisanih korakov, ki jim "
"morajo slediti. Skripte so zasnovane tako, da predvidevajo morebitni odziv "
"obiskovalca in ga vodijo skozi vrsto vprašanj in odgovorov na enak način, "
"kot bi to storil živ član ekipe."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:10
msgid ""
"Chatbots can be customized to fill various roles, from customer support, to "
"creating leads, to collecting contact information. The goal of each chatbot "
"can vary based on several criteria, including the webpage where it is "
"located, and the information it captures."
msgstr ""
"Klepetalne robote lahko prilagodite za različne vloge, od podpore strankam "
"do ustvarjanja potencialnih strank in zbiranja kontaktnih informacij. Cilj "
"vsakega klepetnega robota se lahko razlikuje glede na več meril, vključno s "
"spletno stranjo, kjer se nahaja, in informacijami, ki jih zajame."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of the chat window with a helpdesk ticket created in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Pogled okna za klepet z zahtevkom službe za pomoč, ustvarjenim v Odoo "
"klepetu v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:20
msgid "Build a chatbot"
msgstr "Zgradite klepetnega robota"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:22
msgid ""
"Before creating a new chatbot, the **Live Chat** application must first "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Preden ustvarite novega klepetnega robota, mora biti aplikacija **Klepet v "
"živo** najprej :ref:`nameščena <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:25
msgid ""
"After the **Live Chat** application has been installed on the database, go "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aplikacija **Klepet v živo** nameščena v bazi podatkov, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Klepet v živo --> Konfiguracija --> Klepetalni "
"roboti`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:29
msgid ""
"When the **Live Chat** app is installed, a sample chatbot is created, named "
"*Welcome Bot*. This chatbot has a preconfigured script that walks through a "
"few basic steps, including asking for a visitor's email address, and "
"forwarding the conversation to an operator."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aplikacija **Klepet v živo** nameščena, se ustvari vzorčni klepetalni "
"robot z imenom *Welcome Bot*. Ta klepetalni robot ima vnaprej konfigurirano "
"skripto, ki vas vodi skozi nekaj osnovnih korakov, vključno s povpraševanjem "
"po e-poštnem naslovu obiskovalca in posredovanjem pogovora operaterju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:33
msgid ""
"*Welcome Bot* can be used as a starting point. The existing steps can be "
"edited or removed, and new steps can be added to customize the script, as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"*Welcome Bot* lahko uporabite kot začetno točko. Obstoječe korake lahko "
"uredite ali odstranite, po potrebi pa lahko dodate tudi nove korake za "
"prilagoditev skripta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:36
msgid "*Welcome Bot* can be deleted or archived, if necessary."
msgstr "*Welcome Bot* lahko po potrebi izbrišete ali arhivirate."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "View of the Welcome Bot script in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled skripta Welcome Bot v aplikaciji Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:41
msgid ""
"To create a new chatbot, navigate to the :guilabel:`Chatbot` page "
"(:menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`) and "
"click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank chatbot details page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov chatbot, pojdite na stran :guilabel:`Chatbot` "
"(:menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`) in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`New`, da odprete prazno stran s podrobnostmi chatbota."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:44
msgid ""
"Enter a name in the :guilabel:`Chatbot Name` field and hover over the image "
"on the right. Click on the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon that "
"appears to add a photo."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Chatbot Name` vnesite ime in z miško premaknite kazalec "
"čez sliko na desni. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(svinčnik)`, "
"ki se prikaže, da dodate fotografijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:48
msgid "Chatbot scripts"
msgstr "Skripte chatbota"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:50
msgid ""
"After the new chatbot has been created and named, the next step is to create "
"a script. Chatbot conversations follow an accompanying script, comprised of "
"lines of dialog. Each line is designed to either deliver or capture "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nov chatbot ustvarjen in imenovan, je naslednji korak ustvarjanje "
"skripta. Pogovori chatbotov sledijo priloženemu skriptu, ki ga sestavljajo "
"vrstice dialoga. Vsaka vrstica je zasnovana za dostavo ali zajemanje "
"informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:54
msgid ""
"To create a chatbot script, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` in "
"the :guilabel:`Script` tab of the chatbot detail page, and "
"a :guilabel:`Create Script Steps` pop-up window appears. This form must be "
"filled out for each line of text (dialog) that the chatbot could potentially "
"deliver during the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti skript chatbota, kliknite :guilabel:`Add a Line` v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Script` na strani s podrobnostmi chatbota in prikaže se "
"pojavno okno :guilabel:`Create Script Steps`. Ta obrazec je treba izpolniti "
"za vsako vrstico besedila (dialoga), ki ga lahko chatbot med pogovorom "
"potencialno dostavi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:59
msgid ""
"First, enter the content of the message in the :guilabel:`Message` field. "
"Then, select an option from the :guilabel:`Step Type` and :ref:`Only If "
"<livechat/chatbots/only-if>` drop-down menus."
msgstr ""
"Najprej vnesite vsebino sporočila v polje :guilabel:`Message`. Nato izberite "
"možnost v spustnih menijih :guilabel:`Step Type` in :ref:`Only If <livechat/"
"chatbots/only-if>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:63
msgid "Step types"
msgstr "Vrste korakov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:65
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Step Type` selected depends on the intended purpose of the "
"message. The available options in the :guilabel:`Step Type` drop-down menu "
"are detailed below."
msgstr ""
"Izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Step Type` je odvisna od predvidenega namena "
"sporočila. Razpoložljive možnosti v spustnem meniju :guilabel:`Step Type` so "
"podrobno opisane spodaj."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:69
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Besedilo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:71
msgid ""
"This step is used for messages where no answer is expected or necessary. "
"Text steps can be used for greetings, to offer resources, such as "
"documentation, or provide links to specific web pages."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak se uporablja za sporočila, kjer odgovor ni pričakovan ali potreben. "
"Besedilne korake lahko uporabite za pozdrave, za ponudbo virov, kot je "
"dokumentacija, ali za zagotavljanje povezav do določenih spletnih strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:75
msgid ""
"*Text* step types are only intended to deliver information, and do not allow "
"for any visitor input. As such, they must be followed by additional steps to "
"continue the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Vrste korakov *Text* so namenjene samo dostavi informacij in ne omogočajo "
"vnosa obiskovalca. Zato jim morajo slediti dodatni koraki za nadaljevanje "
"pogovora."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:79
msgid "Question"
msgstr "Vprašanje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:81
msgid ""
"This step asks a question and provides a set of answers. The visitor clicks "
"on one answer, which either leads to a new step in the conversation, or can "
"lead to an optional link to a new webpage."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak zastavi vprašanje in ponudi nabor odgovorov. Obiskovalec klikne na "
"en odgovor, ki bodisi vodi do novega koraka v pogovoru bodisi lahko vodi do "
"izbirne povezave do nove spletne strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:84
msgid ""
"Enter the question in the :guilabel:`Message` field. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Answer` heading, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` to create a "
"blank answer line."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Message` vnesite vprašanje. Nato pod "
"naslovom :guilabel:`Answer` kliknite :guilabel:`Add a Line`, da ustvarite "
"prazno vrstico za odgovor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:87
msgid ""
"Proceed to enter the answer as it should appear to the visitor. To turn the "
"answer into a link that redirects the visitor when selected, add the URL to "
"the answer line under the :guilabel:`Optional Link` heading."
msgstr ""
"Nadaljujte z vnosom odgovora, kot naj se prikaže obiskovalcu. Če želite "
"odgovor spremeniti v povezavo, ki preusmeri obiskovalca ob izbiri, dodajte "
"URL v vrstico odgovora pod naslovom :guilabel:`Optional Link`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:91
msgid ""
"Repeat these steps for every answer to be included for the question. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save & Close` or :guilabel:`Save & New` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Te korake ponovite za vsak odgovor, ki naj bo vključen v vprašanje. Ko "
"končate, kliknite :guilabel:`Save & Close` ali :guilabel:`Save & New`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:95
msgid ""
"It is helpful to add a catchall answer to question steps (e.g: `Something "
"else`). This helps visitors continue the conversation, even if their needs "
"do not fit with any of the other answers."
msgstr ""
"Koristno je dodati splošni odgovor na korake z vprašanji (npr.: `Something "
"else`). To pomaga obiskovalcem nadaljevati pogovor, tudi če njihove potrebe "
"ne ustrezajo nobenemu od drugih odgovorov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:99
msgid "Email"
msgstr "E-pošta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:101
msgid ""
"This step prompts visitors to provide their email address, which is stored "
"and can be used by team members later to follow up with additional "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak pozove obiskovalce, da navedejo svoj e-poštni naslov, ki se shrani "
"in ga lahko člani ekipe pozneje uporabijo za nadaljnje posredovanje dodatnih "
"informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:104
msgid ""
"The only accepted inputs for this step type are email addresses that are in "
"a valid format. If a visitor attempts to enter anything other than a valid "
"email address, the chatbot responds with a message stating it does not "
"recognize the information submitted."
msgstr ""
"Edini sprejeti vnosi za to vrsto koraka so e-poštni naslovi v veljavni "
"obliki. Če obiskovalec poskuša vnesti karkoli drugega kot veljaven e-poštni "
"naslov, chatbot odgovori s sporočilom, da ne prepozna poslanih informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
msgid "View of a chatbot responding to an invalid email."
msgstr "Pogled odziva klepetalnega robota na neveljavno e-pošto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:112
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Telefon"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:114
msgid ""
"Similar to email, this step type prompts the visitor to enter their phone "
"number, which can be used to follow up with additional information, schedule "
"demos, and more."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot e-pošta ta vrsta koraka pozove obiskovalca, da vnese svojo "
"telefonsko številko, ki jo je mogoče uporabiti za nadaljnje spremljanje z "
"dodatnimi informacijami, načrtovanje predstavitev in drugo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:118
msgid ""
"Due to the vast number of formats used for phone numbers worldwide, "
"responses to this step type are not validated for formatting, and can "
"include both numbers and special characters."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi širokega števila formatov telefonskih številk po vsem svetu se odzivi "
"na to vrsto koraka ne preverjajo glede oblikovanja in lahko vključujejo "
"številke in posebne znake."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:124
msgid "Forward to Operator"
msgstr "Posreduj operaterju"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:126
msgid ""
"This step forwards the conversation to an active live chat operator, so they "
"can continue assisting the visitor. As the conversation transcript is passed "
"on to the operator, they can pick up where the chatbot left off. This not "
"only saves time for all parties involved, it can also help qualify "
"conversations before they reach live operators."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak posreduje pogovor aktivnemu operaterju klepеta v živo, da lahko "
"nadaljuje s pomočjo obiskovalcu. Ker se prepis pogovora posreduje "
"operaterju, lahko nadaljuje tam, kjer je klepetaln robot končal. To ne "
"prišrani samo časa vsem udeleženim stranem, temveč lahko pomaga tudi pri "
"kvalifikaciji pogovorov, preden dosežejo operaterje v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:132
msgid ""
"If no active operator is available on the channel, the chatbot continues the "
"conversation with the visitor. Therefore, additional steps should be added "
"after this one to ensure there is no abrupt end to the conversation. The "
"additional steps can both inform visitors about the lack of available "
"operators (e.g. `Uh-oh, it looks like none of our operators are available`) "
"and continue the conversation (e.g. `Would you like to leave your email "
"address?`)."
msgstr ""
"Če na kanalu ni na voljo noben aktiven operater, klepetaln robot nadaljuje "
"pogovor z obiskovalcem. Zato je treba za tem korakom dodati dodatne korake, "
"da se zagotovi, da pogovor ne konča nenadoma. Dodatni koraki lahko obvestijo "
"obiskovalce o pomanjkanju razpoložljivih operaterjev (npr. „Ojoj, zdi se, da "
"noben od naših operaterjev ni na voljo“) in nadaljujejo pogovor (npr. „Bi "
"želeli pustiti svoj e-poštni naslov?“)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of a chatbot follow up messages when no live chat operator is available."
msgstr ""
"Pogled nadaljevalnih sporočil klepetalnega robota, ko operater klepeta v "
"živo ni na voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:142
msgid "Free Input/Multi-Line"
msgstr "Prosti vnos/večvrstni"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:144
msgid ""
"The *free input* step allows visitors to respond to questions without "
"providing pre-written responses. Information provided in these responses is "
"stored in the chat transcripts."
msgstr ""
"Korak *prosti vnos* omogoča obiskovalcem, da odgovorijo na vprašanja brez "
"zagotovljenih vnaprej napisanih odgovorov. Informacije, podane v teh "
"odgovorih, se shranjujejo v prepisih klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:147
msgid ""
"Choose between :guilabel:`Free Input` and :guilabel:`Free Input (Multi-"
"Line)` depending on the type and amount of information the visitor is asked "
"to provide."
msgstr ""
"Izberite med :guilabel:`Prosti vnos` in :guilabel:`Prosti vnos (večvrstni)` "
"glede na vrsto in količino informacij, ki jih mora obiskovalec zagotoviti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:151
msgid "Create Lead"
msgstr "Ustvari potencialno stranko"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:153
msgid ""
"This step creates a lead in the **CRM** application. Select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Team` drop-down field that appears to assign the "
"created lead to a specific team."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak ustvari potencialno stranko v aplikaciji **CRM**. Izberite možnost "
"iz spustnega polja :guilabel:`Prodajna ekipa`, ki se pojavi, da dodelit "
"ustvarjeno potencialno stranko določeni ekipi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:157
msgid ""
"This step is only available if the **CRM** application is installed on the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak je na voljo samo, če je aplikacija **CRM** nameščena v zbirko "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:160
msgid "Create Ticket"
msgstr "Ustvari zahtevek"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:162
msgid ""
"This step creates a :doc:`ticket <../../services/helpdesk/overview/"
"receiving_tickets>` in the **Helpdesk** application. Select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Helpdesk Team` drop-down field that appears to assign the "
"created ticket to a specific team."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak ustvari :doc:`zahtevek <../../services/helpdesk/overview/"
"receiving_tickets>` v aplikaciji **Služba za pomoč**. Izberite možnost iz "
"spustnega polja :guilabel:`Ekipa službe za pomoč`, ki se pojavi, da dodelite "
"ustvarjen zahtevek določeni ekipi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:167
msgid ""
"This step is only available if the **Helpdesk** application is installed on "
"the database."
msgstr ""
"Ta korak je na voljo samo, če je aplikacija **Služba za pomoč** nameščena v "
"zbirko podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:172
msgid "Only if"
msgstr "Samo če"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:174
msgid ""
"Chatbot scripts operate on an if/then basis, which means the next question "
"presented to the visitor is determined by the answer provided to the "
"previous question."
msgstr ""
"Skripte klepetalnih robotov delujejo na osnovi če/potem, kar pomeni, da je "
"naslednje vprašanje, predstavljeno obiskovalcu, določeno z odgovorom, "
"podanim na prejšnje vprašanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:177
msgid ""
"To continue the progression of the conversation, the :guilabel:`Create "
"Script Steps` form for a new step contains a field labeled :guilabel:`Only "
"If`. This field is where the progression of questions are defined."
msgstr ""
"Za nadaljevanje napredovanja pogovora obrazec :guilabel:`Ustvari korake "
"skripta` za nov korak vsebuje polje z oznako :guilabel:`Samo če`. To polje "
"je kraj, kjer je določeno zaporedje vprašanj."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:181
msgid ""
"If a step is intended to follow all of the previous messages, this field can "
"be left empty. However, if a message should only be sent conditionally, "
"based on a previous response, or several previous responses, those responses "
"**must** be added to this field."
msgstr ""
"Če je namenjen korak slediti vsem prejšnjim sporočilom, lahko to polje "
"ostane prazno. Vendar če naj se sporočilo pošlje samo pogojno, na osnovi "
"prejšnjega odziva ali več prejšnjih odzivov, **morajo** biti ti odzivi "
"dodani v to polje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:186
msgid ""
"If any selections are made in the :guilabel:`Only If` field, they must all "
"be selected during the conversation before this step is included. Only "
"include selections in this field if they are necessary for this step to be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če so opravljene kakršnekoli izbire v polju :guilabel:`Samo če`, morajo biti "
"vse izbrane med pogovorom, preden je ta korak vključen. V to polje vključite "
"samo izbire, če so potrebne za prikaz tega koraka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:191
msgid ""
"In the *Welcome Bot* script, a visitor can ask about pricing information. If "
"the visitor selects this response, a step is included to forward the "
"conversation to an operator. The chatbot first sends a message informing the "
"visitor that it is checking to see if an operator is available to assist "
"with pricing information."
msgstr ""
"V skripti *Pozdravn robot* lahko obiskovalec vpraša o cenovnih informacijah. "
"Če obiskovalec izbere ta odziv, se vključi korak za posredovanje pogovora "
"operaterju. Klepetaln robot najprej pošlje sporočilo, ki obvesti "
"obiskovalca, da preverja, ali je operater na voljo za pomoč pri cenovnih "
"informacijah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:196
msgid ""
"However, this message should only be delivered if the visitor requests "
"pricing information. In that situation, the conversation would proceed as "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Vendar naj se to sporočilo dostavi samo, če obiskovalec zahteva cenovne "
"informacije. V tej situaciji bi pogovor potekal, kot sledi:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:199
msgid "Welcome Bot: \"*What are you looking for?*\""
msgstr "Bot pozdravljenja: \"*Kaj iščete?*\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:200
msgid "Visitor: \"**I have a pricing question.**\""
msgstr "Obiskovalec: \"**Imam vprašanje o cenah.**\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:201
msgid ""
"Welcome Bot: \"*Hmmm, let me check if I can find someone that could help you "
"with that...*\""
msgstr ""
"Bot pozdravljenja: \"*Hmmm, naj preverim, če lahko najdem nekoga, ki bi vam "
"lahko pri tem pomagal ...*\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:203
msgid ""
"In the details form for the :guilabel:`Text` step, the *I have a pricing "
"question* response has been selected in the :guilabel:`Only If` field. As "
"such, this step is only shown in conversations where that response has been "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu s podrobnostmi za korak :guilabel:`Besedilo` je bila v "
"polju :guilabel:`Samo če` izbrana odločitev *Imam vprašanje o cenah*. Zato "
"se ta korak prikaže le v pogovorih, kjer je bila izbrana ta odločitev."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "View of the new message form emphasizing the Only If field."
msgstr "Pogled obrazca za novo sporočilo s poudarkom na polju Samo če."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:211
msgid "Script testing"
msgstr "Preizkušanje skripta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:213
msgid ""
"To ensure all visitors have a satisfactory experience with the chatbot, each "
"message needs to lead to a natural conclusion. Chatbot scripts should be "
"tested to confirm there are no dead-ends, and to understand what the visitor "
"sees when they interact with the chatbot."
msgstr ""
"Da bi zagotovili, da imajo vsi obiskovalci zadovoljivo izkušnjo s "
"klepetalnikom, mora vsako sporočilo voditi do naravnega zaključka. Skripte "
"klepetalnika je treba preizkusiti, da se potrdi, da ni slepih ulic in da "
"razumemo, kaj vidi obiskovalec, ko komunicira s klepetalnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:218
msgid ""
"If the visitor provides an answer, or input, that is not assigned a "
"corresponding follow-up response, the conversation stops (*dead-ends*). "
"Since the visitor cannot re-engage the chatbot, they must restart the "
"conversation by refreshing the chat window, or their browser. They may also "
"click on the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon at the top of the "
"message window."
msgstr ""
"Če obiskovalec poda odgovor ali vnos, ki nima dodeljenega ustreznega "
"nadaljevalnega odziva, se pogovor ustavi (*slepa ulica*). Ker obiskovalec ne "
"more ponovno aktivirati klepetalnika, mora pogovor ponovno začeti z "
"osveževanjem okna za klepet ali brskalnika. Lahko tudi klikne na "
"ikono :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(osveži)` na vrhu okna za sporočila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "The refresh button at the top of the message window."
msgstr "Gumb za osvežitev na vrhu okna za sporočila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:226
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-refresh` (refresh) icon only appears when the chatbot script "
"has reached a dead-end."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-refresh` (osveži) se prikaže le, ko je skript klepetalnika "
"dosegel slepo ulico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:229
msgid ""
"To test the performance of a chatbot, first click on the :guilabel:`Test` "
"button at the top-left of the chatbot script page. Then, upon being "
"redirected to the testing screen, answer the chatbot prompts the same way a "
"potential site visitor would."
msgstr ""
"Za preizkušanje delovanja klepetalnika najprej kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Preizkusi` zgoraj levo na strani skripta klepetalnika. Nato, "
"ko boste preusmerjeni na preizkusni zaslon, odgovorite na pozive "
"klepetalnika na način, kot bi to storil potencialni obiskovalec spletnega "
"mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:233
msgid ""
"When the script has reached an end-point, the message *Conversation "
"ended...* appears at the bottom of the chat window. To begin the "
"conversation at the beginning of the script, click on the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon at the top of the message window. To "
"return to the script page, click :guilabel:`Back to edit mode` at the top of "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Ko skript doseže končno točko, se na dnu okna za klepet prikaže sporočilo "
"*Pogovor končan ...*. Za začetek pogovora na začetku skripta kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(osveži)` na vrhu okna za sporočila. Za "
"vrnitev na stran skripta kliknite :guilabel:`Nazaj v način urejanja` na vrhu "
"strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:239
msgid "Add chatbot to a channel"
msgstr "Dodaj klepetalnika v kanal"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:241
msgid ""
"After a chatbot has been created and tested, it needs to be added to a live "
"chat channel."
msgstr ""
"Ko je klepetalnik ustvarjen in preizkušen, ga je treba dodati v kanal za "
"klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:243
msgid ""
"First, open the :menuselection:`Live Chat` application, find the Kanban card "
"for the appropriate live chat channel, hover over it, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon to open the "
"drop-down menu. Click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel "
"detail form."
msgstr ""
"Najprej odprite aplikacijo :menuselection:`Klepet v živo`, poiščite kartico "
"Kanban za ustrezen kanal za klepet v živo, se z miško pomaknite čeznjo in "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri pika)`, da "
"odprete spustni meni. Kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj kanal`, da odprete "
"obrazec s podrobnostmi kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:249
msgid ""
"To create a new live chat channel, open the :menuselection:`Live Chat app` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`. See :doc:`Live Chat <../livechat>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega kanala za klepet v živo "
"odprite :menuselection:`aplikacijo Klepet v živo` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Za več informacij glejte :doc:`Klepet v živo <../"
"livechat>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click on the :guilabel:`Channel Rules` tab. Then, open an existing rule, or "
"create a new one by clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Pravila kanala`. Nato odprite obstoječe pravilo "
"ali ustvarite novo tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:255
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window, choose the appropriate "
"chatbot in the :guilabel:`Chatbot` field."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari pravila` izberite ustreznega klepetalnika "
"v polju :guilabel:`Klepetalnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:258
msgid ""
"If the chatbot should only be active if there are no live chat operators "
"available, check the box labeled :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator`."
msgstr ""
"Če naj bo klepetalnik aktiven le, če ni na voljo operaterjev za klepet v "
"živo, označite polje :guilabel:`Omogočeno le, če ni operaterja`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
msgid "View of the channel rules emphasizing the chatbot field."
msgstr "Pogled pravil kanala s poudarkom na polju klepetalnik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:265
msgid ":doc:`Live chat channel rules </applications/websites/livechat>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Pravila kanala za klepet v živo </applications/websites/livechat>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:118
msgid "Expertise"
msgstr "Strokovno znanje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo's **Live Chat**, agents can designate *expertise* in one or more "
"areas. This allows conversations to be assigned to them based on their scope "
"of knowledge."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo **Live Chat** lahko agenti določijo *strokovnost* na enem ali več "
"področjih. To omogoča dodeljevanje pogovorov glede na obseg njihovega znanja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:8
msgid ""
"When a visitor requests help on a specific topic, Odoo can automatically "
"assign the conversation to an available agent with that expertise. Expertise "
"improves routing efficiency, reduces wait time, and ensures customers speak "
"to the most qualified person available."
msgstr ""
"Ko obiskovalec zaprosi za pomoč pri določeni temi, lahko Odoo samodejno "
"dodeli pogovor razpoložljivemu agentu s to strokovnostjo. Strokovnost "
"izboljša učinkovitost usmerjanja, zmanjša čas čakanja in zagotovi, da "
"stranke govorijo z najbolj usposobljeno razpoložljivo osebo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:13
msgid "Create a new expertise"
msgstr "Ustvarite novo strokovnost"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:15
msgid ""
"To create a new expertise, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Expertise` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter "
"a :guilabel:`Name` for the area of focus."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove strokovnosti pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Live "
"Chat --> Konfiguracija --> Strokovnost` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. "
"Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime` za področje usmeritve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:18
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Operators`, select one or more users from the drop-down to "
"assign this expertise."
msgstr ""
"Pod :guilabel:`Operaterji` izberite enega ali več uporabnikov s spustnega "
"seznama, da jim dodelite to strokovnost."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:21
msgid ""
"*Administrator* level :doc:`access <../../general/users/access_rights>` is "
"required in the **Live Chat** application to create or edit expertise. Those "
"with *User* level access can view the expertise menu and see which users are "
"assigned to each expertise, but they cannot make changes."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje ali urejanje strokovnosti je potreben :doc:`dostop <../../"
"general/users/access_rights>` na ravni *Administrator* v aplikaciji **Live "
"Chat**. Tisti z dostopom na ravni *Uporabnik* lahko pregledujejo meni "
"strokovnosti in vidijo, kateri uporabniki so dodeljeni vsaki strokovnosti, "
"vendar ne morejo izvajati sprememb."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:53
msgid "Set live chat expertise"
msgstr "Nastavite strokovno znanje za klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:28
msgid ""
"To set a user's live chat expertise, click on the user avatar in the top-"
"right corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Preferences` "
"from the drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, select one or more options from "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Expertise` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev strokovnosti uporabnika za klepet v živo kliknite na avatar "
"uporabnika v zgornjem desnem kotu katere koli strani v bazi podatkov. V "
"spustnem meniju izberite :guilabel:`Moje preference`, da odprete stran "
"profila. Na desni strani zavihka :guilabel:`Preference` izberite eno ali več "
"možnosti s spustnega seznama :guilabel:`Strokovnost za klepet v živo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid "A user profile with the Live Chat Expertise menu open."
msgstr "Uporabniški profil z odprtim menijem Strokovnost za klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:37
msgid "Forward conversations based on expertise"
msgstr "Posredujte pogovore glede na strokovnost"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:39
msgid ""
"Once an expertise has been assigned to one or more operators, they can be "
"used to forward conversations. This allows a chatbot to identify the "
"operator who is best suited to handle a customer request."
msgstr ""
"Ko je strokovnost dodeljena enemu ali več operaterjem, jo je mogoče "
"uporabiti za posredovanje pogovorov. To omogoča klepetalnem robotu, da "
"prepozna operaterja, ki je najprimernejši za obravnavo zahteve stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:44
msgid "Forward via chatbot"
msgstr "Posreduj prek klepetalnega robota"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:46
msgid ""
":doc:`Chatbots <chatbots>` are designed to mimic a conversation with a live "
"human, and operate based on a pre-written script of steps to follow. "
"The :ref:`Forward to Operator <chatbot/forward-to-operator>` step type is "
"used to send a conversation from a chatbot to an active live chat agent who "
"can then continue the conversation based on where the chatbot left off. By "
"adding expertise to this step, the chatbot will first look for an agent with "
"matching expertise, to ensure the agent is the best person for the situation."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Klepetalni roboti <chatbots>` so zasnovani tako, da posnemajo pogovor "
"z živo osebo in delujejo na podlagi vnaprej napisanega scenarija korakov. "
"Tip koraka :ref:`Posreduj operaterju <chatbot/forward-to-operator>` se "
"uporablja za pošiljanje pogovora s klepetalnega robota aktivnemu agentu za "
"klepet v živo, ki lahko nato nadaljuje pogovor tam, kjer se je klepetalnega "
"robot končal. Z dodajanjem strokovnosti temu koraku bo klepetalnega robot "
"najprej poiskal agenta z ujemajočo se strokovnostjo, da zagotovi, da je "
"agent najboljša oseba za situacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:53
msgid ""
"To add expertise to a chatbot conversation, navigate to :menuselection:`Live "
"Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`. Click on an existing chatbot to "
"open it, or click :guilabel:`New` to :ref:`create a new one <chatbot/build-a-"
"chatbot>`."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje strokovnosti pogovoru s klepetalnim robotom pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Live Chat --> Konfiguracija --> Klepetalni "
"roboti`. Kliknite na obstoječega klepetalnega robota, da ga odprete, ali "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da :ref:`ustvarite novega <chatbot/build-a-"
"chatbot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:57
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Script` tab, if there is an existing *Forward to Operator* "
"step, click on it. If not, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then select "
"*Forward to Operator* in the :guilabel:`Step Type` field."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`Scenarij`, če obstaja korak *Posreduj operaterju*, "
"kliknite nanj. Če ne, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, nato izberite "
"*Posreduj operaterju* v polju :guilabel:`Tip koraka`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:61
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Operator Expertise` field, select one or more expertise "
"for the chatbot to consider when prioritizing users for conversations on the "
"related channel. Click :guilabel:`Save` when finished."
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Strokovnost operaterja` izberite eno ali več "
"strokovnosti, ki naj jih klepetalnega robot upošteva pri določanju prednosti "
"uporabnikov za pogovore na povezanem kanalu. Ko končate, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:66
msgid ""
"When making selections in this field, consider the use case for the chatbot. "
"A *Support* chatbot will cover different topics than a *Recruitment* chatbot."
msgstr ""
"Pri izbiri v tem polju upoštevajte primer uporabe klepetalnega robota. "
"Klepetalnega robot za *podporo* bo obravnaval različne teme kot klepetalnega "
"robot za *zaposlovanje*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid "A forward to operator script step pop-up."
msgstr "Pojavno okno koraka scenarija posredovanja operaterju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:73
msgid "Add users to a conversation"
msgstr "Dodajte uporabnike v pogovor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:75
msgid ""
"Users can add other live chat agents to an ongoing conversation directly "
"from the chat window. Open an active live chat conversation through "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. At the top-right of the chat, click "
"the :icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(user plus)` icon to open the *Invite "
"People* menu. The user's expertise is listed next to the :icon:`fa-"
"graduation-cap` :guilabel:`(graduation cap)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki lahko druge agente za klepet v živo dodajo v tekoči pogovor "
"neposredno iz okna klepeta. Odprite aktivni pogovor klepeta v živo "
"prek :menuselection:`Aplikacije Discuss`. V zgornjem desnem kotu klepeta "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(uporabnik plus)`, da odprete "
"meni *Povabi osebe*. Strokovnost uporabnika je navedena poleg "
"ikone :icon:`fa-graduation-cap` :guilabel:`(kapa)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid "The add users menu in a live chat conversation."
msgstr "Meni za dodajanje uporabnikov v pogovoru klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:84
msgid ""
"To add a user to the conversation, tick the checkbox to the right of the "
"user's name, then click :guilabel:`Invite`."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje uporabnika v pogovor označite potrditveno polje na desni strani "
"uporabnikovega imena, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Povabi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:88
msgid ""
"*Expertise* only appear on the *Invite People* pop-up for live chat "
"conversations, not direct messages."
msgstr ""
"*Strokovnost* se pojavi v pojavnem oknu *Povabi osebe* samo za pogovore "
"klepeta v živo, ne za neposredna sporočila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:92
msgid "Looking for help conversations"
msgstr "Iskanje pogovorov za pomoč"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:94
msgid ""
"In an active livechat conversation, the :ref:`Status <information/status>` "
"can be set to allow agents to identify conversations that require immediate "
"action, and inform other agents which conversations require their expertise "
"at any given time. If a conversation is marked with the status *Looking for "
"help*, other agents have the opportunity to join."
msgstr ""
"V aktivnem pogovoru v živem klepetu je mogoče nastaviti :ref:`Status "
"<information/status>`, da lahko agenti prepoznajo pogovore, ki zahtevajo "
"takojšnje ukrepanje, in obvestijo druge agente, kateri pogovori zahtevajo "
"njihovo strokovno znanje. Če je pogovor označen s statusom *Iskanje pomoči*, "
"imajo drugi agenti možnost, da se pridružijo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:99
msgid ""
"To view *Looking for help* conversations, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. Conversations with the status appear under "
"the *Looking for help* heading."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled pogovorov *Iskanje pomoči* pojdite v :menuselection:`aplikacijo "
"Discuss`. Pogovori s tem statusom se prikažejo pod naslovom *Iskanje pomoči*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:102
msgid ""
"If an agent has a matching expertise, the conversation is marked with "
"a :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`(star)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Če ima agent ustrezno strokovno znanje, je pogovor označen z ikono :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(zvezdica)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid ""
"A conversation with the looking for help status and relevant expertise "
"tagged."
msgstr ""
"Pogovor s statusom Iskanje pomoči in označenim ustreznim strokovnim znanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:109
msgid ""
"*Looking for help* conversations can also be viewed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Sessions --> Looking for Help`."
msgstr ""
"Pogovore *Iskanje pomoči* si lahko ogledate tudi tako, da pojdete "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Živi klepet --> Seje --> Iskanje pomoči`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:112
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:79
msgid ""
"To join a conversation in progress, click the :icon:`fa-sign-"
"in` :guilabel:`(sign in)` icon at the top of the information panel. Doing so "
"moves the conversation back to the channel heading and reverts the status to "
"*In progress*. The customer is also informed that a new user has joined the "
"chat."
msgstr ""
"Za pridružitev potekajočemu pogovoru kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-sign-"
"in` :guilabel:`(prijava)` na vrhu informacijske plošče. S tem se pogovor "
"vrne nazaj pod naslov kanala in status se spremeni nazaj na *V teku*. "
"Stranko se tudi obvesti, da se je novemu uporabniku pridružil klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:3
msgid "Information panel"
msgstr "Informacijska plošča"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Live Chat** information panel provides agents with the context they "
"need to handle live chat conversations efficiently. It gathers key "
"information about the visitor and the conversation history, allowing agents "
"to respond faster and avoid repetitive messaging."
msgstr ""
"Informacijska plošča **Klepeta v živo** agentom zagotavlja kontekst, ki ga "
"potrebujejo za učinkovito obravnavo pogovorov v klepetu v živo. Zbira "
"ključne informacije o obiskovalcu in zgodovini pogovora ter agentom omogoča "
"hitrejše odzivanje in izogibanje ponavljajočim se sporočilom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:10
msgid "Accessing the info panel"
msgstr "Dostop do informacijske plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:12
msgid ""
"To view the info panel, open a live chat conversation either in the "
"**Discuss** app or the **Live Chat** app. Live chat discussions in the "
"**Discuss** app are listed on the left side panel, under the title of the "
"live chat channel where the conversation began. In the **Live Chat** app, "
"conversations can be accessed by navigating to :menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Sessions --> All Conversations`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled informacijske plošče odprite pogovor v klepetu v živo bodisi v "
"aplikaciji **Discuss** ali aplikaciji **Klepet v živo**. Pogovori klepeta v "
"živo v aplikaciji **Discuss** so navedeni na levem stranskem panelu pod "
"naslovom kanala klepeta v živo, kjer se je pogovor začel. V aplikaciji "
"**Klepet v živo** je do pogovorov mogoče dostopati tako, da se pomaknete "
"na :menuselection:`Klepet v živo --> Seje --> Vsi pogovori`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:18
msgid ""
"The information panel appears on the right side of the conversation. Click "
"the :icon:`fa-info` :guilabel:`(information)` icon to toggle the info panel "
"open or closed."
msgstr ""
"Informacijska plošča se prikaže na desni strani pogovora. Kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-info` :guilabel:`(informacije)`, da preklopite informacijsko "
"ploščo v odprto ali zaprto stanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The information panel for a known contact."
msgstr "Informacijska plošča za znanega stika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:25
msgid "Contact information"
msgstr "Informacije o stiku"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:27
msgid ""
"If the live chat conversation involves a known contact, a :guilabel:`View "
"Contact` button appears at the top of the panel. Clicking this button opens "
"the :doc:`contact record <../../essentials/contacts>` for the customer, "
"without closing the conversation. The contact record links to the customers' "
"sales, invoices, meetings, and previous live chat sessions."
msgstr ""
"Če pogovor v klepetu v živo vključuje znanega stika, se na vrhu plošče "
"prikaže gumb :guilabel:`Ogled stika`. Klik na ta gumb odpre :doc:`zapis "
"stika <../../essentials/contacts>` za stranko, ne da bi zaprl pogovor. Zapis "
"stika se povezuje s prodajami strank, računi, sestanki in prejšnjimi sejami "
"klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:35
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Status"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:37
msgid ""
"In an active livechat conversation, the *Status* can be set to allow agents "
"to identify conversations that require immediate action, and inform other "
"agents which conversations require their expertise at any given time."
msgstr ""
"V aktivnem pogovoru klepeta v živo je mogoče *Status* nastaviti, da lahko "
"agenti prepoznajo pogovore, ki zahtevajo takojšnje ukrepanje, in obvestijo "
"druge agente, kateri pogovori kadarkoli zahtevajo njihovo strokovno znanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:42
msgid "In progress"
msgstr "V postopku"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:44
msgid ""
"The *In progress* status is the default status for a conversation. This "
"status indicates that the customer is waiting for a response from an agent."
msgstr ""
"Status *V teku* je privzeti status za pogovor. Ta status označuje, da "
"stranka čaka na odziv agenta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:48
msgid ""
"If a conversation is set to *Waiting for customer*, it will revert to *In "
"progress* as soon as the customer sends a new message."
msgstr ""
"Če je pogovor nastavljen na *Čakanje na stranko*, se bo takoj vrnil na *V "
"teku*, ko bo stranka poslala novo sporočilo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:52
msgid "Waiting for customer"
msgstr "Čakanje na stranko"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:54
msgid ""
"The *Waiting for customer* status indicates that an agent has sent a message "
"to the customer and is waiting for a response. When this status is applied, "
"the conversation is highlighted in yellow with a :icon:`fa-hourglass-"
"start` :guilabel:`(hourglass)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Status *Čakanje na stranko* označuje, da je agent poslal sporočilo stranki "
"in čaka na odziv. Ko je ta status uporabljen, je pogovor označen rumeno z "
"ikono :icon:`fa-hourglass-start` :guilabel:`(peščena ura)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "A conversation with the waiting for customer status."
msgstr "Pogovor s statusom čakanje na stranko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:62
msgid "The *Waiting for customer* status **must** be manually applied."
msgstr "Status *Čakanje na stranko* **mora** biti ročno uporabljen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:65
msgid "Looking for help"
msgstr "Iskanje pomoči"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:67
msgid ""
"If a conversation is marked with the status *Looking for help*, it moves "
"from its original channel name heading to the *Looking for help* heading, "
"and the :icon:`fa-exclamation-circle` :guilabel:`(exclamation circle)` icon "
"is added. Any user with **Live Chat** permissions can view or join these "
"conversations, even if they are not currently active in a live chat channel."
msgstr ""
"Če je pogovor označen s statusom *Iskanje pomoči*, se premakne iz naslova "
"izvirnega kanala pod naslov *Iskanje pomoči* in doda se ikona :icon:`fa-"
"exclamation-circle` :guilabel:`(krog z klicajem)`. Vsak uporabnik z "
"dovoljenji za **Klepet v živo** lahko pregleduje ali se pridruži tem "
"pogovorom, tudi če trenutno ni aktiven v kanalu za klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:72
msgid ""
"If a conversation with the *Looking for help* status has an :ref:`expertise "
"<information/expertise>` listed that matches the user's, the conversation is "
"marked with a :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`(star)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Če ima pogovor s statusom *Iskanje pomoči* naveden :ref:`strokovni področje "
"<information/expertise>`, ki se ujema z uporabnikovim, je pogovor označen z "
"ikono :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`(zvezdica)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid ""
"The looking for help panel with a star marking conversations relevant to "
"user expertise."
msgstr ""
"Plošča za iskanje pomoči z zvezdico, ki označuje pogovore, relevantne za "
"uporabnikovo strokovno znanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:84
msgid ""
"If the icon does not appear, manually set the status to *In progress* to "
"inform other agents the conversation is being handled."
msgstr ""
"Če se ikona ne prikaže, ročno nastavite status na *V teku*, da obvestite "
"druge agente, da se pogovor obravnava."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:88
msgid ""
"All conversations that have been tagged with the status *Looking for help* "
"can be found by navigating to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Sessions --> "
"Looking for Help`. Use the filters to find the appropriate session date."
msgstr ""
"Vse pogovore, ki so bili označeni s statusom *Iskanje pomoči*, najdete tako, "
"da odprete :menuselection:`Aplikacija Klepet v živo --> Seje --> Iskanje "
"pomoči`. Uporabite filtre za iskanje ustreznega datuma seje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:93
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "Beležke"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Notes` field allows agents to leave comments about the "
"conversation, recap the situation when transferring it to another agent, or  "
"to add context to the conversation that can be viewed later in reporting."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Opombe` omogoča agentom, da pustijo komentarje o pogovoru, "
"povzamejo situacijo pri prenosu na drugega agenta ali dodajo kontekst "
"pogovoru, ki ga je mogoče pozneje pregledati v poročanju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:102
msgid ""
"Tags can be added to a conversation to assist with categorizing, tracking "
"issues, and enhancing reporting. Click :guilabel:`Tags` :icon:`fa-plus`, "
"then select a tag from the list, or enter a new one in the field. Multiple "
"tags can be added to a single conversation."
msgstr ""
"Pogovoru je mogoče dodati oznake za pomoč pri kategorizaciji, sledenju "
"težavam in izboljšanju poročanja. Kliknite :guilabel:`Oznake` :icon:`fa-"
"plus`, nato izberite oznako s seznama ali vnesite novo v polje. Enemu "
"pogovoru je mogoče dodati več oznak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:107
msgid "Chatbot answers"
msgstr "Odgovori klepetalnega robota"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:109
msgid ""
"If the conversation was forwarded from a chatbot, the answers selected from "
"the chatbot are included on the information panel under *Chatbot answers*."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil pogovor posredovan iz klepetalnega robota, so odgovori, izbrani iz "
"klepetalnega robota, vključeni na informacijski plošči pod *Odgovori "
"klepetalnega robota*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The chatbot answers section of the information panel."
msgstr "Oddelek z odgovori klepetalnega robota na informacijski plošči."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Expertise` field allows agents to designate the topic of "
"conversation to a specific skillset or knowledge scope. This helps to "
"categorize the conversation for assignment purposes, as well as issue "
"tacking and enchanced reporting. Click into the field and select one or more "
"options from the drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Strokovnost` omogoča agentom, da temo pogovora dodelijo "
"določenemu naboru veščin ali obsegu znanja. To pomaga pri kategorizaciji "
"pogovora za namene dodelitve, kot tudi pri sledenju težavam in izboljšanem "
"poročanju. Kliknite v polje in izberite eno ali več možnosti s spustnega "
"seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:126
msgid "Country & language"
msgstr "Država in jezik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:128
msgid ""
"The *Country & Language* section identifies where the customer is located, "
"and their language. A visitor's language is determined via their browser's "
"language settings."
msgstr ""
"Oddelek *Država in jezik* določa, kje se stranka nahaja, in njen jezik. "
"Jezik obiskovalca se določi prek jezikovnih nastavitev brskalnika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:132
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:39
msgid ""
"Conversations are assigned to operators based on a number of criteria, "
"including availability and the number of ongoing conversations. While the "
"operator's main language and additional languages are taken into "
"consideration, they do **not** supersede all other criteria."
msgstr ""
"Pogovori se operaterjem dodelijo na podlagi številnih meril, vključno z "
"razpoložljivostjo in številom potekajočih pogovorov. Čeprav se upoštevata "
"operaterjev glavni jezik in dodatni jeziki, **ne** prevladajo nad vsemi "
"drugimi merili."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:137
msgid "Recent conversations"
msgstr "Nedavni pogovori"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:139
msgid ""
"Any recent live chat conversations with this customer also appear in the "
"information panel. Click on the :icon:`fa-external-"
"link` :guilabel:`(external link)` icon on the ticket title to open the "
"conversation in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Vsi nedavni pogovori v klepetu v živo s to stranko se prav tako prikažejo na "
"informacijski plošči. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-external-"
"link` :guilabel:`(zunanja povezava)` na naslovu zahtevka, da odprete pogovor "
"v novem zavihku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The recent conversations field on the information panel."
msgstr "Polje z nedavnimi pogovori na informacijski plošči."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:147
msgid "Open tickets"
msgstr "Odprti zahtevki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:149
msgid ""
"Any open **Helpdesk** tickets created by the customer also appear in the "
"information panel. Click on the :icon:`fa-external-"
"link` :guilabel:`(external link)` icon on the ticket title to open the "
"ticket record in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Vsi odprti zahtevki **Službe za pomoč**, ki jih je ustvarila stranka, se "
"prav tako prikažejo na informacijski plošči. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"external-link` :guilabel:`(zunanja povezava)` na naslovu zahtevka, da "
"odprete zapis zahtevka v novem zavihku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The open ticket field on the information panel."
msgstr "Polje odprtega zahtevka na informacijskem panelu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:157
msgid "Outcome"
msgstr "Izid"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:159
msgid ""
"For closed conversations, the *Outcome* field defines how the conversation "
"concluded:"
msgstr "Za zaprte pogovore polje *Izid* določa, kako se je pogovor zaključil:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:161
msgid ""
"*No Answer*: assigned when the customer does not respond to the agent. This "
"usually occurs when the session is initiated, but the customer does not "
"engage or send additional messages."
msgstr ""
"*Ni odgovora*: dodeljeno, ko stranka ne odgovori operaterju. To se običajno "
"zgodi, ko se seja začne, vendar stranka ne sodeluje ali ne pošlje dodatnih "
"sporočil."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:163
msgid ""
"*No One Available*: assigned when no agents are available to respond to the "
"customer. This occurs when the session is initiated, but no operator is "
"online or available to be assigned to the chat."
msgstr ""
"*Nihče ni na voljo*: dodeljeno, ko ni na voljo nobenega operaterja za "
"odgovor stranki. To se zgodi, ko se seja začne, vendar noben operater ni "
"povezan ali na voljo za dodelitev klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:165
msgid ""
"*Success*: assigned when the live chat session is completed successfully. "
"This outcome does **not** depend the customer providing a positive rating, "
"it is dependent on the session being resolved without escalation or failure."
msgstr ""
"*Uspešno*: dodeljeno, ko se seja klepeta v živo uspešno zaključi. Ta izid "
"**ni** odvisen od pozitivne ocene stranke, ampak od tega, da se seja razreši "
"brez eskalacije ali neuspeha."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:168
msgid ""
"*Escalated*: assigned when the session is forwarded to another operator. "
"This indicates the initial operator could not resolve the issue, and "
"required assistance."
msgstr ""
"*Eskalirano*: dodeljeno, ko je seja posredovana drugemu operaterju. To "
"pomeni, da začetni operater ni mogel rešiti težave in je potreboval pomoč."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:172
msgid "Send conversation"
msgstr "Pošlji pogovor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:174
msgid ""
"When the conversation is complete, scroll to the bottom of the info panel. "
"The email address in the field can be edited to send to a different "
"address.click the :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(paper plane)` icon to "
"send a copy of the conversation transcript."
msgstr ""
"Ko je pogovor zaključen, se pomaknite na dno informacijskega panela. E-"
"poštni naslov v polju lahko uredite, če želite poslati na drug naslov. "
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(papirnato letalo)`, da "
"pošljete kopijo prepisa pogovora."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The send conversation button at the bottom of the info panel."
msgstr "Gumb za pošiljanje pogovora na dnu informacijskega panela."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:3
msgid "Participate in live chat"
msgstr "Sodelujte v klepetu v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Operators* are the users who respond to live chat requests from customers "
"and website visitors. The information below outlines the necessary steps for "
"operators participating in live chat conversations on an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"*Operaterji* so uporabniki, ki se odzivajo na zahteve za klepet v živo "
"strank in obiskovalcev spletne strani. Spodnje informacije opisujejo "
"potrebne korake za operaterje, ki sodelujejo v pogovorih klepeta v živo v "
"podatkovni bazi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:10
msgid "Set an online chat name"
msgstr "Nastavite ime za spletni klepet"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:12
msgid ""
"Before participating in a live chat, operators may choose to update their "
"*Online Chat Name*. This is the name displayed to site visitors in the live "
"chat conversation."
msgstr ""
"Preden sodelujejo v klepetu v živo, lahko operaterji posodobijo svoje *ime "
"za spletni klepet*. To je ime, ki se obiskovalcem spletnega mesta prikaže v "
"pogovoru klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:15
msgid ""
"To update the *Online Chat Name*, click on the user avatar in the top-right "
"corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, locate the :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` "
"field, and enter a preferred name."
msgstr ""
"Za posodobitev *imena za spletni klepet* kliknite na avatar uporabnika v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu katerekoli strani v podatkovni bazi. V spustnem meniju "
"izberite :guilabel:`Moj profil`, da odprete stran profila. Na desni strani "
"zavihka :guilabel:`Nastavitve` poiščite polje :guilabel:`Ime za spletni "
"klepet` in vnesite želeno ime."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:20
msgid ""
"If a user's :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` is not set, the name displayed "
"defaults to the user's name that is designated on their profile page."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabnikovo :guilabel:`ime za spletni klepet` ni nastavljeno, se "
"privzeto prikaže ime uporabnika, ki je določeno na njegovi strani profila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:24
msgid ""
"A user has their full name as their :guilabel:`User Name`, but they do not "
"want to include their last name in a live chat conversation. They would then "
"set their :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` to include only their first name."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik ima kot :guilabel:`uporabniško ime` polno ime, vendar ne želi "
"vključiti priimka v pogovor klepeta v živo. V tem primeru bi "
"nastavil :guilabel:`ime za spletni klepet`, da vključuje samo svoje ime."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:0
msgid "View of user profile in Odoo, emphasizing the Online Chat name field."
msgstr ""
"Pogled uporabniškega profila v Odoo z poudarkom na polju za ime za spletni "
"klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:32
msgid "Set online chat languages"
msgstr "Nastavite jezike za spletni klepet"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:34
msgid ""
"If an operator speaks multiple languages, they can add this information to "
"their user profile. This information can then be used to determine which "
"conversations the operator is assigned. A visitor's language is determined "
"via their browser's language settings."
msgstr ""
"Če operater govori več jezikov, lahko te informacije doda na svoj "
"uporabniški profil. Te informacije se nato lahko uporabijo za določanje, "
"katerim pogovorom je operater dodeljen. Jezik obiskovalca se določi na "
"podlagi jezikovnih nastavitev njegovega brskalnika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:43
msgid ""
"To add *Online Chat Languages*, click on the user avatar in the top-right "
"corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, click into the :guilabel:`Online Chat "
"Language` field, and select one or more languages from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje *jezikov za spletni klepet* kliknite na avatar uporabnika v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu katerekoli strani v podatkovni bazi. V spustnem meniju "
"izberite :guilabel:`Moj profil`, da odprete stran profila. Na desni strani "
"zavihka :guilabel:`Nastavitve` kliknite v polje :guilabel:`Jezik za spletni "
"klepet` in v spustnem meniju izberite enega ali več jezikov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:49
msgid ""
"Only :doc:`languages <../../general/users/language>` that are enabled on the "
"database can be selected in the :guilabel:`Online Chat Language` field."
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Jezik za spletni klepet` je mogoče izbrati "
"samo :doc:`jezike <../../general/users/language>`, ki so omogočeni v "
"podatkovni bazi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:55
msgid ""
"Operators can designate *Expertise* in one or more areas on their profile. "
"A :doc:`chatbot <chatbots>` can then assign conversations to the operator "
"with the appropriate expertise. Select one or more options from "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Expertise` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Operaterji lahko na svojem profilu določijo *strokovno znanje* na enem ali "
"več področjih. :doc:`Klepetalni robot <chatbots>` lahko nato pogovore dodeli "
"operaterju z ustreznim strokovnim znanjem. V spustnem "
"seznamu :guilabel:`Strokovno znanje za klepet v živo` izberite eno ali več "
"možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:59
msgid ""
"To create a new expertise, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Expertise` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`Name` of the expertise, and, if desired, select one or "
"more :guilabel:`Operators`. Click :guilabel:`Save` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega strokovnega znanja pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija za klepet v živo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Strokovno znanje` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Vnesite :guilabel:`ime` "
"strokovnega znanja in po želji izberite enega ali "
"več :guilabel:`operaterjev`. Ko končate, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:64
msgid ""
"When forwarding live chat conversations, the chatbot prioritizes users with "
"matching expertise. If no applicable match is found, the chatbot forwards "
"the conversation to the next available operator."
msgstr ""
"Pri posredovanju pogovorov klepeta v živo ima klepetalni robot prednost "
"uporabnikom z ujemajočim se strokovnim znanjem. Če ustreznega ujemanja ni "
"mogoče najti, klepetalni robot posreduje pogovor naslednjemu razpoložljivemu "
"operaterju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:69
msgid "Join or leave a channel"
msgstr "Pridružite se kanalu ali ga zapustite"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:71
msgid ""
"To join a live chat channel, go to the :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Channels`, and click the :guilabel:`Join` button on the Kanban card for the "
"appropriate channel."
msgstr ""
"Za pridružitev kanalu za klepet v živo pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"za klepet v živo --> Kanali` in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Pridruži se` na "
"kartici Kanban za ustrezen kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:74
msgid ""
"Any channel where the user is currently active shows a :guilabel:`Leave` "
"button. Click this button to disconnect from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Vsak kanal, kjer je uporabnik trenutno aktiven, prikazuje "
"gumb :guilabel:`Zapusti`. Kliknite ta gumb, da se odjavite iz kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a channel form and the option to join a channel for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled obrazca kanala in možnost pridružitve kanalu za Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:81
msgid ""
"Operators that do not show any activity in Odoo for more than thirty minutes "
"are considered disconnected, and subsequently removed from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Operaterji, ki v Odoo ne kažejo nobene aktivnosti več kot trideset minut, se "
"štejejo za odklenjene in so posledično odstranjeni iz kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:85
msgid "Manage live chat requests"
msgstr "Upravljanje zahtevkov za klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:87
msgid ""
"When an operator is active in a channel, chat windows open in the bottom-"
"right corner of the screen, no matter where they are in the database. This "
"allows them to access other pages and apps, while still participating in the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Ko je operater aktiven v kanalu, se okna klepeta odprejo v spodnjem desnem "
"kotu zaslona, ne glede na to, kje se nahajajo v zbirki podatkov. To jim "
"omogoča dostop do drugih strani in aplikacij, medtem ko še vedno sodelujejo "
"v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:91
msgid ""
"Live chat conversations can also be viewed by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. New conversations appear in bold under the "
"channel name, located along the left panel."
msgstr ""
"Pogovore v klepetu v živo si lahko ogledate tudi tako, da se pomaknete "
"na :menuselection:`aplikacijo Discuss`. Novi pogovori so prikazani krepko "
"pod imenom kanala, ki se nahaja v levem pultu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the discuss application with a message sent through live chat in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pogled aplikacije Discuss s sporočilom, poslanim prek klepeta v živo v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:97
msgid ""
"Click on a conversation in the left panel to select it. This opens the "
"conversation. From this view, an operator can participate in the chat the "
"same as they would in the normal chat window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite pogovor v levem pultu, da ga izberete. To odpre pogovor. S tega "
"pogleda lahko operater sodeluje v klepetu enako, kot bi v običajnem oknu "
"klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:101
msgid ""
"Conversations can also be accessed by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"comments` :guilabel:`(Messages)` icon in the menu bar."
msgstr ""
"Do pogovorov lahko dostopate tudi tako, da kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-"
"comments` :guilabel:`(Sporočila)` v menijski vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:0
msgid "View of the menu bar in Odoo emphasizing the comments icon."
msgstr "Pogled menijske vrstice v Odoo s poudarkom na ikoni za komentarje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:108
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:109
msgid ":doc:`../livechat`"
msgstr ":doc:`../livechat`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:110
msgid ":doc:`../livechat/responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`../livechat/responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:3
msgid "Ratings"
msgstr "Ocene"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:9
msgid ""
"At the end of a **Live Chat** conversation, customers have the opportunity "
"to rate the quality of support they received from the live chat *operator*. "
"Customers provide ratings as soon as they close the conversation. This "
"allows operators to receive immediate feedback on their performance. It also "
"allows customers to share any final comments before leaving the chat window."
msgstr ""
"Ob koncu pogovora **Live Chat** imajo stranke možnost oceniti kakovost "
"podpore, ki so jo prejele od *operaterja* klepeta v živo. Stranke podajo "
"ocene takoj, ko zaprejo pogovor. To operaterjem omogoča takojšnje povratne "
"informacije o njihovi uspešnosti. Prav tako omogoča strankam, da delijo "
"morebitne končne komentarje, preden zapustijo okno klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:15
msgid "Rate live chat conversations"
msgstr "Ocenjevanje pogovorov v klepetu v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:17
msgid ""
"Customers end a live chat conversation by clicking the :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(close)` icon in the upper right-hand corner of the chat "
"window. They are then prompted to select an icon that reflects their level "
"of satisfaction. The icons represent the following ratings:"
msgstr ""
"Stranke končajo pogovor v klepetu v živo tako, da kliknejo ikono :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(zapri)` v zgornjem desnem kotu okna klepeta. Nato so "
"pozvane, da izberejo ikono, ki odraža njihovo raven zadovoljstva. Ikone "
"predstavljajo naslednje ocene:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:21
msgid "**Satisfied** - |smile|"
msgstr "**Zadovoljen** - |smile|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:22
msgid "**Okay** - |meh|"
msgstr "**V redu** - |meh|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:23
msgid "**Dissatisfied** - |frown|"
msgstr "**Nezadovoljen** - |frown|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the chat window from a user's side for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled okna klepeta s strani uporabnika za Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:29
msgid ""
"When customers end a conversation, a field marked :guilabel:`Receive a copy "
"of this conversation` appears under the *ratings* icons. Customers can enter "
"their email either before or after they submit a rating."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranke končajo pogovor, se pod ikonami za *ocenjevanje* prikaže polje z "
"oznako :guilabel:`Prejmi kopijo tega pogovora`. Stranke lahko vnesejo svoj e-"
"poštni naslov pred ali po oddaji ocene."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:33
msgid ""
"If the customer selects the |smile|, they are presented with a thank you "
"message and a :guilabel:`Close Conversation` link."
msgstr ""
"Če stranka izbere |smile|, se ji prikaže zahvalno sporočilo in "
"povezava :guilabel:`Zapri pogovor`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of customer's live chat window with thank you message."
msgstr "Pogled okna klepeta v živo stranke s sporočilom zahvale."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:39
msgid ""
"If the customer selects either the |meh| or the |frown|, a text box appears. "
"Customers can add comments in this text box to explain why they chose this "
"rating. This message, along with the rating icon, is sent to the live chat "
"operator."
msgstr ""
"Če stranka izbere |meh| ali |frown|, se prikaže besedilno polje. Stranke "
"lahko v to besedilno polje dodajo komentarje, s katerimi pojasnijo, zakaj so "
"izbrale to oceno. To sporočilo skupaj z ikono ocene se pošlje operaterju "
"klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a chat window from an operator's window highlighting a rating for "
"Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Pogled okna klepeta iz okna operaterja z označeno oceno za Odoo klepet v "
"živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:47
msgid "Publish customer ratings"
msgstr "Objavi ocene strank"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:49
msgid ""
"To publish a channel's ratings on the website, first navigate to a live chat "
"channel's record by going to the :menuselection:`Live Chat` app and clicking "
"on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the "
"Kanban card for that team. Then, click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open "
"the channel details form. Then click on the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button. This opens the :guilabel:`Live Chat Channel Statistics` page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite objaviti ocene kanala na spletnem mestu, najprej odprite zapis "
"kanala za klepet v živo tako, da odprete aplikacijo :menuselection:`Klepet v "
"živo` in kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri-"
"pičje)` na Kanban kartici za to ekipo. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj "
"kanal`, da odprete obrazec s podrobnostmi kanala. Nato kliknite pametni "
"gumb :guilabel:`Pojdi na spletno mesto`. S tem se odpre "
"stran :guilabel:`Statistika kanala za klepet v živo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:55
msgid ""
"In the upper right corner of the page, click the red :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"slider. The slider changes from :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem desnem kotu strani kliknite rdeči "
"drsnik :guilabel:`Neobjavljeno`. Drsnik se spremeni "
"iz :guilabel:`Neobjavljeno` v :guilabel:`Objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the published ratings on the portal for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled objavljenih ocen na portalu za Odoo klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:62
msgid ""
"The customer notes submitted with the rating are *not* published on the "
"website; they are kept internal. Only a statistical overview of the "
"operators' performance for the *channel* appears on the website."
msgstr ""
"Opombe strank, oddane z oceno, *niso* objavljene na spletnem mestu; ostanejo "
"notranje. Na spletnem mestu se prikaže samo statistični pregled uspešnosti "
"operaterjev za *kanal*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:67
msgid "Add ratings page to site"
msgstr "Dodaj stran z ocenami na spletno mesto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:69
msgid ""
"Once the rating page has been published, it has to be manually added to the "
"website. To do this, go to the main Odoo dashboard and open the **Website** "
"application. :menuselection:`Website app --> Site --> Pages`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je stran z ocenami objavljena, jo je treba ročno dodati na spletno mesto. "
"Za to odprite glavno Nadzorno ploščo Odoo in odprite aplikacijo **Spletno "
"mesto**. :menuselection:`Aplikacija Spletno mesto --> Spletno mesto --> "
"Strani`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:73
msgid ""
"This opens a :guilabel:`New Page` pop-up window. In the :guilabel:`Page "
"Title` field, enter `livechat`. This acts as the URL for the published "
"webpage."
msgstr ""
"S tem se odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Nova stran`. V "
"polje :guilabel:`Naslov strani` vnesite `livechat`. To služi kot URL za "
"objavljeno spletno stran."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:77
msgid ""
"The URL *must* be named `livechat` in order for the database to recognize "
"and connect the ratings page. After the page has been published, the page "
"title can be changed later under the :guilabel:`Menu Editor`."
msgstr ""
"URL *mora* biti imenovan `livechat`, da lahko zbirka podatkov prepozna in "
"poveže stran z ocenami. Ko je stran objavljena, lahko naslov strani pozneje "
"spremenite v :guilabel:`Urejevalnik menija`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create`, and the newly created webpage opens. "
"The :guilabel:`Web Editor` appears in the right panel."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari` in odpre se novo ustvarjena spletna stran. V "
"desnem pultu se prikaže :guilabel:`Spletni urejevalnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:84
msgid ""
"The page lists the names of the :guilabel:`Live Chat Channels` whose ratings "
"pages have been published. On the left side of the channel name is an icon, "
"which users can click on to go to the ratings page for the respective "
"channel."
msgstr ""
"Stran navaja imena :guilabel:`Kanalov za klepet v živo`, katerih strani z "
"ocenami so bile objavljene. Na levi strani imena kanala je ikona, na katero "
"lahko uporabniki kliknejo, da pridejo na stran z ocenami za posamezni kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the webpage for Live Chat ratings emphasizing the channel icon."
msgstr ""
"Pogled spletne strani za ocene klepeta v živo s poudarkom na ikoni kanala."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:92
msgid ""
"The icon displayed on this page is configured on the live chat channel's "
"configuration page. To update this image, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Live Chat` app and click on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the Kanban card for that team. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel details form. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon in the image box to "
"upload an image."
msgstr ""
"Ikona, prikazana na tej strani, je konfigurirana na konfiguracijski strani "
"kanala za klepet v živo. Za posodobitev te slike odprite "
"aplikacijo :menuselection:`Klepet v živo` in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri-pičje)` na Kanban kartici za to ekipo. "
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj kanal`, da odprete obrazec s "
"podrobnostmi kanala. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(svinčnik)` "
"v polju s sliko za nalaganje slike."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:98
msgid ""
"Make any desired changes or additions to this page, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` in the top right of the webpage editor. The website "
"editor side panel closes, and the webpage remains on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Naredite želene spremembe ali dodatke na tej strani, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani` v zgornjem desnem delu urejevalnika spletne "
"strani. Stranski pult urejevalnika spletnega mesta se zapre in spletna stran "
"ostane na zaslonu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:101
msgid ""
"To publish the `livechat` webpage, return to the list of webpages by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Site --> Content --> Pages`. Click the "
"checkbox to the left of `livechat` in the list of pages to select the page "
"and highlight the line. Then, click the checkbox under the column "
"labeled :guilabel:`Is Published`. The field with the checkbox is highlighted "
"in white. Click the checkbox a second time to activate the :guilabel:`Is "
"Published` box. The webpage is now published."
msgstr ""
"Za objavo spletne strani `livechat` se vrnite na seznam spletnih strani "
"tako, da odprete :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Vsebina --> Strani`. "
"Kliknite potrditveno polje levo od `livechat` na seznamu strani, da izberete "
"stran in označite vrstico. Nato kliknite potrditveno polje pod stolpcem z "
"oznako :guilabel:`Je objavljeno`. Polje s potrditvenim poljem je označeno "
"belo. Drugo pot kliknite potrditveno polje, da aktivirate "
"polje :guilabel:`Je objavljeno`. Spletna stran je zdaj objavljena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the list of pages for a website with the 'is published' box "
"emphasized."
msgstr ""
"Pogled seznama strani za spletno mesto z označenim poljem »je objavljeno«."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:110
msgid ""
"Once the page has been added to the site, ratings are set to be published by "
"default. However, individual ratings can be manually selected to be hidden "
"from the public. The rating is still included in internal reports, and can "
"still be viewed by internal teams. However, public website visitors and "
"portal users do not have access."
msgstr ""
"Ko je stran dodana na spletno mesto, so ocene privzeto nastavljene za "
"objavo. Vendar je mogoče posamezne ocene ročno izbrati, da se skrijejo pred "
"javnostjo. Ocena je še vedno vključena v notranja poročila in si jo lahko "
"ogledajo notranje ekipe. Vendar obiskovalci spletnega mesta in uporabniki "
"portala nimajo dostopa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:115
msgid ""
"See :ref:`Hide individual ratings <livechat/overview/hide-ratings>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte :ref:`Skrivanje posameznih ocen <livechat/overview/"
"hide-ratings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:118
msgid "Customer ratings report"
msgstr "Poročilo o ocenah strank"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer Ratings` report (:menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Report --> Customer Ratings`) displays an overview of the ratings received "
"on live chat conversations, as well as any additional comments submitted "
"with the rating."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Ocene strank` (:menuselection:`Klepet v živo --> "
"Poročilo --> Ocene strank`) prikazuje pregled ocen, prejetih v pogovorih s "
"klepetom v živo, kot tudi vse dodatne komentarje, predložene z oceno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the customer ratings report in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Pogled poročila o ocenah strank v Odoo Klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:127
msgid ""
"The report defaults to a Kanban view, with each rating represented by a "
"different card. To switch to a different view, click on one of the icons in "
"the upper-right corner of the screen. The report is available in *list* "
"view, *pivot* view, and *graph* view."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo je privzeto prikazano v pogledu Kanban, pri čemer vsako oceno "
"predstavlja druga kartica. Za preklop na drug pogled kliknite eno od ikon v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu zaslona. Poročilo je na voljo v pogledu *seznam*, "
"pogledu *pivot* in pogledu *graf*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:131
msgid ""
"Click on an individual rating to see additional details about the "
"conversation, and the rating."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na posamezno oceno, da si ogledate dodatne podrobnosti o pogovoru "
"in oceni."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:136
msgid "Hide individual ratings"
msgstr "Skrivanje posameznih ocen"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:138
msgid ""
"Ratings are set to be published by default. However, individual ratings can "
"be manually selected to be hidden from the public. The rating is still "
"included in internal reports, and can still be viewed by internal teams. "
"However, public website visitors and portal users do not have access."
msgstr ""
"Ocene so privzeto nastavljene za objavo. Vendar je mogoče posamezne ocene "
"ročno izbrati, da se skrijejo pred javnostjo. Ocena je še vedno vključena v "
"notranja poročila in si jo lahko ogledajo notranje ekipe. Vendar obiskovalci "
"spletnega mesta in uporabniki portala nimajo dostopa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:142
msgid ""
"To hide a rating, go to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report --> "
"Customer Ratings`. Click on the Kanban card for the rating to be hidden. On "
"the individual rating's detail page, check the box "
"labeled :guilabel:`Visible Internally Only`."
msgstr ""
"Za skritje ocene pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Klepet v živo --> "
"Poročilo --> Ocene strank`. Kliknite na kartico Kanban za oceno, ki jo "
"želite skriti. Na strani s podrobnostmi posamezne ocene označite polje z "
"oznako :guilabel:`Vidno samo interno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of an individual rating's detail page with the visible internally "
"setting checked."
msgstr ""
"Pogled strani s podrobnostmi posamezne ocene z označeno nastavitvijo "
"vidnosti samo interno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:150
msgid ":doc:`/applications/websites/livechat`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/websites/livechat`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:152
msgid ":doc:`/applications/websites/website`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/websites/website`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:3
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** includes several reports that allow for the monitoring of "
"operator performance and the identification of trends in customer "
"conversations."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Klepet v živo** vključuje več poročil, ki omogočajo spremljanje "
"učinkovitosti operaterjev in prepoznavanje trendov v pogovorih s strankami."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:8
msgid "The following reports are included in the **Live Chat** app:"
msgstr "V aplikaciji **Klepet v živo** so vključena naslednja poročila:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Sessions History <livechat/sessions-history>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Zgodovina sej <livechat/sessions-history>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:11
msgid ":ref:`Session Statistics <livechat/session-statistics>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Statistika sej <livechat/session-statistics>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:12
msgid ":ref:`Operator Analysis <livechat/operator-analysis>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Analiza operaterjev <livechat/operator-analysis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:15
msgid ""
"The *Live Chat Ratings Report* can also be accessed through "
"the :guilabel:`Report` menu. For more information on this report, and on the "
"**Live Chat** rating process, see :doc:`Live Chat Ratings <../livechat/"
"ratings>`."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo *Ocene klepetov v živo* je dostopno tudi prek "
"menija :guilabel:`Poročilo`. Za več informacij o tem poročilu in procesu "
"ocenjevanja **klepetov v živo** glejte :doc:`Ocene klepetov v živo <../"
"livechat/ratings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:19
msgid ""
"To access a drop-down menu of all the available reports, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do spustnega menija vseh razpoložljivih poročil pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Klepet v živo --> Poročilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:25
msgid "Sessions History"
msgstr "Zgodovina sej"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:27
msgid ""
"The *Sessions History* report displays an overview of live chat sessions, "
"including session dates, participant name and country, session duration, the "
"number of messages, and the rating. It also provides access to the complete "
"transcripts of live chat sessions."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo *Zgodovina sej* prikazuje pregled sej klepeta v živo, vključno z "
"datumi sej, imenom in državo udeleženca, trajanjem seje, številom sporočil "
"in oceno. Omogoča tudi dostop do popolnih prepisov sej klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:31
msgid ""
"To access this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report "
"--> Sessions History`. Each live chat session is represented by a Kanban "
"card."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do tega poročila pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Klepet v "
"živo --> Poročilo --> Zgodovina sej`. Vsaka seja klepeta v živo je "
"predstavljena s kartico Kanban."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "Example of the Sessions History report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Primer poročila Zgodovina sej iz aplikacije Klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:37
msgid ""
"To view the transcript from a specific session, click the Kanban card. This "
"opens the *Discuss* thread for the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled prepisa določene seje kliknite kartico Kanban. S tem se odpre nit "
"*Discuss* za pogovor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the *Discuss* thread, the conversation view displays the entire "
"transcript of the conversation. If the visitor left a rating, it is included "
"at the end of the transcript."
msgstr ""
"V niti *Discuss* pogovorni pogled prikazuje celoten prepis pogovora. Če je "
"obiskovalec pustil oceno, je vključena na koncu prepisa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "View of the chat transcript in the Discuss application."
msgstr "Pogled prepisa klepeta v aplikaciji Discuss."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:47
msgid "Export sessions history"
msgstr "Izvoz zgodovine sej"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:49
msgid ""
"The information in this report can be exported, or inserted into a "
"spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Informacije iz tega poročila je mogoče izvoziti ali vstaviti v preglednico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:51
msgid ""
"On the *Sessions History* report, click the :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(List)` icon to switch to list view. Next, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`History` page title to reveal a drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"V poročilu *Zgodovina sej* kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(Seznam)`, da preklopite na seznamski pogled. Nato kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)` na desni strani naslova "
"strani :guilabel:`Zgodovina`, da se prikaže spustni meni."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:55
msgid ""
"From the drop-down menu, click :guilabel:`Export All` to export all sessions "
"to a spreadsheet, or :guilabel:`Insert list in spreadsheet` to insert the "
"information in a new, or existing, spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem meniju kliknite :guilabel:`Izvozi vse`, da izvozite vse seje v "
"preglednico, ali :guilabel:`Vstavi seznam v preglednico`, da vstavite "
"informacije v novo ali obstoječo preglednico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:58
msgid ""
"To only export select sessions, first select the desired sessions to be "
"exported from the list, by clicking the checkbox to the left of each "
"individual session. With the sessions selected, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon at the top of the page, and "
"click :guilabel:`Export` or :guilabel:`Insert list in spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti samo izbrane seje, najprej na seznamu izberite želene "
"seje za izvoz tako, da kliknete potrditveno polje na levi strani vsake "
"posamezne seje. Ko so seje izbrane, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` na vrhu strani in kliknite :guilabel:`Izvozi` "
"ali :guilabel:`Vstavi seznam v preglednico`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:66
msgid "Session Statistics"
msgstr "Statistika seje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:68
msgid ""
"The *Session Statistics* report provides a statistical overview of live chat "
"sessions. The default view for this report displays sessions grouped by the "
"date of creation."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo *Statistika sej* zagotavlja statistični pregled sej klepeta v živo. "
"Privzeti pogled za to poročilo prikazuje seje, združene po datumu nastanka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:71
msgid ""
"To access this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Reports "
"--> Session Statistics`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do tega poročila pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Klepet v "
"živo --> Poročila --> Statistika sej`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:77
msgid ""
"Example of the Sessions Statistics report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Primer poročila Statistika sej iz aplikacije Klepet v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:77
msgid ""
"The stacked bar graph view of the *Session Statistics* report, with results "
"grouped by Creation Date (hour), then by rating."
msgstr ""
"Pogled zloženega stolpčnega grafa poročila *Statistika sej* z rezultati, "
"združenimi po datumu nastanka (ura), nato po oceni."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:112
msgid ""
"To view a different measure, click the :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down menu "
"at the top-left of the report. The measures available for this report "
"include:"
msgstr ""
"Za ogled druge mere kliknite spustni meni :guilabel:`Mere` v zgornjem levem "
"kotu poročila. Mere, ki so na voljo za to poročilo, vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`# of speakers`: number of participants in the conversation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Število govorcev`: število udeležencev v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Days of activity`: number of days since the operator's first "
"session."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dnevi aktivnosti`: število dni od prve seje operaterja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration of Session (min)`: the duration of a conversation, in "
"minutes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Trajanje seje (min)`: trajanje pogovora v minutah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is visitor anonymous`: denotes whether the conversation "
"participant is anonymous."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je obiskovalec anonimen`: označuje, ali je udeleženec pogovora "
"anonimen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Messages per session`: the total number of messages sent in a "
"conversation. This measure is included in the default view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sporočil na sejo`: skupno število sporočil, poslanih v pogovoru. "
"Ta mera je vključena v privzeti pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: the rating received by an operator at the end of a "
"session, if one was provided."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ocena`: ocena, ki jo je operater prejel ob koncu seje, če je bila "
"podana."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Session not rated`: denotes if a session did **not** receive a "
"rating at the end of the conversation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Seja ni ocenjena`: označuje, ali seja ob koncu pogovora **ni** "
"prejela ocene."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time to answer (sec)`: the average time, in seconds, before an "
"operator responds to a chat request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čas do odgovora (sek)`: povprečni čas v sekundah, preden operater "
"odgovori na zahtevo za klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visitor is Happy`: denotes whether a positive rating was "
"provided. If the visitor gave either a negative or neutral rating, they are "
"considered *unhappy*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obiskovalec je zadovoljen`: označuje, ali je bila podana "
"pozitivna ocena. Če je obiskovalec podal negativno ali nevtralno oceno, "
"velja za *nezadovoljnega*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:97
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Count`: the total number of sessions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Število`: skupno število sej."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:102
msgid "Operator Analysis"
msgstr "Analiza operaterja"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:104
msgid ""
"The *Operator Analysis* report is used to monitor the performance of "
"individual live chat operators."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo *Analiza operaterjev* se uporablja za spremljanje uspešnosti "
"posameznih operaterjev v neposrednem klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:106
msgid ""
"To access the report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Reports "
"--> Operator Analysis`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do poročila pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Neposredni "
"klepet --> Poročila --> Analiza operaterjev`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:108
msgid ""
"The default view for this report is a bar chart, which only displays "
"conversations from the current month, as indicated by the :guilabel:`This "
"Month` default search filter. Conversations are grouped by operator."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti pogled za to poročilo je stolpčni grafikon, ki prikazuje samo "
"pogovore iz tekočega meseca, kot je navedeno v privzetem iskalnem "
"filtru :guilabel:`Ta mesec`. Pogovori so razvrščeni po operaterjih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# of Sessions`: the number of sessions an operator participated "
"in. This measure is included by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Št. sej`: število sej, v katerih je operater sodeloval. Ta mera "
"je privzeto vključena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average duration`: the average duration of a conversation, in "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Povprečno trajanje`: povprečno trajanje pogovora v sekundah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average rating`: the average rating received by the operator."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Povprečna ocena`: povprečna ocena, ki jo je operater prejel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time to answer`: the average amount of time before the operator "
"responds to a chat request, in seconds."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čas do odgovora`: povprečni čas, preden operater odgovori na "
"zahtevo za klepet, v sekundah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "Example of the Operator Analysis report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Primer poročila Analiza operaterjev iz aplikacije Neposredni klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:3
msgid "Commands and canned responses"
msgstr "Ukazi in vnaprej pripravljeni odgovori"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the Odoo **Live Chat** application, *commands* allow the user to perform "
"specific actions both inside the chat window, and through other Odoo "
"applications. The **Live Chat** app also includes *canned responses*. These "
"are customized, preconfigured substitutions that allow users to replace "
"shortcut entries in place of longer, well-thought out responses to some of "
"the most common questions and comments."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji Odoo **Neposredni klepet** *ukazi* uporabniku omogočajo "
"izvajanje določenih dejanj tako v oknu klepeta kot prek drugih aplikacij "
"Odoo. Aplikacija **Neposredni klepet** vključuje tudi *vnaprej pripravljene "
"odgovore*. To so prilagojene, vnaprej konfigurirane zamenjave, ki "
"uporabnikom omogočajo, da bližnjice nadomestijo z daljšimi, dobro "
"premišljenimi odgovori na nekatera najpogostejša vprašanja in komentarje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:11
msgid ""
"Both commands and canned responses save time, and allow users to maintain a "
"level of consistency throughout their conversations."
msgstr ""
"Tako ukazi kot vnaprej pripravljeni odgovori prihranijo čas in uporabnikom "
"omogočajo ohranjanje doslednosti v svojih pogovorih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:15
msgid "Execute a command"
msgstr "Izvedi ukaz"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:17
msgid ""
"Live chat *commands* are keywords that trigger preconfigured actions. When a "
"live chat *operator* is participating in a conversation with a customer or "
"website visitor, they can execute a command by typing `/`, followed by the "
"command."
msgstr ""
"Ukazi za klepet v živo (*commands*) so ključne besede, ki sprožijo vnaprej "
"nastavljena dejanja. Ko operater klepeta v živo (*operator*) sodeluje v "
"pogovoru s stranko ali obiskovalcem spletnega mesta, lahko izvrši ukaz tako, "
"da vnese `/`, ki mu sledi ukaz."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:21
msgid ""
"Commands, and the resulting actions, are only visible in the conversation "
"window for the live chat operator. A customer does not see any commands that "
"an operator uses in a conversation from their view of the chat."
msgstr ""
"Ukazi in dejanja, ki iz njih izhajajo, so vidni samo v oknu pogovora za "
"operaterja klepeta v živo. Stranka ne vidi nobenih ukazov, ki jih operater "
"uporablja v pogovoru iz svojega pogleda na klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:26
msgid ""
"During a conversation with a customer, a live chat operator executes the "
"command to :ref:`create a ticket <live-chat/ticket>`. After entering the "
"command, `/ticket`, the system automatically creates a ticket with the "
"information from the conversation. It also includes a link to the new "
"ticket, so the operator can go there directly to add any additional "
"information, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Med pogovorom s stranko operater klepeta v živo izvrši ukaz "
"za :ref:`ustvarjanje zahtevka <live-chat/ticket>`. Po vnosu ukaza `/ticket` "
"sistem samodejno ustvari zahtevek z informacijami iz pogovora. Vključuje "
"tudi povezavo do novega zahtevka, tako da lahko operater neposredno odpre ta "
"zahtevek in po potrebi doda dodatne informacije."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:34
msgid "More information about each available command can be found below."
msgstr "Več informacij o vsakem razpoložljivem ukazu je na voljo spodaj."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:37
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:39
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/help` in the chat window, an informative message that "
"includes the potential entry types an operator can make is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če operater vnese `/help` v okno za klepet, se prikaže informativno "
"sporočilo, ki vključuje morebitne vrste vnosov, ki jih lahko operater opravi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:42
msgid ""
"Type `@username` to mention a user in the conversation. A notification will "
"be sent to that user's inbox or email, depending on their notification "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite `@uporabniškoime`, da omenite uporabnika v pogovoru. Obvestilo bo "
"poslano v prečalni predal tega uporabnika ali po e-pošti, odvisno od "
"njihovih nastavitev obvestil."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:44
msgid "Type `/command` to execute a command."
msgstr "Vnesite `/ukaz`, da izvršite ukaz."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:45
msgid ""
"Type `:shortcut` to insert a :ref:`canned response <live-chat/canned-"
"responses>`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite `:bližnjica`, da vstavite :ref:`vnaprej pripravljeni odgovor <live-"
"chat/canned-responses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:48
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:49
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:52
msgid "Ticket & search tickets"
msgstr "Zahtevek in iskanje zahtevkov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:54
msgid ""
"The `/ticket` and `/search_tickets` commands allow operators to create "
"helpdesk tickets directly from a conversation, and search through existing "
"tickets by keyword or ticket number."
msgstr ""
"Ukaza `/ticket` in `/search_tickets` omogočata operaterjem, da ustvarijo "
"zahtevke službe za pomoč neposredno iz pogovora in iščejo po obstoječih "
"zahtevkih po ključni besedi ali številki zahtevka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:58
msgid ""
"The `/ticket` and `/search_tickets` commands can **only** be used if the "
"**Helpdesk** app has been installed, and *Live Chat* has been activated on a "
"*Helpdesk* team. To activate *Live Chat*, go to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app "
"--> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams`, and select a team. Scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Channels` section, and check the box labeled, :guilabel:`Live "
"Chat`."
msgstr ""
"Ukaza `/ticket` in `/search_tickets` se lahko uporabljata **samo**, če je "
"aplikacija **Služba za pomoč** nameščena in je *Klepet v živo* aktiviran v "
"ekipi *Službe za pomoč*. Za aktivacijo *Klepeta v živo* pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Služba za pomoč --> Nastavitve --> Ekipe "
"službe za pomoč` in izberite ekipo. Pomaknite se do "
"odseka :guilabel:`Kanali` in označite polje z oznakoijo :guilabel:`Klepet v "
"živo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:66
msgid "Create a ticket from a live chat"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje zahtevka iz klepeta v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:68
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/ticket` in the chat window, the conversation is used "
"to create a *Helpdesk* ticket."
msgstr ""
"Če operater vnese `/ticket` v okno za klepet, se pogovor uporabi za "
"ustvarjanje zahtevka *Službe za pomoč*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:71
msgid ""
"After entering the `/ticket` command, type a title for the ticket into the "
"chat window, then press `Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu ukaza `/ticket` vnesite naslov zahtevka v okno za klepet in "
"pritisnite `Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid "View of the results from a helpdesk search in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Pogled rezultatov iskanja službe za pomoč v pogovoru klepeta v živo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:77
msgid ""
"The newly created ticket will be added to the *Helpdesk* team that has live "
"chat enabled. If more than one team has live chat enabled, the ticket will "
"automatically be assigned based on the team's priority."
msgstr ""
"Novo ustvarjen zahtevek bo dodan ekipi *Službe za pomoč*, ki ima omogočen "
"klepet v živo. Če ima več ekip omogočen klepet v živo, bo zahtevek samodejno "
"dodeljen glede na prednost ekipe."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:81
msgid ""
"The transcript from the conversation will be added to the new ticket, under "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab."
msgstr ""
"Prepis pogovora bo dodan novemu zahtevku pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Opis`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:84
msgid ""
"To access the new ticket, click on the link in the chat window, or go to "
"the :menuselection:`Helpdesk app` and click the :guilabel:`Tickets` button "
"on the Kanban card for the appropriate team."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do novega zahtevka kliknite povezavo v oknu za klepet ali pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Služba za pomoč` in kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Zahtevki` na Kanban kartici ustrezne ekipe."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:89
msgid "Search for a ticket from a live chat"
msgstr "Iskanje zahtevka iz neposrednega klepeta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:91
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/search_tickets` in the chat window, they can search "
"through *Helpdesk* tickets, either by ticket number or keyword."
msgstr ""
"Če operater vpiše `/search_tickets` v okno za klepet, lahko išče po "
"zahtevkih *Službe za pomoč*, bodisi po številki zahtevka bodisi po ključni "
"besedi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:94
msgid ""
"After entering the `/search_tickets` command, type a keyword or ticket "
"number, then press :kbd:`Enter`. If one or more related tickets are found, a "
"list of links is generated in the conversation window."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu ukaza `/search_tickets` vnesite ključno besedo ali številko "
"zahtevka, nato pritisnite :kbd:`Enter`. Če je najden en ali več povezanih "
"zahtevkov, se v oknu pogovora ustvari seznam povezav."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:102
msgid ""
"Results from the search command will only be seen by the operator, not the "
"customer."
msgstr "Rezultate iskalnega ukaza bo videl samo operater, ne stranka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:105
msgid "History"
msgstr "Zgodovina"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:107
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/history` in the chat window, it generates a list of "
"the most recent pages the visitor has viewed on the website (up to 15)."
msgstr ""
"Če operater vpiše `/history` v okno za klepet, se ustvari seznam najnovejših "
"strani, ki si jih je obiskovalec ogledal na spletnem mestu (do 15)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the results from a /history command in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Pogled rezultatov ukaza /history v pogovoru neposrednega klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:114
msgid "Lead"
msgstr "Indic"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:116
msgid ""
"By typing `/lead` in the chat window, an operator can create a *lead* in the "
"**CRM** application."
msgstr ""
"Z vpisom `/lead` v okno za klepet lahko operater ustvari *priložnost* v "
"aplikaciji **CRM**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid "View of the results from a /lead command in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Pogled rezultatov ukaza /lead v pogovoru neposrednega klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:122
msgid ""
"The `/lead` command can only be used if the **CRM** app has been installed."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz `/lead` je mogoče uporabiti le, če je aplikacija **CRM** nameščena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:124
msgid ""
"After typing `/lead`, create a title for this new lead, then press `Enter`. "
"A link with the lead title appears. Click the link, or navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`CRM` app to view the :guilabel:`Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu `/lead` ustvarite naslov za to novo priložnost, nato pritisnite "
"`Enter`. Prikaže se povezava z naslovom priložnosti. Kliknite povezavo ali "
"pojdite v aplikacijo :menuselection:`CRM`, da si ogledate :guilabel:`Potek`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:129
msgid ""
"The link to the new lead can only be seen and accessed by the operator, not "
"the customer."
msgstr ""
"Povezavo do nove priložnosti lahko vidi in odpre samo operater, ne stranka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:131
msgid ""
"The transcript of that specific live chat conversation (where the lead was "
"created) is added to the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab of the lead form."
msgstr ""
"Zapis tega določenega pogovora v neposrednem klepetu (kjer je bila "
"priložnost ustvarjena) je dodan na zavihek :guilabel:`Notranja opomba` "
"obrazca priložnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:134
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Extra Information` tab of the lead form, "
"the :guilabel:`Source` will be listed as :guilabel:`Livechat`."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`Dodatne informacije` obrazca priložnosti "
"bo :guilabel:`Vir` naveden kot :guilabel:`Livechat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:138
msgid "Leave"
msgstr "Zapusti"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:140
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/leave` in the chat window, they can automatically "
"exit the conversation. This command does not cause the customer to be "
"removed from the conversation, nor does it automatically end the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Če operater vpiše `/leave` v okno za klepet, lahko samodejno zapusti "
"pogovor. Ta ukaz ne povzroči odstranitve stranke iz pogovora in tudi ne "
"konča pogovora samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:146
msgid ":doc:`../../services/helpdesk`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../services/helpdesk`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:151
msgid "Canned responses"
msgstr "Vnaprej pripravljeni odgovori"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:153
msgid ""
"*Canned responses* are customizable inputs where a *shortcut* stands in for "
"a longer response. An operator will enter the shortcut, and it is "
"automatically replaced by the expanded *substitution* response in the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"*Predpripravljeni odgovori* so prilagodljivi vnosi, kjer *bližnjica* "
"nadomesti daljši odgovor. Operater vnese bližnjico in ta se v pogovoru "
"samodejno nadomesti z razširjenim *nadomestitvenim* odgovorom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:158
msgid "Create canned responses"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje predpripravljenih odgovorov"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:160
msgid ""
"To create a new canned response, go to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Canned Responses --> New`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega predpripravljenega odgovora pojdite "
"v :menuselection:`Aplikacija Neposredni klepet --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Predpripravljeni odgovori --> Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:163
msgid ""
"Type a shortcut command in the :guilabel:`Shortcut` field. Next, click "
"the :guilabel:`Substitution` field, and type the message that should replace "
"the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Bližnjica` vnesite ukaz za bližnjico. Nato kliknite v "
"polje :guilabel:`Nadomestitev` in vnesite sporočilo, ki naj nadomesti "
"bližnjico."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:167
msgid ""
"Try to connect the shortcut to the topic of the substitution. The easier it "
"is for the operators to remember, the easier it is to use the canned "
"responses in conversations."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite povezati bližnjico s temo nadomestitve. Lažje kot si operaterji "
"zapomnijo bližnjico, lažje je uporabiti pripravljene odgovore v pogovorih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:171
msgid "Authorized groups"
msgstr "Pooblaščene skupine"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:173
msgid ""
"When a new canned response is created, it can **only** be utilized by the "
"operator that created it. To allow the response to be used by other "
"operators, select one or more :ref:`groups <access-rights/groups>` from "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized Groups` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ustvarjen nov pripravljeni odgovor, ga lahko uporabi **samo** "
"operater, ki ga je ustvaril. Da bi odgovor lahko uporabljali tudi drugi "
"operaterji, izberite eno ali več :ref:`skupin <access-rights/groups>` s "
"spustnega seznama :guilabel:`Pooblaščene skupine`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:178
msgid "Use canned responses in a live chat conversation"
msgstr "Uporaba pripravljenih odgovorov v pogovoru v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:180
msgid ""
"To use a canned response in a conversation, click the :icon:`fa-plus-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon in the message window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Insert a Canned Response`. This opens a list of available "
"canned responses. Either select a response from the list, or type the "
"appropriate shortcut, then click the :icon:`fa-paper-"
"plane` :guilabel:`(send)` icon or hit :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti pripravljeni odgovor v pogovoru, kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` v oknu s sporočilom. Nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Vstavi pripravljeni odgovor`. Odpre se seznam "
"razpoložljivih pripravljenih odgovorov. Izberite odgovor s seznama ali "
"vnesite ustrezno bližnjico, nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-paper-"
"plane` :guilabel:`(pošlji)` ali pritisnite :kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:186
msgid ""
"Typing `::` into a chat window on its own generates a list of available "
"canned responses. Responses can be manually selected from the list, in "
"addition to the use of shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Vnos `::` v okno klepeta sam po sebi ustvari seznam razpoložljivih "
"pripravljenih odgovorov. Odgovore lahko izberete ročno s seznama, poleg "
"uporabe bližnjic."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:0
msgid "View of a chat window and the list of available canned responses."
msgstr "Pogled okna klepeta in seznam razpoložljivih pripravljenih odgovorov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:7
msgid "Website"
msgstr "Spletna stran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Odoo Website** offers a user-friendly platform for creating and managing "
"your website. It includes various tools and features to help you design, "
"publish, and maintain web pages without needing advanced technical skills. "
"You can easily customize layouts, add multimedia content, and integrate with "
"other Odoo apps to expand your website's functionality."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Website** ponuja uporabniku prijazen vmesnik za ustvarjanje in "
"upravljanje vaše spletne strani. Vključuje različna orodja in funkcije, ki "
"vam pomagajo pri oblikovanju, objavljanju in vzdrževanju spletnih strani "
"brez potrebe po naprednih tehničnih znanjih. Lahko zlahka prilagodite "
"postavitve, dodate večpredstavnostno vsebino in integrirate z drugimi "
"aplikacijami Odoo za razširitev funkcionalnosti vaše spletne strani."

