"izberite :guilabel:`Izraz filtra po meri` in uporabite naslednjo "
"konfiguracijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:339
msgid ":guilabel:`Field`: select `Hostname`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Polje`: izberite `Hostname`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:340
msgid ":guilabel:`Operator`: select `equals`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Operator`: izberite `equals`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:341
msgid ":guilabel:`Value`: enter your domain name, e.g., `yourdomain.com`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrednost`: vnesite ime svoje domene, npr. `yourdomain.com`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:343
msgid "Under the :guilabel:`Then...` section, use the following configuration:"
msgstr "V razdelku :guilabel:`Potem...` uporabite naslednjo konfiguracijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:345
msgid ":guilabel:`Type`: select `Dynamic`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tip`: izberite `Dynamic`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:346
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expression`: enter the following expression `concat(\"https://"
"www.yourdomain.com\", http.request.uri.path)`, replacing `yourdomain.com` "
"with your domain name."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izraz`: vnesite naslednji izraz `concat(\"https://"
"www.yourdomain.com\", http.request.uri.path)` in zamenjajte `yourdomain.com` "
"z imenom svoje domene."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:348
msgid ":guilabel:`Status code`: select `301`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Koda stanja`: izberite `301`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:349
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Preserve query string`: enable the option by ticking the box."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ohrani niz poizvedbe`: omogočite možnost s kljukico v polju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:351
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Deploy`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Deploy`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid ""
"Defining a Cloudflare redirect rule to create a permanent redirect (301)"
msgstr ""
"Definiranje pravila preusmeritve Cloudflare za ustvarjanje trajne "
"preusmeritve (301)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:356
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`SSL/TLS --> Overview --> Configure` and ensure the "
"encryption mode is set to :guilabel:`Full`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`SSL/TLS --> Overview --> Configure` in preverite, "
"da je način šifriranja nastavljen na :guilabel:`Full`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid "Setting the encryption mode to full on Cloudflare"
msgstr "Nastavitev načina šifriranja na popolno v Cloudflare"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:365
msgid "Map a domain name to an Odoo database"
msgstr "Preslikava domenskega imena na podatkovno bazo Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:368
msgid ""
"Ensure you have :ref:`added a CNAME record <domain-name/existing/cname>` to "
"your domain name's DNS **before** mapping your domain name to your Odoo "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da ste :ref:`dodali zapis CNAME <domain-name/existing/"
"cname>` v DNS svojega domenskega imena **preden** preslikate domensko ime v "
"svojo bazo Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:371
msgid ""
"Failing to do so may prevent the :ref:`SSL certificate <domain-name/existing/"
"db-map/ssl>` from being validated and could result in a *certificate name "
"mismatch* error. Web browsers often display this as a warning, such as "
"*\"Your connection is not private\"*."
msgstr ""
"Če tega ne storite, se morda :ref:`potrdilo SSL <domain-name/existing/db-map/"
"ssl>` ne bo moglo potrditi in bi lahko prišlo do napake *neujemanje imena "
"potrdila*. Spletni brskalniki to pogosto prikažejo kot opozorilo, na primer "
"*\"Vaša povezava ni zasebna\"*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:375
msgid ""
"If you encounter this error after mapping the domain name to your database, "
"wait up to five days, as the validation may still be in progress. If not, "
"you can `submit a support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/help-form>`_, "
"including screenshots of your CNAME records."
msgstr ""
"Če naletite na to napako po presliku domenskega imena v svojo bazo, "
"počakajte do pet dni, saj je preverjanje morda še v teku. Če ne, lahko "
"`oddate zahtevek za podporo <https://www.odoo.com/help-form>`_ in priložite "
"posnetke zaslona svojih zapisov CNAME."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:385
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Use my own domain`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Use my own domain`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:386
msgid ""
"Enter the domain name (e.g., `www.yourdomain.com`), "
"click :guilabel:`Verify`, then :guilabel:`I confirm, it's done`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite domensko ime (npr. `www.yourdomain.com`), "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Verify`, nato :guilabel:`I confirm, it's done`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid "Mapping a domain name to an Odoo Online database"
msgstr "Preslikava domenskega imena na podatkovno bazo Odoo Online"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:394
msgid ""
"On Odoo.sh, go to :menuselection:`Branches --> select your branch --> "
"Settings --> Custom domains`, type the domain name to add, then "
"click :guilabel:`Add domain`."
msgstr ""
"Na Odoo.sh pojdite na :menuselection:`Veje --> izberite svojo vejo --> "
"Nastavitve --> Domene po meri`, vnesite domensko ime, ki ga želite dodati, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj domeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:0
msgid "Mapping a domain name to an Odoo.sh branch"
msgstr "Preslikava domenskega imena na vejo Odoo.sh"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:401
msgid ":ref:`Odoo.sh branches: settings tab <odoo-sh/branches/tabs/settings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Zavihek nastavitev vej Odoo.sh <odoo-sh/branches/tabs/settings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:406
msgid "SSL encryption (HTTPS protocol)"
msgstr "Šifriranje SSL (protokol HTTPS)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:408
msgid ""
"**SSL encryption** allows visitors to navigate a website over a secure "
"connection, indicated by the *https://* protocol at the beginning of a web "
"address rather than the non-secure *http://* protocol."
msgstr ""
"**Šifriranje SSL** obiskovalcem omogoča brskanje po spletni strani prek "
"varne povezave, ki jo označuje protokol *https://* na začetku spletnega "
"naslova namesto nezaščitenega protokola *http://*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:412
msgid ""
"Odoo generates a separate SSL certificate for each domain :ref:`mapped to a "
"database <domain-name/existing/db-map>` using `Let's Encrypt's certificate "
"authority and ACME protocol <https://letsencrypt.org/how-it-works/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ustvari ločeno potrdilo SSL za vsako domeno, :ref:`preslikano v bazo "
"<domain-name/existing/db-map>`, z uporabo `avtoritete za potrdila Let's "
"Encrypt in protokola ACME <https://letsencrypt.org/how-it-works/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:417
msgid "Certificate generation may take up to 24 hours."
msgstr "Generiranje certifikata lahko traja do 24 ur."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:418
msgid ""
"Several attempts to validate your certificate are made over the next five "
"days after you map your domain name to your database."
msgstr ""
"V naslednjih petih dneh po presliku domenskega imena v bazo je opravljenih "
"več poskusov potrditve vašega potrdila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:420
msgid "If you use another service, you can keep using it or change to Odoo's."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate drugo storitev, jo lahko še naprej uporabljate ali preklopite "
"na Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:423
msgid ""
"No SSL certificate is generated for naked domains :dfn:`(domain names "
"without any subdomains or prefixes)`."
msgstr ""
"Za gole domene :dfn:`(domenska imena brez poddomen ali predpon)` se ne "
"generira certifikat SSL."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:429
msgid "Web base URL of a database"
msgstr "Spletni osnovni URL podatkovne baze"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:432
msgid ""
"If the Website app is installed on your database, skip this section and "
"continue from the :ref:`Map a domain name to an Odoo website <domain-name/"
"existing/website-map>` section."
msgstr ""
"Če je aplikacija Spletna stran nameščena v vaši bazi, preskočite ta razdelek "
"in nadaljujte od razdelka :ref:`Preslikava domenskega imena na spletno stran "
"Odoo <domain-name/existing/website-map>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:435
msgid ""
"The *web base URL* or root URL of a database affects your main website "
"address and all the links sent to your customers (e.g., quotations, portal "
"links, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"*Spletni osnovni URL* ali korenski URL podatkovne baze vpliva na vaš glavni "
"naslov spletnega mesta in vse povezave, poslane vašim strankam (npr. "
"ponudbe, povezave do portala itd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:438
msgid ""
"To make your custom domain name the *web base URL* of your database, access "
"your database using your custom domain name and log in as an "
"administrator :dfn:`(a user part of the Settings access right group under "
"Administration)`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite svoje domensko ime po meri nastaviti kot *spletni osnovni URL* "
"svoje podatkovne baze, dostopite do svoje podatkovne baze z uporabo svojega "
"domenskega imena po meri in se prijavite kot skrbnik :dfn:`(uporabnik, ki je "
"del skupine dostopnih pravic Nastavitve pod Administracija)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:443
msgid ""
"If you access your database using the original Odoo address (e.g., "
"`mycompany.odoo.com`), the database's *web base URL* will be updated "
"accordingly. To prevent the automatic update of the *web base URL* when an "
"administrator logs in to the database, activate the :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>`, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System "
"Parameters --> New`, and enter `web.base.url.freeze` as the :guilabel:`Key` "
"and `True` as the :guilabel:`Value`."
msgstr ""
"Če dostopate do svoje baze z uporabo izvirnega naslova Odoo (npr. "
"`mycompany.odoo.com`), se bo *osnovni spletni URL* baze posodobil ustrezno. "
"Če želite preprečiti samodejno posodobitev *osnovnega spletnega URL-ja*, ko "
"se skrbnik prijavi v bazo, aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-"
"mode>`, pojdite na :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System "
"Parameters --> New` in vnesite `web.base.url.freeze` kot :guilabel:`Key` ter "
"`True` kot :guilabel:`Value`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:450
msgid ""
"You can also set the *web base URL* manually. To do so, activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go to :menuselection:`Settings --"
"> Technical --> System Parameters`, and search for the `web.base.url` key "
"(create it if necessary) and enter the full address of your website as the "
"value (e.g., `https://www.yourdomain.com`). The URL must include the "
"protocol `https://` (or `http://`) and *not* end with a slash (`/`)."
msgstr ""
"Lahko tudi ročno nastavite *osnovni spletni URL*. Za to "
"aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters` in poiščite "
"ključ `web.base.url` (če je potrebno, ga ustvarite) ter vnesite celoten "
"naslov svoje spletne strani kot vrednost (npr. `https://"
"www.yourdomain.com`). URL mora vključevati protokol `https://` (ali `http://"
"`) in se *ne sme* končati s poševnico (`/`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:459
msgid "Map a domain name to an Odoo website"
msgstr "Preslikava domenskega imena na spletno mesto Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:462
msgid ""
"Mapping your domain name to your website is different than mapping it to "
"your database:"
msgstr ""
"Preslikava vašega domenskega imena na vaše spletno mesto se razlikuje od "
"preslikave na vašo podatkovno bazo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:464
msgid ""
"It defines your domain name as the main one for your website, helping search "
"engines index it correctly."
msgstr ""
"Določa vašo domensko ime kot glavno za vašo spletno stran in pomaga "
"iskalnikom, da jo pravilno indeksirajo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:466
msgid ""
"It defines your domain name as the base URL for your database, including "
"portal links sent to your customers via email."
msgstr ""
"Določa vašo domensko ime kot osnovni URL za vašo bazo podatkov, vključno s "
"povezavami do portala, poslanimi vašim strankam po e-pošti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:468
msgid ""
"If you have multiple websites, it maps your domain name to the appropriate "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Če imate več spletnih mest, preslika vaše domensko ime na ustrezno spletno "
"mesto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:470
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. If you have "
"multiple websites, select the one you want to configure. In "
"the :guilabel:`Domain` field, enter the URL of your website (e.g., `https://"
"www.yourdomain.com`) and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. "
"Če imate več spletnih strani, izberite tisto, ki jo želite konfigurirati. V "
"polje :guilabel:`Domena` vnesite URL vaše spletne strani (npr. `https://"
"www.vasadomena.com`) in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:475
msgid ""
"Mapping your domain name to your Odoo website prevents Google Search from "
"indexing your original database address (e.g., `mycompany.odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Preslikava vašega domenskega imena na vašo spletno mesto Odoo prepreči, da "
"bi Google Search indeksiral vaš prvotni naslov zbirke podatkov (npr. "
"`mycompany.odoo.com`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:478
msgid ""
"If both addresses are already indexed, it may take some time for the "
"indexation of the second address to be removed from Google Search. You can "
"use the `Google Search Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/"
"welcome>`_ to fix the issue."
msgstr ""
"Če sta oba naslova že indeksirana, lahko traja nekaj časa, preden se "
"indeksacija drugega naslova odstrani iz Google Iskanja. Za odpravo težave "
"lahko uporabite `Google Search Console <https://search.google.com/search-"
"console/welcome>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:487
msgid ""
"Adding a subdomain label to a domain name (e.g., `subdomain.yourdomain.com`) "
"allows creating :doc:`multiple websites <multi_website>` with a single "
"domain name. To do so:"
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje oznake poddomene k domenskemu imenu (npr. "
"`poddomena.vasadomena.com`) omogoča ustvarjanje :doc:`več spletnih strani "
"<multi_website>` z enim samim domenskim imenom. To storite tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:490
msgid ""
"Add a CNAME record to forward your subdomain (e.g., "
"`subdomain.yourdomain.com`) to the address of your Odoo database (e.g., "
"`mycompany.odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte zapis CNAME za preusmeritev vaše poddomene (npr. "
"`poddomena.vasadomena.com`) na naslov vaše zbirke podatkov Odoo (npr. "
"`mojepodjetje.odoo.com`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:3
msgid "Google Search Console"
msgstr "Googlova konzola za iskanje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:5
msgid ""
"Google Search Console is a free web service provided by Google that allows "
"website owners to monitor, maintain, and troubleshoot their site's presence "
"in Google Search results. It offers valuable insights into how Google views "
"and interacts with your site, helping you optimize its performance."
msgstr ""
"Google Search Console je brezplačna spletna storitev, ki jo zagotavlja "
"Google in omogoča lastnikom spletnih mest nadzor, vzdrževanje in "
"odpravljanje težav pri prisotnosti njihovega spletnega mesta v rezultatih "
"iskanja Google. Ponuja dragocene vpoglede v to, kako Google gleda na vaše "
"spletno mesto in komunicira z njim, kar vam pomaga optimizirati njegovo "
"delovanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:10
msgid ""
"To enable Google Search Console for your website, go to `Google Search "
"Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/welcome>`_. Then, select "
"the property type :ref:`GSC-Domain` or :ref:`GSC-URL prefix`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti Google Search Console za vaše spletno mesto, pojdite na "
"`Google Search Console <https://search.google.com/search-console/welcome>`_. "
"Nato izberite vrsto lastnosti :ref:`GSC-Domain` ali :ref:`GSC-URL prefix`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:None
msgid "Google Search Console domain or URL prefix"
msgstr "Domena ali predpona URL-ja Google Search Console"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:20
msgid "Domain property"
msgstr "Lastnost domene"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:22
msgid ""
"A domain property in Search Console tracks all versions of your website, "
"including subdomains and protocols (http/https). This comprehensive view "
"allows you to analyze your overall website's search performance and make "
"informed decisions to optimize its visibility. Enter the domain, e.g., "
"`example.com` and click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Lastnost domene v Search Console sledi vsem različicam vašega spletnega "
"mesta, vključno s poddomenami in protokoli (http/https). Ta celovit pogled "
"vam omogoča analizo splošnega učinka vašega spletnega mesta v iskanju in "
"sprežemanje informiranih odločitev za optimizacijo njegove vidnosti. Vnesite "
"domeno, npr. `example.com`, in kliknite :guilabel:`Nadaljuj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:28
msgid ""
"The domain property type can only be verified via `DNS record <https://"
"support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_."
msgstr ""
"Vrsto lastnosti domene je mogoče preveriti samo prek `DNS zapisa <https://"
"support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:30
msgid ""
"Google suggests creating at least one domain property to represent your "
"site, as it is the most complete view of your website information."
msgstr ""
"Google priporoča ustvarjanje vsaj ene lastnosti domene za predstavitev "
"vašega spletnega mesta, saj je to najbolj celovit pogled na informacije o "
"vašem spletnem mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:36
msgid "URL prefix property"
msgstr "Lastnost predpone URL-ja"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:38
msgid ""
"This type of verification is usually simpler as you have multiple "
"verification methods, such as using your existing Google Analytics or Tag "
"Manager account. It also makes sense to view a section of your website "
"separately. For example, if you work with a consultant on a specific part of "
"your website, you might want to verify this part separately to limit access "
"to your data. Enter the URL, e.g., `https://example.odoo.com/` and "
"click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrsta preverjanja je običajno preprostejša, saj imate na voljo več "
"načinov preverjanja, kot je uporaba obstoječega računa Google Analytics ali "
"Tag Manager. Smiselno je tudi ločeno ogledati del vašega spletnega mesta. Na "
"primer, če delate s svetovalcem na določenem delu vašega spletnega mesta, "
"boste morda želeli ta del preveriti ločeno, da omejite dostop do vaših "
"podatkov. Vnesite URL, npr. `https://example.odoo.com/`, in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Nadaljuj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:46
msgid "Site ownership verification"
msgstr "Preverjanje lastništva spletnega mesta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:48
msgid ""
"Before using Google Search Console for your website, you must verify your "
"site ownership. This verification process is a security measure that "
"protects both you and Google. It ensures that only authorized users have "
"access to sensitive data and that you have control over how your website is "
"treated in Google Search."
msgstr ""
"Preden uporabite Google Search Console za vaše spletno mesto, morate "
"preveriti lastništvo spletnega mesta. Ta postopek preverjanja je varnostni "
"ukrep, ki ščiti tako vas kot Google. Zagotavlja, da imajo dostop do "
"občutljivih podatkov samo pooblaščeni uporabniki in da imate nadzor nad tem, "
"kako se z vašim spletnim mestom ravna v iskanju Google."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:53
msgid "Five methods are available to do this:"
msgstr "Na voljo je pet načinov za to:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:57
msgid ":ref:`GSC-HTML-file-upload`"
msgstr ":ref:`GSC-HTML-file-upload`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:58
msgid ""
"`DNS record <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"
msgstr ""
"`DNS zapis <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#domain_name_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:59
msgid ""
"`HTML tag <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#meta_tag_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"
msgstr ""
"`HTML oznaka <https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9008080?"
"hl=en#meta_tag_verification&zippy=%2Chtml-tag>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:60
msgid ""
"`Google Analytics tracking code <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_analytics_verification>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Koda za sledenje Google Analytics <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_analytics_verification>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:61
msgid ""
"`Google Tag Manager container snippet <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_tag_manager_verification>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Delček vsebnika Google Tag Manager <https://support.google.com/webmasters/"
"answer/9008080?hl=en#google_tag_manager_verification>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:64
msgid ""
"The best method for you depends on your comfort level and technical "
"expertise. For beginners, using a file upload or HTML tag might be easiest. "
"Those options are convenient if you already use :ref:`Google Analytics "
"<analytics/google-analytics>` or :ref:`Google Tag Manager <analytics/google-"
"tag-manager>`. You need to access your domain registrar's settings for "
"domain verification."
msgstr ""
"Najboljša metoda za vas je odvisna od vaše ravni udobja in tehničnega "
"znanja. Za začetnike je morda najlažja uporaba nalaganja datoteke ali HTML "
"oznake. Te možnosti so priročne, če že uporabljate :ref:`Google Analytics "
"<analytics/google-analytics>` ali :ref:`Google Tag Manager <analytics/google-"
"tag-manager>`. Za preverjanje domene morate dostopati do nastavitev "
"registratorja domene."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:73
msgid "HTML file upload"
msgstr "Nalaganje datoteke HTML"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:75
msgid ""
"This method involves uploading an HTML file provided by Google containing "
"the verification code you have to put in your Odoo's Website Settings. "
"Google verifies ownership by checking for this code."
msgstr ""
"Ta metoda vključuje nalaganje datoteke HTML, ki jo zagotovi Google in "
"vsebuje verifikacijsko kodo, ki jo morate vnesti v nastavitve spletnega "
"mesta Odoo. Google preveri lastništvo s preverjanjem te kode."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:78
msgid ""
"Once you added your website URL under the URL prefix option and "
"clicked :guilabel:`continue`, expand the HTML file section where you find a "
"download :icon:`fa-download` button."
msgstr ""
"Ko dodate URL svojega spletnega mesta pod možnost predpone URL in "
"kliknete :guilabel:`nadaljuj`, razširite razdelek datoteke HTML, kjer "
"najdete gumb za prenos :icon:`fa-download`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "HTML file download"
msgstr "Prenos datoteke HTML"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:84
msgid ""
"Download your HTML verification file and copy the verification code (e.g., "
"`google123abc.html`)."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite svojo verifikacijsko datoteko HTML in kopirajte verifikacijsko "
"kodo (npr. `google123abc.html`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Open and copy html file"
msgstr "Odprite in kopirajte datoteko html"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:89
msgid ""
"In your Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, and enable :guilabel:`Google Search Console` in "
"the :guilabel:`SEO` section. Paste the verification code (e.g., "
"`google123abc.html`) in the dedicated field."
msgstr ""
"V svoji zbirki podatkov Odoo pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in omogočite :guilabel:`Google Search Console` "
"v razdelku :guilabel:`SEO`. Prilepite verifikacijsko kodo (npr. "
"`google123abc.html`) v namensko polje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Paste html code in Odoo"
msgstr "Prilepite kodo html v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:96
msgid ""
"In Google Search Console, click :guilabel:`Verify`. If you perform the steps "
"above correctly, verification should be done immediately."
msgstr ""
"V Google Search Console kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri`. Če pravilno izvedete "
"zgornje korake, bi morala biti verifikacija opravljena takoj."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:102
msgid "HTML tag"
msgstr "Oznaka HTML"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:104
msgid ""
"This method involves copying a meta tag provided by Google and pasting it "
"into your Odoo website. To verify your site ownership using an HTML tag, "
"follow these instructions:"
msgstr ""
"Ta metoda vključuje kopiranje meta oznake, ki jo zagotovi Google, in njeno "
"lepljenje na spletno mesto Odoo. Če želite preveriti lastništvo spletnega "
"mesta z uporabo oznake HTML, sledite tem navodilom:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:107
msgid "Expand the HTML tag section."
msgstr "Razširite razdelek oznake HTML."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Open HTML tag section."
msgstr "Odprite razdelek oznake HTML."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:112
msgid ":guilabel:`Copy` the HTML tag to clipboard."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kopirajte` oznako HTML v odložišče."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:113
msgid ""
"On your Odoo website, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Theme` tab, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Advanced` "
"section, then click :guilabel:`<head> and </body>` next to :guilabel:`Code "
"Injection`. Paste the copied tag into the first field (:guilabel:`<head>`), "
"and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Na svojem spletnem mestu Odoo kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` v zgornjem desnem "
"kotu, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Tema`, se pomaknite navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Napredno`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`<head> in </body>` "
"poleg :guilabel:`Vstavljanje kode`. Prilepite kopirano oznako v prvo polje "
"(:guilabel:`<head>`) in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:0
msgid "Paste tag in head field."
msgstr "Prilepite oznako v polje head."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:121
msgid ""
"Return to :abbr:`GSC (Google Search Console)` and click :guilabel:`Verify`."
msgstr ""
"Vrnite se v :abbr:`GSC (Google Search Console)` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:124
msgid ":doc:`domain_names`"
msgstr ":doc:`domain_names`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to :doc:`create <../website_creation>` multiple websites "
"from the same database. This can be useful, for example, if you have "
"multiple brands operating under your organization, or if you want to create "
"separate websites for different products/services or audiences."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:10
msgid "Creating another website"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje druge spletne strani"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:12
msgid ""
"Creating multiple websites requires having *at least* one :doc:`domain name "
"<domain_names>`. Different alternatives exist, but before creating another "
"website, you should either"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje več spletnih strani zahteva, da imate *vsaj* eno :doc:`domensko "
"ime <domain_names>`. Obstajajo različne možnosti, vendar bi morali pred "
"ustvarjanjem druge spletne strani bodisi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:15
msgid ""
":ref:`Register a domain name for free with Odoo <domain-name/register>` for "
"your first website, then, for your second website, either:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Registrirati domensko ime brezplačno z Odoo <domain-name/register>` za "
"vašo prvo spletno stran, nato pa za vašo drugo spletno stran bodisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:18
msgid ""
":ref:`Use a subdomain of your free Odoo domain name <domain-name/register/"
"subdomains>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Uporabiti poddomeno vaše brezplačne domene Odoo <domain-name/register/"
"subdomains>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:19
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:25
msgid ":ref:`Use a domain name you purchased <domain-name/existing>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Uporabiti domensko ime, ki ste ga kupili <domain-name/existing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:21
msgid ""
":ref:`Use a domain name you purchased <domain-name/existing>` for your first "
"website, then, for your second website, either:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Uporabiti domensko ime, ki ste ga kupili <domain-name/existing>` za "
"vašo prvo spletno stran, nato pa za vašo drugo spletno stran bodisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:24
msgid ""
":ref:`Use a subdomain of your purchased domain name <domain-name/existing/"
"subdomains>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Uporabiti poddomeno vašega kupljenega domenskega imena <domain-name/"
"existing/subdomains>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:26
msgid ""
":ref:`Register a domain name for free with Odoo <domain-name/register>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Registrirati domensko ime brezplačno z Odoo <domain-name/register>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:28
msgid ""
"Once it is time to :ref:`map your second domain name's address to your "
"second Odoo website <domain-name/existing/website-map>`, you can `create "
"<../../website_creation>` it and map it directly by entering the second "
"website's address in the :guilabel:`Website Domain` field (e.g., `https://"
"www.yourseconddomain.com` or `https://subdomain.yourdomain.com`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:34
msgid ""
"To switch from one website's frontend to another, click the website "
"selection drop-down in the top right corner and select the website you want "
"to switch to."
msgstr ""
"Za preklop iz ene spletne strani na drugo kliknite spustni meni za izbiro "
"spletne strani v zgornjem desnem kotu in izberite spletno stran, na katero "
"želite preklopiti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:0
msgid "Selecting a website on the frontend"
msgstr "Izbira spletnega mesta na vmesniku"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:41
msgid "Website-specific configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija za določeno spletno mesto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:43
msgid ""
"Most website settings are website-specific. To access the settings of a "
"website, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"select the desired website using the website selection drop-down at the top "
"left of the settings page."
msgstr ""
"Večina nastavitev spletnega mesta je specifičnih za posamezno spletno mesto. "
"Za dostop do nastavitev spletnega mesta pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno "
"mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in izberite želeno spletno mesto z "
"uporabo spustnega menija za izbiro spletnega mesta v zgornjem levem kotu "
"strani z nastavitvami."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:None
msgid "Selecting a website in the app settings"
msgstr "Izbira spletnega mesta v nastavitvah aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:51
msgid ""
"Settings shared by all websites are indicated using the :icon:`fa-info-"
"circle` (:guilabel:`information`) icon."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve, ki so skupne vsem spletnim mestom, so označene z ikono :icon:`fa-"
"info-circle` (:guilabel:`informacije`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:0
msgid "Shared setting infobox"
msgstr "Informacijsko polje skupnih nastavitev"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:57
msgid ""
"When you create another website, it uses the default settings; settings are "
"not copied from one website to another."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite novo spletno mesto, se uporabijo privzete nastavitve; "
"nastavitve se ne kopirajo iz enega spletnega mesta na drugo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:61
msgid "eCommerce features"
msgstr "Funkcije e-trgovine"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:63
msgid ""
"eCommerce features such as products, eCommerce categories, pricelists, "
"discounts, payment providers, etc., can be restricted to :ref:`a specific "
"website <multi-website/website_content>`."
msgstr ""
"Funkcije eShopping, kot so izdelki, kategorije eShopping, ceniki, popusti, "
"ponudniki plačil itd., so lahko omejene na :ref:`določeno spletno mesto "
"<multi-website/website_content>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:69
msgid ""
"To :doc:`allow your customers to use the same account <../../ecommerce/"
"configuration/customer_accounts>` on all of your websites, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"enable :guilabel:`Shared Customer Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite :doc:`svojim strankam omogočiti uporabo istega računa <../../"
"ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts>` na vseh vaših spletnih mestih, "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` "
"in omogočite :guilabel:`Skupni računi strank`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:75
msgid "Pricing"
msgstr "Določanje cen"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:77
msgid ""
"Products can be priced differently based on the website "
"using :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`. To do so:"
msgstr ""
"Izdelki so lahko različno ocenjeni glede na spletno mesto z "
"uporabo :ref:`cenikov <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`. To storite "
"tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:81
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and select "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelists` option :guilabel:`Multiple prices per product`."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`Trgovina - Izdelki` in izberite "
"možnost :guilabel:`Ceniki` :guilabel:`Več cen na izdelek`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:83
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Pricelists` to define new pricelists or edit existing ones."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ceniki`, da določite nove cenike ali uredite obstoječe."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select the pricelist or click :guilabel:`New` to create a new one, then "
"select the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab and set the :guilabel:`Website` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Izberite cenik ali kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite novega, nato "
"izberite zavihek :guilabel:`Konfiguracija` in nastavite "
"polje :guilabel:`Spletno mesto`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:90
msgid "Content availability across websites"
msgstr "Razpoložljivost vsebine na spletnih mestih"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:93
msgid ""
"All installed website-related apps (e.g., eCommerce, eLearning, Forum, etc.) "
"and their related pages are also available on the new website. You can "
"remove them from the website's menu."
msgstr ""
"Vse nameščene aplikacije, povezane s spletnim mestom (npr. eShopping, "
"eUčenje, Forum itd.) in njihove povezane strani, so na voljo tudi na novem "
"spletnem mestu. Odstranite jih lahko iz menija spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:96
msgid ""
"By default, most records (products, courses, forum posts, etc.) created from "
"the frontend are displayed on all websites. To restrict the content to a "
"single website, search for the :guilabel:`Website` field in the backend."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so večina zapisov (izdelki, tečaji, objave na forumu itd.), "
"ustvarjenih iz vmesnika, prikazanih na vseh spletnih mestih. Če želite "
"omejiti vsebino na eno samo spletno mesto, poiščite polje :guilabel:`Spletno "
"mesto` v zalednem sistemu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:100
msgid ""
"For example, for products, go to :menuselection:`eCommerce --> Products`, "
"select a product, open the :guilabel:`eCommerce` tab, and specify which "
"website the product should be available on."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, za izdelke pojdite na :menuselection:`eShopping --> Izdelki`, "
"izberite izdelek, odprite zavihek :guilabel:`eShopping` in določite, na "
"katerem spletnem mestu naj bo izdelek na voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:None
msgid "Restricting a product to a single website"
msgstr "Omejevanje izdelka na eno samo spletno mesto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:107
msgid ""
"In a :doc:`multi-company environment </applications/general/companies>`, "
"each website can be linked to a specific company so that only that company's "
"data (e.g., products, events, etc.) is displayed on the website. To display "
"company-specific data, go to :guilabel:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and set the desired company in the :guilabel:`Company` field."
msgstr ""
"V :doc:`večpodjetniškemu okolju </applications/general/companies>` je lahko "
"vsako spletno mesto povezano z določenim podjetjem, tako da so na spletnem "
"mestu prikazani samo podatki tega podjetja (npr. izdelki, dogodki itd.). Za "
"prikaz podatkov, specifičnih za podjetje, pojdite na :guilabel:`Spletno "
"mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in nastavite želeno podjetje v "
"polju :guilabel:`Podjetje`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:113
msgid ""
"When generating links, for example, a customer portal link to a quotation, "
"Odoo uses the following logic to select the website domain:"
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju povezav, na primer povezave portala za stranke do ponudbe, "
"Odoo uporablja naslednjo logiko za izbiro domene spletnega mesta:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:116
msgid "If a company has a *single* website, that website's domain is used."
msgstr ""
"Če ima podjetje *eno samo* spletno mesto, se uporabi domena tega spletnega "
"mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:117
msgid ""
"If a company has *multiple* websites, Odoo uses the domain of the website "
"that was created first. To change the order of priority, "
"enable :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go to :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Configuration --> Websites`, and use the :icon:`oi-draggable` "
"(:guilabel:`drag handle`) icon to reorder websites."
msgstr ""
"Če ima podjetje *več* spletnih mest, Odoo uporabi domeno spletnega mesta, ki "
"je bilo ustvarjeno prvo. Za spremembo vrstnega reda prednosti "
"omogočite :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Spletna mesta` in "
"uporabite ikono :icon:`oi-draggable` (:guilabel:`ročaj za vlečenje`) za "
"prerazporeditev spletnih mest."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:121
msgid ""
"If a company's website has *no domain*, the :ref:`web base URL <domain-name/"
"existing/db-map/web-base-url>` is used."
msgstr ""
"Če spletno mesto podjetja *nima domene*, se uporabi :ref:`osnovni spletni "
"URL <domain-name/existing/db-map/web-base-url>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:125
msgid "Website pages"
msgstr "Strani spletnega mesta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:127
msgid "To modify the website on which a page is published, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo spletnega mesta, na katerem je stran objavljena, sledite "
"naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:129
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."
msgstr "Pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Stran --> Strani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:130
msgid ""
"Open the search panel and select the website on which the page is currently "
"published."
msgstr ""
"Odprite iskalno ploščo in izberite spletno mesto, na katerem je stran "
"trenutno objavljena."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:0
msgid "Display pages per website"
msgstr "Prikaz strani po spletnem mestu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:135
msgid "Tick the check box next to the page(s) you want to change."
msgstr "Označite potrditveno polje poleg strani, ki jih želite spremeniti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:136
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Website` field and select the website, or empty it to "
"publish the page on all websites."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite polje :guilabel:`Spletno mesto` in izberite spletno mesto ali ga "
"izpraznite, da objavite stran na vseh spletnih mestih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:140
msgid ""
"Each website must have its own homepage; you may not use the same homepage "
"for several websites."
msgstr ""
"Vsako spletno mesto mora imeti svojo domačo stran; iste domače strani ne "
"smete uporabljati za več spletnih mest."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:145
msgid ""
"Each website has its own :ref:`analytics <analytics/plausible>`. To switch "
"between websites, use the buttons in the top right corner."
msgstr ""
"Vsako spletno mesto ima svoje :ref:`analitike <analytics/plausible>`. Za "
"preklop med spletnimi mesti uporabite gumbe v zgornjem desnem kotu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:None
msgid "Switching websites in analytics"
msgstr "Preklop med spletnimi mesti v analitikah"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:151
msgid ""
"Other reporting data, such as eCommerce dashboard data, online sales "
"analyses, and visitors, can be grouped by website by opening the search "
"panel and selecting :guilabel:`Group by --> Website`."
msgstr ""
"Drugi podatki poročanja, kot so podatki nadzorne plošče e-trgovine, analize "
"spletne prodaje in obiskovalci, se lahko združijo po spletnem mestu tako, da "
"odprete iskalno ploščo in izberete :guilabel:`Združi po --> Spletno mesto`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:3
msgid "Forms spam protection"
msgstr "Zaščita obrazcev pred neželeno pošto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:5
msgid ""
":ref:`Cloudflare Turnstile <website/spam_protection/cloudflare-turnstile>` "
"and :ref:`Google reCAPTCHA v3 <website/spam_protection/google-recaptcha>` "
"protect website forms against spam and abuse. They attempt to distinguish "
"between human and bot submissions using non-interactive challenges based on "
"telemetry and visitor behavior."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Cloudflare Turnstile <website/spam_protection/cloudflare-turnstile>` "
"in :ref:`Google reCAPTCHA v3 <website/spam_protection/google-recaptcha>` "
"ščitita obrazce spletnih mest pred nezaželeno pošto in zlorabo. Poskušata "
"razlikovati med človeškimi in botovskimi prispevki z uporabo neinteraktivnih "
"izzivov, ki temeljijo na telemetriji in obnašanju obiskovalcev."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:11
msgid ""
"We recommend using **Cloudflare Turnstile**, as reCAPTCHA v3 may not be "
"compliant with local data protection regulations."
msgstr ""
"Priporočamo uporabo **Cloudflare Turnstile**, saj reCAPTCHA v3 morda ni v "
"skladu z lokalnimi predpisi o varstvu podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:15
msgid ""
"All pages using the :guilabel:`Form`, :guilabel:`Newsletter Block`, "
"or :guilabel:`Newsletter Popup` snippets are protected by both tools. Web "
"login, sign-up and password reset pages are also protected."
msgstr ""
"Vse strani, ki uporabljajo izrezke :guilabel:`Obrazec`, :guilabel:`Blok e-"
"novic` ali :guilabel:`Pojavno okno e-novic`, so zaščitene z obema orodjema. "
"Zaščitene so tudi strani za spletno prijavo, registracijo in ponastavitev "
"gesla."

