msgid ""
"To translate a website page, switch to the language to translate and "
"click :menuselection:`Edit --> Translate` in the top-right corner to "
"activate the translation mode."
msgstr ""
"Za prevajanje strani spletnega mesta preklopite na jezik, ki ga želite "
"prevesti, in kliknite :menuselection:`Edit --> Translate` v zgornjem desnem "
"kotu, da aktivirate način prevajanja."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:80
msgid ""
"In this mode, only translatable text can be edited. Any other type of "
"modification with the website builder must be carried out while using the "
"default language."
msgstr ""
"V tem načinu je mogoče urejati samo besedilo, ki ga je mogoče prevesti. Vse "
"druge spremembe z gradnikom spletnih mest je treba izvesti pri uporabi "
"privzetega jezika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:82
msgid ""
"Depending on the language added, some default content may already be "
"translated. However, the content you added manually should be translated "
"using the :guilabel:`Translate` feature."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od dodanega jezika je nekatere privzete vsebine morda že preveden. "
"Vendar je treba vsebino, ki ste jo dodali ročno, prevesti z uporabo "
"funkcije :guilabel:`Translate`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:84
msgid ""
"When text is highlighted in green, it indicates that it has already been "
"translated (manually or automatically). When text is highlighted in yellow, "
"it indicates that it has not been translated."
msgstr ""
"Ko je besedilo označeno zeleno, to pomeni, da je bilo že prevedeno (ročno "
"ali samodejno). Ko je besedilo označeno rumeno, to pomeni, da ni bilo "
"prevedeno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:88
msgid ""
"Click the green button next to the :guilabel:`Translated to` field to "
"automatically translate all text highlighted in yellow. You can also "
"manually translate or adapt text, whether it is highlighted in green or "
"yellow, by selecting it and editing it. Click :guilabel:`Save` when you are "
"done translating."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zeleni gumb poleg polja :guilabel:`Translated to`, da samodejno "
"prevedete vse besedilo, označeno rumeno. Lahko tudi ročno prevedete ali "
"prilagodite besedilo, ne glede na to, ali je označeno zeleno ali rumeno, "
"tako da ga izberete in uredite. Ko končate s prevajanjem, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:None
msgid "Entering the translation mode"
msgstr "Vstop v prevajalski način"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:97
msgid ""
"The core URL structure remains consistent across languages, while specific "
"elements like product names or categories are translated. For example, "
"`https://www.mywebsite.com/shop/product/my-product-1` is the default version "
"of a product page, while `https://www.mywebsite.com/fr/shop/product/mon-"
"produit-1` is the translated version of the same product page. The structure "
"(`/shop/product/`) remains unchanged, but the product name (`my-product`) is "
"translated (`mon-produit`)."
msgstr ""
"Osnovna struktura URL-ja ostaja dosledna v vseh jezikih, medtem ko so "
"določeni elementi, kot so imena izdelkov ali kategorije, prevedeni. Na "
"primer, `https://www.mywebsite.com/shop/product/my-product-1` je privzeta "
"različica strani izdelka, medtem ko je `https://www.mywebsite.com/fr/shop/"
"product/mon-produit-1` prevedena različica iste strani izdelka. Struktura (`/"
"shop/product/`) ostane nespremenjena, vendar je ime izdelka (`my-product`) "
"prevedeno (`mon-produit`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:103
msgid ""
"Some elements can also be translated from the backend (e.g., product names)."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere elemente je mogoče prevesti tudi iz zalednega sistema (npr. imena "
"izdelkov)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:106
msgid "Translate SEO-related elements"
msgstr "Prevajanje elementov, povezanih s SEO"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:108
msgid ""
"To translate an :ref:`image's alt tag <seo/images>` (i.e., the "
"image's :guilabel:`Description` field) and title tag (i.e., the "
"image's :guilabel:`Tooltip` field), switch to the language to translate, "
"click :menuselection:`Edit --> Translate`, and select the image. In "
"the :guilabel:`Translate Attribute` box, enter the translation for "
"the :guilabel:`alt` and/or the :guilabel:`title` tags."
msgstr ""
"Za prevajanje :ref:`oznake alt slike <seo/images>` (tj. "
"polja :guilabel:`Description` slike) in oznake naslova (tj. "
"polja :guilabel:`Tooltip` slike) preklopite na jezik, ki ga želite prevesti, "
"kliknite :menuselection:`Edit --> Translate` in izberite sliko. V "
"polju :guilabel:`Translate Attribute` vnesite prevod za "
"oznaki :guilabel:`alt` in/ali :guilabel:`title`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:114
msgid ""
"To add translated :ref:`meta tags <seo/meta-tags>`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Optimize SEO`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Keywords` section, select the language and add the keywords."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje prevedenih :ref:`metaoznake <seo/meta-tags>` pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Optimize SEO`. V "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Keywords` izberite jezik in dodajte ključne besede."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:118
msgid ""
"When viewing a website in its default language, all keywords are displayed, "
"regardless of their language. However, when viewing a website in another "
"language, only the keywords relevant to that language are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Pri ogledu spletnega mesta v privzetem jeziku so prikazane vse ključne "
"besede, ne glede na njihov jezik. Pri ogledu spletnega mesta v drugem jeziku "
"pa so prikazane samo ključne besede, ki so relevantne za ta jezik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/translate.rst:123
msgid ":doc:`Search Engine Optimization <../structure/seo>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Search Engine Optimization <../structure/seo>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **mail groups** feature allows website visitors to have a public "
"discussion by email. They can join a group to receive emails from other "
"group members (i.e., website users who have subscribed to the group) and "
"send new ones to all group members."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija **poštnih skupin** omogoča obiskovalcem spletnega mesta javno "
"razpravo prek e-pošte. Lahko se pridružijo skupini, da prejemajo e-pošto od "
"drugih članov skupine (tj. uporabnikov spletnega mesta, ki so se naročili na "
"skupino) in pošljejo nove vsem članom skupine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:9
msgid ""
"To activate the feature, :ref:`install <general/install>` "
"the :guilabel:`Website Mail Group` (`website_mail_group`) module."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:13
msgid ""
"The **mail groups** feature is not to be confused with the :doc:`../../"
"marketing/email_marketing/mailing_lists` in the Email Marketing app."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:19
msgid "Configuring mail groups"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:21
msgid "To configure mail groups, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:23
msgid ""
"Configure a custom email alias domain by accessing the **General settings**, "
"scrolling down to the :guilabel:`Discuss` section, enabling "
"the :guilabel:`Custom Email Server` feature, and entering "
"the :guilabel:`Alias domain` (e.g., `@mycompany.com`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:26
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Mailing Lists`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:27
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`Group Name`, the :guilabel:`Email Alias`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Description`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:28
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Moderate this group` and specify "
"the :guilabel:`Moderators` if you wish to :ref:`moderate messages <website/"
"mailing_lists/moderate>` from this group. Alternatively, if the group is not "
"moderated, you can define :guilabel:`Responsible Users` who can manage the "
"messages in the group."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Privacy` tab, define who can subscribe to the mail group:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Everyone`: to make the mail group public so anyone can subscribe "
"to it;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Members only`: to only allow users defined as members to "
"subscribe to the mail group;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Selected group of users`: to only allow users from "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized group` to subscribe to the mail group."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:39
msgid ""
"If the mail group is moderated, you can automatically notify authors when "
"their message is pending moderation by enabling :guilabel:`Automatic "
"notification` in the :guilabel:`Notify Members` tab and writing "
"the :guilabel:`Notification message`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:42
msgid ""
"If you wish to send out guidelines to new subscribers, "
"enable :guilabel:`Send guidelines to new subscribers` and write them in "
"the :guilabel:`Guidelines` tab. This is particularly useful when the mail "
"group is moderated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:47
msgid "Using mail groups"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:50
msgid "Subscribing/unsubscribing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:52
msgid ""
"Based on the :ref:`configuration of the mail group <website/mailing_lists/"
"configure_groups>`, users can subscribe to and unsubscribe from mail groups "
"from the website page (`/groups` by default)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:None
msgid "Mail group web page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:58
msgid ""
"Internal users can also do this from :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Mailing Lists`, using the :guilabel:`Join` "
"and :guilabel:`Leave` buttons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:62
msgid "Sending messages"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:64
msgid ""
"To send messages to a mail group, website users can email the :ref:`mail "
"group's email address <website/mailing_lists/configure_groups>`. Internal "
"users can also create messages directly from Odoo. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Mailing Lists`, select the "
"mail group, click the :guilabel:`Emails` smart button, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Then, fill in the fields and click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Za pošiljanje sporočil skupini lahko uporabniki spletnega mesta po e-pošti "
"uporabijo :ref:`e-poštni naslov skupine <website/mailing_lists/"
"configure_groups>`. Notranji uporabniki lahko sporočila ustvarijo tudi "
"neposredno v Odoo. To storite tako, da greste v :menuselection:`Spletno "
"mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Poštni seznami`, izberete skupino, kliknete "
"pametni gumb :guilabel:`E-pošta` in kliknete :guilabel:`Novo`. Nato "
"izpolnite polja in kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:71
msgid ""
"The list of messages can also be accessed by selecting the group from the `/"
"groups` website page."
msgstr ""
"Do seznama sporočil lahko dostopate tudi tako, da izberete skupino na "
"spletni strani `/groups`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:73
msgid ""
"Group members can also unsubscribe from the group, access the mail group "
"page, and send emails to the group using the URLs in the footer of any group "
"email they have received."
msgstr ""
"Člani skupine se lahko tudi odjavijo iz skupine, dostopajo do strani skupine "
"in pošiljajo e-pošto skupini s pomočjo naslovov URL v nogi katerega koli e-"
"poštnega sporočila skupine, ki so ga prejeli."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:0
msgid "URLs in the footer of a group email."
msgstr "Naslovi URL v nogi e-poštnega sporočila skupine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:82
msgid "Moderating mail group messages"
msgstr "Moderiranje sporočil poštne skupine"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:84
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Moderate this group` feature has been enabled for "
"the :ref:`mail group <website/mailing_lists/configure_groups>`, one of "
"the :guilabel:`Moderators` must approve the group's messages before they are "
"dispatched to the other members."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila za :ref:`poštno skupino <website/mailing_lists/configure_groups>` "
"omogočena funkcija :guilabel:`Moderiraj to skupino`, mora eden "
"od :guilabel:`Moderatorjev` odobriti sporočila skupine, preden so poslana "
"drugim članom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:88
msgid ""
"To moderate messages, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Mailing Lists`, select the mail group, and click the :guilabel:`To review` "
"smart button. You can moderate messages using the buttons at the end of the "
"message line or select a message to view its content and moderate it "
"accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Za moderiranje sporočil pojdite v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Poštni seznami`, izberite poštno skupino in kliknite "
"pametni gumb :guilabel:`Za pregled`. Sporočila lahko moderirate s pomočjo "
"gumbov na koncu vrstice sporočila ali izberete sporočilo, si ogledate "
"njegovo vsebino in ga ustrezno moderirate."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:0
msgid "Moderation buttons in the message line."
msgstr "Gumbi za moderiranje v vrstici sporočila."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:96
msgid "The following actions are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednja dejanja:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:98
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accept`: to accept the email and send it to the mail group "
"members."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sprejmi`: za sprejetje e-pošte in pošiljanje članom skupine."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reject`: to reject the email. In the pop-up window that opens, "
"click :guilabel:`Reject Silently` to reject the email without notifying the "
"author, or specify an explanation for rejecting the message, then "
"click :guilabel:`Send & Reject` to reject the message and send the "
"explanation to the author."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zavrni`: za zavrnitev e-pošte. V pojavnem oknu, ki se odpre, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Tiho zavrni`, če želite zavrniti e-pošto brez obveščanja "
"avtorja, ali navedite razlog za zavrnitev sporočila in nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji in zavrni`, da zavrnete sporočilo in pošljete "
"razlago avtorju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Whitelist`: to whitelist the author, i.e. automatically accept "
"all of their emails. As a result, a :ref:`moderation rule <website/"
"mailing_lists/moderate>` is created for the author's email address with the "
"status :guilabel:`Always allow`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Beli seznam`: za dodajanje avtorja na beli seznam, tj. samodejno "
"sprejemanje vseh njegovih e-poštnih sporočil. Posledično se za avtorjev e-"
"poštni naslov ustvari :ref:`pravilo moderiranja <website/mailing_lists/"
"moderate>` s statusom :guilabel:`Vedno dovoli`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Ban`: to blacklist the author, i.e. automatically discard all "
"their emails. In the pop-up window that opens, click :guilabel:`Ban` to ban "
"the author without notifying them, or specify an explanation, then "
"click :guilabel:`Send & Ban` to ban the author and send them the "
"explanation. As a result, a :ref:`moderation rule <website/mailing_lists/"
"moderate>` is created for the author's email address with the "
"status :guilabel:`Permanent ban`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prepovedati`: za dodajanje avtorja na črni seznam, tj. samodejno "
"zavračanje vseh njegovih e-poštnih sporočil. V pojavnem oknu, ki se odpre, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Prepovedati`, če želite prepovedati avtorja brez "
"obveščanja, ali navedite razlago in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji in "
"prepovedati`, da prepoveste avtorja in mu pošljete razlago. Posledično se za "
"avtorjev e-poštni naslov ustvari :ref:`pravilo moderiranja <website/"
"mailing_lists/moderate>` s statusom :guilabel:`Trajna prepoved`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:113
msgid ""
"Messages can also be moderated from the group's list of messages. Go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Groups --> Mailing List Groups`, select the "
"mail group and click the :guilabel:`Emails` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila lahko moderirate tudi s seznama sporočil skupine. Pojdite "
"v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Skupine --> Skupine poštnih seznamov`, "
"izberite poštno skupino in kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`E-pošta`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:120
msgid "Whitelisting/Blacklisting authors"
msgstr "Dodajanje avtorjev na beli/črni seznam"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:122
msgid ""
"You can whitelist or blacklist an author either directly :ref:`from a mail "
"group message <website/mailing_lists/moderate>`, or by creating a moderation "
"rule. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Moderation Rules` and click :guilabel:`New`. Then, select "
"the :guilabel:`Group`, specify the author's :guilabel:`Email` and set "
"the :guilabel:`Status` field."
msgstr ""
"Avtorja lahko dodate na beli ali črni seznam bodisi neposredno :ref:`iz "
"sporočila poštne skupine <website/mailing_lists/moderate>` bodisi z "
"ustvarjanjem pravila moderiranja. To storite tako, da greste "
"v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Pravila moderiranja` "
"in kliknete :guilabel:`Novo`. Nato izberite :guilabel:`Skupino`, navedite "
"avtorjev :guilabel:`E-poštni naslov` in nastavite polje :guilabel:`Status`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:129
msgid ""
"You can also access the mail group's moderation rules by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Mailing Lists`, selecting "
"the group, then clicking the :guilabel:`Moderations` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Do pravil moderiranja poštne skupine lahko dostopate tudi tako, da greste "
"v :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> Konfiguracija --> Poštni seznami`, "
"izberete skupino in nato kliknete pametni gumb :guilabel:`Moderiranja`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:3
msgid "Website analytics"
msgstr "Spletna analitika"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:5
msgid ""
"Website analytics helps website owners monitor how people use their site. It "
"provides data on visitor demographics, behavior, and interactions, helping "
"improve websites and marketing strategies."
msgstr ""
"Spletna analitika pomaga lastnikom spletnih mest spremljati, kako ljudje "
"uporabljajo njihovo spletno mesto. Zagotavlja podatke o demografskih "
"značilnostih obiskovalcev, vedenju in interakcijah ter pomaga izboljševati "
"spletna mesta in trženjske strategije."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can track your Odoo website's traffic using :ref:`analytics/plausible` "
"or :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`. We recommend using Plausible.io as it "
"is privacy-friendly, lightweight, and easy to use."
msgstr ""
"Promet na svoji spletni strani Odoo lahko spremljate s "
"pomočjo :ref:`analytics/plausible` ali :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`. "
"Priporočamo uporabo Plausible.io, saj spoštuje zasebnost, je lahek in "
"enostaven za uporabo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:15
msgid "Plausible.io"
msgstr "Plausible.io"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:17
msgid ""
"Odoo hosts its own Plausible.io server. The Plausible Analytics dashboard is "
"integrated into Odoo and can be accessed via :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Reporting --> Analytics`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo gostuje svoj lastni strežnik Plausible.io. Nadzorna plošča Plausible "
"Analytics je integrirana v Odoo in je dostopna prek :menuselection:`Spletno "
"mesto --> Poročanje --> Analitika`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:20
msgid ""
"Databases hosted on Odoo Online and using an `odoo.com` domain name benefit "
"from a free, ready-to-use Plausible.io solution with automatically generated "
"credentials and a preconfigured Plausible account. To enable it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, then, in "
"the :guilabel:`Tracking & SEO` section, enable :guilabel:`Plausible "
"Analytics`. The credentials are automatically filled in "
"the :guilabel:`Shared Link Auth` and the :guilabel:`Site` fields."
msgstr ""
"Baze podatkov, gostovane na Odoo Online in uporabljajo domeno `odoo.com`, "
"imajo brezplačno, pripravljeno za uporabo rešitev Plausible.io z samodejno "
"ustvarjenimi poverilnicami in vnaprej konfiguriranim računom Plausible. Če "
"jo želite omogočiti, pojdite na :menuselection:`Spletno mesto --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, nato v razdelku :guilabel:`Sledenje in SEO` "
"omogočite :guilabel:`Plausible Analytics`. Poverilnice so samodejno "
"izpolnjene v poljih :guilabel:`Overitev deljene povezave` "
"in :guilabel:`Spletno mesto`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:28
msgid ""
"**If you already have a Plausible.io account** and you want to connect it to "
"your Odoo Online database, you must create two `ir.config.parameters` to use "
"Plausible.io's servers. To do so, enable the :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>` and go to :menuselection:`General Settings --> Technical --> System "
"Parameters`. Click :guilabel:`New` and fill in the following :guilabel:`Key` "
"and :guilabel:`Value` fields:"
msgstr ""
"**Pokud již máte účet Plausible.io** a chcete jej připojit k vaší databázi "
"Odoo Online, musíte vytvořit dva `ir.config.parameters` pro použití serverů "
"Plausible.io. Chcete-li to provést, zapněte :ref:`vývojářský režim "
"<developer-mode>` a přejděte na :menuselection:`Obecné nastavení --> "
"Technické --> Systémové parametry`. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Nový` a vyplňte "
"následující pole :guilabel:`Klíč` a :guilabel:`Hodnota`:"

