"Spletno mesto se prepričajte, da je iz spustnega menija na vrhu strani "
"izbrano pravilno spletno mesto, preden prilepite :guilabel:`Deljeno "
"povezavo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:90
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically pushes two custom goals: `Lead Generation` and `Shop`. "
"Custom goals can be added via Plausible.io. To do so, click the :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`ellipsis`) button on the relevant website card, then "
"navigate to :guilabel:`Goals` in the sidebar menu, and click :guilabel:`Add "
"goal`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno potisne dva ciljna cilja: `Lead Generation` in `Shop`. Cilje "
"po meri je mogoče dodati prek Plausible.io. To storite tako, da kliknete "
"gumb :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`tri pike`) na ustrezni kartici "
"spletnega mesta, nato se pomaknete do :guilabel:`Goals` v meniju stranske "
"vrstice in kliknete :guilabel:`Add goal`."

