"support.google.com/analytics/answer/9304153?hl=en/"
"&visit_id=638278591144564289-3612494643&rd=2#property>`_ na domeno. V Odoo v "
"nastavitvah :guilabel:`Website` pred lepljenjem :guilabel:`Measurement ID` "
"poskrbite, da izberete spletno mesto v polju poleg `+New website` v zgornjem "
"levem delu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/analytics.rst:136
msgid ""
"`Google documentation on setting up Analytics for a website <https://"
