#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to :ref:`create <website/pages/page_creation>` different "
"kinds of webpages, including with the help of :ref:`AI <website/pages/ai-"
"generator>`, :ref:`publish <website/pages/un-publish-page>` them, and define "
"their structure and visibility by configuring :ref:`page properties <website/"
"pages/page_properties>`. Pages can be :ref:`duplicated <website/pages/"
"duplicate-page>`, :ref:`deleted <website/pages/delete-page>`, "
"and :ref:`redirected <website/pages/URL-redirection>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo vam omogoča :ref:`ustvarjanje <website/pages/page_creation>` različnih "
"vrst spletnih strani, tudi s pomočjo :ref:`AI <website/pages/ai-generator>`, "
"njihovo :ref:`objavo <website/pages/un-publish-page>` in določanje njihove "
"strukture in vidnosti s konfiguriranjem :ref:`lastnosti strani <website/"
"pages/page_properties>`. Strani je mogoče :ref:`podvojiti <website/pages/"
"duplicate-page>`, :ref:`izbrisati <website/pages/delete-page>` "
"in :ref:`preusmeriti <website/pages/URL-redirection>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:16
msgid "Page types"
msgstr "Vrste strani"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Static** pages, such as the homepage or :ref:`custom <website/pages/"
"page_creation>` pages, contain fixed content that does not change "
"dynamically. You can manually create these pages, define their URLs, and "
"adapt their :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_properties>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"**Statične** strani, kot so domača stran ali strani :ref:`po meri <website/"
"pages/page_creation>`, vsebujejo fiksno vsebino, ki se ne spreminja "
"dinamično. Te strani lahko ročno ustvarite, določite njihove URL-je in po "
"potrebi prilagodite njihove :ref:`lastnosti <website/pages/page_properties>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Dynamic** pages, on the other hand, display content that changes "
"automatically based on the data in the database and user interaction (e.g., "
"filtering). They are generated automatically by Odoo, for example, when "
"installing an app or module (e.g., `/shop` or `/blog`) or publishing a "
"new :doc:`product <../../ecommerce>` or :doc:`blog post <../../blog>`. "
"Dynamic pages are managed differently from static pages."
msgstr ""
"**Dinamične** strani pa prikazujejo vsebino, ki se samodejno spreminja glede "
"na podatke v bazi podatkov in interakcijo uporabnika (npr. filtriranje). "
"Odoo jih ustvarja samodejno, na primer pri namestitvi aplikacije ali modula "
"(npr. `/shop` ali `/blog`) ali objavi novega :doc:`izdelka <../../"
"ecommerce>` ali :doc:`blog objave <../../blog>`. Dinamične strani se "
"upravljajo drugače kot statične strani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:31
msgid "Page creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje strani"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:33
