msgstr "Ko opravite želene spremembe, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:122
msgid "Add an Odoo contact form on a non-Odoo website"
msgstr "Dodajte kontaktni obrazec Odoo na spletno mesto zunaj Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:124
msgid ""
"You can display an Odoo contact form on another website using an iframe. To "
"do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Kontaktni obrazec Odoo lahko prikažete na drugem spletnem mestu z uporabo "
"iframe. To storite tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:127
msgid ""
"**Prepare the Odoo form:** Create a contact form on a page in Odoo Website "
"and remove the :ref:`header design <website/header_footer/header-design>` "
"and the :ref:`footer design <website/header_footer/footer-design>`. Make "
"sure only the contact form remains on the page."
msgstr ""
"**Pripravite obrazec Odoo:** Ustvarite kontaktni obrazec na strani v Odoo "
"Website in odstranite :ref:`oblikovanje glave <website/header_footer/header-"
"design>` ter :ref:`oblikovanje noge <website/header_footer/footer-design>`. "
"Prepričajte se, da na strani ostane samo kontaktni obrazec."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:130
msgid ""
"**Generate an embeddable code:** Copy the URL of the Odoo form page and "
"paste it into an iframe generator, such as `La Digitale.dev <https://"
"ladigitale.dev/digitools/generateur-iframe>`_ or `iFrame Generator <https://"
"www.iframe-generator.com/>`_ . Adjust the width and height for proper "
"display."
msgstr ""
"**Ustvarite vgrajen kodo:** Kopirajte URL strani obrazca Odoo in ga "
"prilepite v generator iframe, kot je `La Digitale.dev <https://"
"ladigitale.dev/digitools/generateur-iframe>`_ ali `iFrame Generator <https://"
"www.iframe-generator.com/>`_. Prilagodite širino in višino za pravilen "
"prikaz."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:134
msgid ""
"**Add the embedded code to the non-Odoo website:** Open the relevant page’s "
"HTML (in the code editor or CMS) and insert the embedded code where the form "
"should be displayed."
msgstr ""
"**Dodajte vgrajeno kodo na spletno mesto zunaj Odoo:** Odprite HTML ustrezne "
"strani (v urejevalniku kode ali CMS) in vstavite vgrajeno kodo na mesto, "
"kjer naj bo prikazan obrazec."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:138
msgid "Example of an embedded code:"
msgstr "Primer vgrajene kode:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:157
msgid "Embed code"
msgstr "Vdelana koda"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:159
msgid ""
"Embedding code allows you to integrate content from third-party services "
"into a page, such as videos from YouTube, maps from Google Maps, social "
"media posts from Instagram, etc."
msgstr ""
"Vdeljevanje kode omogoča integracijo vsebine storitev tretjih oseb na stran, "
"kot so videoposnetki z YouTube, zemljevidi iz Google Maps, objave na "
"družbenih omrežjih z Instagrama itd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:162
msgid ""
"After dragging and dropping the :guilabel:`Embed Code` block from "
"the :guilabel:`Inner Content` section into a page, click the block, then go "
"to the :guilabel:`Style` tab and click :guilabel:`Edit`. Replace the "
"placeholder code with your custom embed code."
msgstr ""
"Ko povlečete in spustite blok :guilabel:`Vdelana koda` iz "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Notranja vsebina` na stran, kliknite blok, nato pojdite "
"na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi`. Zamenjajte "
"nadomestno kodo s svojo kodo za vdelavo po meri."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:None
msgid "Add the link to the embedded code you want to point to"
msgstr "Dodajte povezavo do vdelane kode, na katero želite kazati"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:170
msgid ""
"Do not copy/paste code you do not understand, as it could put your data at "
"risk."
msgstr ""
"Ne kopirajte/prilepite kode, ki je ne razumete, saj bi lahko ogrozila "
"varnost vaših podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:175
msgid "Move, switch, duplicate or delete a building block"
msgstr "Premikanje, zamenjava, podvajanje ali brisanje gradbenega bloka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:177
msgid ""
"Pull the turquoise borders on the block to reduce or increase the space at "
"the top or bottom of it."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite turkizne robove na bloku, da zmanjšate ali povečate prostor na "
"vrhu ali dnu bloka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:179
msgid ""
"Change the block order by clicking :icon:`fa-chevron-up` (:guilabel:`chevron "
"up`) or :icon:`fa-chevron-down` (:guilabel:`chevron down`) and move the "
"block on the page by clicking :icon:`fa-arrows` (:guilabel:`arrows`). When "
"you have multiple :ref:`columns <website/building_blocks/cols>`, move a "
"column to the left or right by clicking :icon:`fa-chevron-left` "
"(:guilabel:`chevron left`) or :icon:`fa-chevron-right` (:guilabel:`chevron "
"right`)."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite vrstni red blokov s klikom na :icon:`fa-chevron-up` "
"(:guilabel:`puščica gor`) ali :icon:`fa-chevron-down` (:guilabel:`puščica "
"dol`) in premaknite blok po strani s klikom na :icon:`fa-arrows` "
"(:guilabel:`puščice`). Ko imate več :ref:`stolpcev <website/building_blocks/"
"cols>`, premaknite stolpec v levo ali desno s klikom na :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"left` (:guilabel:`puščica levo`) ali :icon:`fa-chevron-right` "
"(:guilabel:`puščica desno`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:186
msgid ""
"To duplicate a building block, click :icon:`fa-clone` "
"(:guilabel:`duplicate`). Once duplicated, the new block appears on the page "
"beneath the original one."
msgstr ""
"Če želite podvojiti gradbeni blok, kliknite :icon:`fa-clone` "
"(:guilabel:`podvoji`). Ko je podvojen, se nov blok prikaže na strani pod "
"izvirnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:190
msgid ""
"Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`duplicate`) icon at "
"the top of the :guilabel:`Style` tab to duplicate the selected block."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`podvoji`) "
"na vrhu zavihka :guilabel:`Slog`, da podvojite izbrani blok."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:193
msgid "To delete a block, click :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`trash`)."
msgstr "Če želite izbrisati blok, kliknite :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`koš`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Extend margins on building block"
msgstr "Razširite robove gradbenega bloka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:201
msgid "Edit a building block"
msgstr "Uredite gradbeni blok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:203
msgid ""
"To edit the content of a building block, click it and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab. Available customization options vary depending on "
"the type of block selected."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti vsebino gradbenega bloka, ga kliknite in pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Slog`. Razpoložljive možnosti prilagajanja se razlikujejo "
"glede na vrsto izbranega bloka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:207
msgid ":doc:`Web design elements <elements>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Elementi spletne zasnove <elements>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:208
msgid ":doc:`Visibility <visibility>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Vidnost <visibility>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:211
msgid "Background"
msgstr "Ozadje"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:213
msgid ""
"To modify the background of a building block, select the block, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the color dot or "
"another :guilabel:`Background` option. You can change the color and/or add "
"an image, video, and/or shape. Once you've selected a shape, new fields "
"appear to allow you to customize the shape."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ozadje gradbenega bloka, izberite blok, pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in kliknite barvno piko ali drugo "
"možnost :guilabel:`Ozadje`. Spremenite lahko barvo in/ali dodate sliko, "
"videoposnetek in/ali obliko. Ko izberete obliko, se prikažejo nova polja, ki "
"vam omogočajo prilagajanje oblike."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:219
msgid ""
"Position an element (image, text, etc.) behind or in front of another one by "
"using the :guilabel:`Send to back` or :guilabel:`Bring to front` icons."
msgstr ""
"Postavite element (sliko, besedilo itd.) za ali pred drug element z uporabo "
"ikon :guilabel:`Pošlji v ozadje` ali :guilabel:`Prinesi v ospredje`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Change block position"
msgstr "Sprememba položaja bloka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:225
msgid ""
"To resize a block, click and drag the dots around its edges to adjust it as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti velikost bloka, kliknite in povlecite pike okoli "
"njegovih robov ter ga po potrebi prilagodite."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Adapt block size"
msgstr "Prilagoditev velikosti bloka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:231
msgid ":doc:`General theme <themes>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Splošna tema <themes>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:234
msgid "Layout: grid and columns"
msgstr "Postavitev: mreža in stolpci"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:236
msgid ""
"For most building blocks, you can choose between two layout "
"styles: :ref:`grid <website/building_blocks/grid>` or :ref:`columns (cols) "
"<website/building_blocks/cols>`. To change the default layout style, click "
"the block, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and set the :guilabel:`Layout` "
"field to :guilabel:`Grid` or :guilabel:`Cols`."
msgstr ""
"Za večino gradbenih blokov lahko izbirate med dvema stiloma "
"postavitve: :ref:`mreža <website/building_blocks/grid>` ali :ref:`stolpci "
"<website/building_blocks/cols>`. Če želite spremeniti privzeti slog "
"postavitve, kliknite blok, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in nastavite "
"polje :guilabel:`Postavitev` na :guilabel:`Mreža` ali :guilabel:`Stolpci`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:244
msgid "Grid"
msgstr "Mreža"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:246
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Grid` layout allows you to reposition and resize elements, "
"such as images or text, by dragging and dropping them. When :guilabel:`Grid` "
"is selected, additional options are available to :guilabel:`Add Elements` by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Image`, :guilabel:`Text`, or :guilabel:`Button`."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev :guilabel:`Mreža` vam omogoča premikanje in spreminjanje "
"velikosti elementov, kot so slike ali besedilo, tako da jih povlečete in "
"spustite. Ko je izbrana :guilabel:`Mreža`, so na voljo dodatne možnosti "
"za :guilabel:`Dodajanje elementov` s klikom "
"na :guilabel:`Slika`, :guilabel:`Besedilo` ali :guilabel:`Gumb`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:None
msgid ""
"When the grid layout is selected, choose an image and drag and drop it where "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana mrežna postavitev, izberite sliko in jo povlecite ter "
"spustite, kjer je potrebno."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:256
msgid "Cols"
msgstr "Stolpci"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:258
msgid ""
"Choosing the :guilabel:`Cols` layout allows you to determine the number of "
"elements per line within the block. To do so, select the block to modify, "
"click the dropdown next to the :guilabel:`Cols` field, and adjust the "
"number. You can then modify a specific column's settings using the options "
"in the :guilabel:`Column` section of the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"Izbira postavitve :guilabel:`Stolpci` vam omogoča določitev števila "
"elementov na vrstico znotraj bloka. To storite tako, da izberete blok za "
"spreminjanje, kliknete spustni meni poleg polja :guilabel:`Stolpci` in "
"prilagodite število. Nato lahko spremenite nastavitve določenega stolpca z "
"uporabo možnosti v razdelku :guilabel:`Stolpec` zavihka :guilabel:`Slog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:264
msgid ""
"By default, :doc:`on mobile devices <visibility>`, only one element (column) "
"is visible per line to ensure that content remains easily readable and "
"accessible on smaller screens. To adjust the value, click the :icon:`fa-"
"mobile` (:guilabel:`mobile icon`) at the top of the website editor and adapt "
"the number of columns. Shapes are hidden by default on mobiles."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so :doc:`na mobilnih napravah <visibility>` viden samo en element "
"(stolpec) na vrstico, da vsebina ostane lahko berljiva in dostopna na "
"manjših zaslonih. Če želite prilagoditi vrednost, kliknite :icon:`fa-mobile` "
"(:guilabel:`ikona mobilne naprave`) na vrhu urejevalnika spletnega mesta in "
"prilagodite število stolpcev. Oblike so privzeto skrite na mobilnih napravah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:272
msgid "Save a custom building block"
msgstr "Shranjevanje gradnika po meri"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:274
msgid ""
"You can save a customized building block to reuse it elsewhere. To do so, "
"select it, navigate to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"floppy-o` (:guilabel:`floppy disk`) icon. Click the :guilabel:`Save` button "
"in the popup to confirm saving your custom block."
msgstr ""
"Prilagojen gradbeni blok lahko shranite, da ga ponovno uporabite drugje. To "
"storite tako, da ga izberete, se pomaknete na zavihek :guilabel:`Slog` in "
"kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-floppy-o` (:guilabel:`disketa`). V pojavnem oknu "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Shrani`, da potrdite shranjevanje bloka po meri."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:278
msgid ""
"To add a saved building block to the page, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Blocks` tab and drag and drop the :guilabel:`Custom` block "
"from the :guilabel:`Categories` section. In the popup that opens, click the "
"desired block in the :guilabel:`Custom` category."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati shranjen gradnik na stran, pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Bloki` in povlecite ter spustite blok :guilabel:`Po meri` "
"iz razdelka :guilabel:`Kategorije`. V pojavnem oknu, ki se odpre, kliknite "
"želeni blok v kategoriji :guilabel:`Po meri`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:283
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Insert a block` popup, click :icon:`fa-pencil` "
"(:guilabel:`edit`) to rename the custom block or :icon:`fa-trash` "
"(:guilabel:`delete`) to delete it."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Vstavi blok` kliknite :icon:`fa-pencil` "
"(:guilabel:`uredi`) za preimenovanje gradnika po meri ali :icon:`fa-trash` "
"(:guilabel:`izbriši`) za brisanje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:289
msgid "Create an anchor link"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje sidra povezave"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:291
msgid ""
"Anchor links are hyperlinks that direct users to a **specific section** of a "
"page. To create an anchor link for a block, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Sidra povezav so hiperpovezave, ki uporabnike usmerijo na **določen "
"razdelek** strani. Če želite ustvariti sidro povezave za blok, sledite tem "
"korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:294
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the block you want to link to."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` in izberite blok, na katerega želite povezati."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:295
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`link`) at the top of the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`povezava`) na vrhu "
"zavihka :guilabel:`Slog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:296
msgid ""
"To edit the default anchor name, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the green popup "
"message that opens."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti privzeto ime sidra, kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` v zelenem "
"pojavnem sporočilu, ki se odpre."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:297
msgid "Replace the anchor name and click :guilabel:`Save & copy`."
msgstr "Zamenjajte ime sidra in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in kopiraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:299
msgid ""
"Once the anchor is saved, you can :ref:`link to it <website/elements/links>` "
"from anywhere on your website."
msgstr ""
"Ko je sidro shranjeno, lahko :ref:`povežete nanj <website/elements/links>` "
"od kjerkoli na vašem spletnem mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:5
msgid ""
"Elements help structure and present content effectively. They range from "
"text-based components like :ref:`titles <website/elements/"
"titles>`, :ref:`lists <website/elements/lists>` and :ref:`text highlights "
"<website/elements/text_highlights>` to interactive ones such "
"as :ref:`buttons <website/elements/buttons>` and :ref:`links <website/"
"elements/links>`. Visual elements like :ref:`images <website/elements/"
"images>`, :ref:`icons <website/elements/icons>`, :ref:`videos <website/"
"elements/videos>`, and :ref:`animations <website/elements/animations>` can "
"also be added to improve content presentation and organization."
msgstr ""
"Elementi pomagajo strukturirati in učinkovito predstaviti vsebino. Segajo od "
"besedilnih komponent, kot so :ref:`naslovi <website/elements/"
"titles>`, :ref:`seznami <website/elements/lists>` in :ref:`poudarki besedila "
"<website/elements/text_highlights>`, do interaktivnih, kot so :ref:`gumbi "
"<website/elements/buttons>` in :ref:`povezave <website/elements/links>`. Za "
"izboljšanje predstavitve in organizacije vsebine je mogoče dodati tudi "
"vizualne elemente, kot so :ref:`slike <website/elements/"
"images>`, :ref:`ikone <website/elements/icons>`, :ref:`videoposnetki "
"<website/elements/videos>` in :ref:`animacije <website/elements/animations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:13
msgid "To add or modify a website element:"
msgstr "Če želite dodati ali spremeniti element spletnega mesta:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:15
msgid "Navigate to the relevant website page and click on :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se na ustrezno stran spletnega mesta in kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:16
msgid ""
"Click the section on the page where you want to add or modify an element."
msgstr "Kliknite odsek na strani, kjer želite dodati ali spremeniti element."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:17
msgid "Make the necessary changes."
msgstr "Opravite potrebne spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:18
msgid "Click on :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:21
msgid ""
"The default styles for headings, buttons, links, and paragraph text, for "
"example, are defined in the :doc:`Theme tab <themes>` of the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti slogi za naslove, gumbe, povezave in besedilo odstavka so na primer "
"definirani na zavihku :doc:`Tema <themes>` urejevalnika spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:None
msgid "Type / to add website elements."
msgstr "Vnesite /, če želite dodati elemente spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:30
msgid "Titles"
msgstr "Naslovi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:32
msgid ""
"Titles define headings and organize website content into different levels "
"for clarity and structure. To insert a title, type `/title`, choose the "
"heading style (:guilabel:`Heading 1`, :guilabel:`Heading 2`, "
"or :guilabel:`Heading 3`), and type the text."
msgstr ""
"Naslovi določajo naslove in organizirajo vsebino spletnega mesta v različne "
"ravni za jasnost in strukturo. Če želite vstaviti naslov, vnesite `/title`, "
"izberite slog naslova (:guilabel:`Naslov 1`, :guilabel:`Naslov 2` "
"ali :guilabel:`Naslov 3`) in vnesite besedilo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:37
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type the text, select it, and choose the appropriate style "
"from the :guilabel:`Inline Text` section in the :guilabel:`Customize` tab of "
"the website editor. Additional formatting options, such as fonts and colors, "
"are also available in this section."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da vnesete besedilo, ga izberete in izberete ustrezen slog "
"v razdelku :guilabel:`Vdelano besedilo` na zavihku :guilabel:`Prilagodi` "
"urejevalnika spletnega mesta. V tem razdelku so na voljo tudi dodatne "
"možnosti oblikovanja, kot so pisave in barve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:46
msgid ""
"Buttons are interactive elements that allow to link to another page or to a "
"page anchor. To insert a button:"
msgstr ""
"Gumbi so interaktivni elementi, ki omogočajo povezavo na drugo stran ali na "
"sidro strani. Če želite vstaviti gumb:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:49
msgid "Type `/button`."
msgstr "Vnesite `/button`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:50
msgid "Enter the button's label in the :guilabel:`Link Label` field."
msgstr "Vnesite oznako gumba v polje :guilabel:`Oznaka povezave`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:51
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`URL or Email`. Type `/` to search for a page and `#` to "
"link to an anchor."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`URL ali e-pošto`. Vnesite `/` za iskanje strani in `#` za "
"povezavo na sidro."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:52
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Style`, :guilabel:`Size`, and :guilabel:`Layout` to "
"define the button's appearance."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :guilabel:`Slog`, :guilabel:`Velikost` in :guilabel:`Postavitev`, "
"da določite videz gumba."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:54
msgid ""
"If needed, toggle the switch to open the linked page or anchor in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi preklopite stikalo, da odprete povezano stran ali sidro v novem "
"zavihku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:55
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply` to save changes."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`, da shranite spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:58
msgid ""
"To modify an existing button, click the button and edit the options in "
"the :guilabel:`Inline text` section of the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obstoječi gumb, kliknite gumb in uredite možnosti v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Vdelano besedilo` urejevalnika spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:66
msgid "To insert an image:"
msgstr "Za vstavljanje slike:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:68
msgid "Type `/image`."
msgstr "Vnesite `/image`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:69
msgid ""
":doc:`Search the Unsplash database </applications/general/integrations/"
"unsplash>` or click :guilabel:`Upload an image` to choose a file from your "
"local images."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Išči v bazi podatkov Unsplash </applications/general/integrations/"
"unsplash>` ali kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži sliko`, da izberete datoteko iz "
"svojih lokalnih slik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:71
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:72
msgid ""
"To customize the image, click on the image and edit the options in "
"the :guilabel:`Image` section of the website editor. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi sliko, kliknite nanjo in uredite možnosti v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Slika` urejevalnika spletnega mesta. Na primer:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:75
msgid ":guilabel:`Replace` the image."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Zamenjajte` sliko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:76
msgid ""
"Define an `alt tag <https://help.siteimprove.com/support/solutions/articles/"
"80000448480-where-are-alt-tags- used-and-why-are-they-important>`_ in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` field."
msgstr ""
"Določite `alt oznako <https://help.siteimprove.com/support/solutions/"
"articles/80000448480-where-are-alt-tags- used-and-why-are-they-important>`_ "
"v polju :guilabel:`Opis`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:78
msgid ""
"Enter a title tag in the :guilabel:`Tooltip` field. This text will appear "
"when visitors hover their mouse over the image."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Namig` vnesite oznako naslova. To besedilo se bo "
"prikazalo, ko bodo obiskovalci z miško lebdeli nad sliko."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:80
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Shape`; some shapes also allow for color customization."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`Obliko`; nekatere oblike omogočajo tudi prilagajanje "
"barve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:81
msgid ""
"Adjust the image's :guilabel:`Width`, e.g., to improve performance. A "
"smaller size may be suggested if it is sufficient for display."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite :guilabel:`Širino` slike, npr. za izboljšanje zmogljivosti. "
"Manjša velikost je lahko predlagana, če je zadostna za prikaz."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:83
msgid "Resize the image using the :guilabel:`Transform` tool."
msgstr "Spremenite velikost slike s pomočjo orodja :guilabel:`Preoblikuj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:84
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`Padding` to add space (in pixels) around the image."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite :guilabel:`Razmik`, da dodate prostor (v pikslih) okoli slike."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:85
msgid "Etc."
msgstr "Itd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:90
msgid "Videos"
msgstr "Videoposnetki"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:92
msgid ""
"To add a video, type `/video`, insert the URL, and turn on the desired "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje videoposnetka vnesite `/video`, vstavite URL in vklopite želene "
"možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Autoplay`: to automatically play the video when the page is "
"accessed. The video is automatically muted by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samodejno predvajanje`: za samodejno predvajanje videoposnetka ob "
"dostopu do strani. Videoposnetek je privzeto samodejno utišan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:96
msgid ":guilabel:`Loop`: to play the video on a loop."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Zanka`: za predvajanje videoposnetka v zanki."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:97
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide player controls`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skrij kontrole predvajalnika`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:98
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide fullscreen button`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skrij gumb za celozaslonski prikaz`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start at`: to define the timestamp where the video should start, "
"in `MM:SS` format."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Začni pri`: za določitev časovne oznake, kjer naj se video začne, "
"v obliki `MM:SS`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:104
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikone"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:106
msgid ""
"To insert an icon, type `/image`, go to the :guilabel:`Icons` tab, select an "
"icon, and click :guilabel:`Add`. To modify an icon, click on it and use "
"the :guilabel:`Icon` section of the website editor to customize options, "
"such as :guilabel:`Color`, :guilabel:`Size`, :ref:`Animations <website/"
"elements/animations>`, :guilabel:`Shape`, etc."
msgstr ""
"Za vstavljanje ikone vnesite `/image`, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Ikone`, "
"izberite ikono in kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`. Za spreminjanje ikone kliknite "
"nanjo in uporabite razdelek :guilabel:`Ikona` urejevalnika spletnega mesta "
"za prilagajanje možnosti, kot "
"so :guilabel:`Barva`, :guilabel:`Velikost`, :ref:`Animacije <website/"
"elements/animations>`, :guilabel:`Oblika` itd."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:189
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Povezave"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:116
msgid ""
"Links are used to connect different pages and resources, guiding visitors "
"and improving navigation. To add a link, type `/link`, then, in the pop-up "
"that opens, enter the link's :guilabel:`Label` and add the :guilabel:`URL or "
"Email`. Type `/` to search for a page and `#` to link to an :ref:`anchor "
"<website/building_blocks/anchor>`."
msgstr ""
"Povezave se uporabljajo za povezovanje različnih strani in virov, usmerjanje "
"obiskovalcev in izboljšanje navigacije. Za dodajanje povezave vnesite `/"
"link`, nato v pojavnem oknu, ki se odpre, vnesite :guilabel:`Oznako` "
"povezave in dodajte :guilabel:`URL ali e-pošto`. Vnesite `/` za iskanje "
"strani in `#` za povezavo na :ref:`sidro <website/building_blocks/anchor>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:122
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Style` field is set to :guilabel:`Link`. Select a "
"different style to transform the link into a :ref:`button <website/elements/"
"buttons>`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je polje :guilabel:`Slog` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Povezava`. "
"Izberite drug slog, da povezavo spremenite v :ref:`gumb <website/elements/"
"buttons>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:128
msgid "Lists"
msgstr "Seznam"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:130
msgid ""
"Lists help organize content clearly, making information easier to read and "
"improving web pages' structures. Type `/list` and choose from three "
"different types of lists: :guilabel:`Bulleted lists`, :guilabel:`Numbered "
"lists`, or :guilabel:`Checklists`."
msgstr ""
"Seznami pomagajo jasno organizirati vsebino, zaradi česar so informacije "
"lažje berljive in se izboljša struktura spletnih strani. Vnesite `/list` in "
"izbirajte med tremi različnimi vrstami seznamov: :guilabel:`Seznami z "
"alinejami`, :guilabel:`Oštevilčeni seznami` ali :guilabel:`Kontrolni "
"seznami`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:137
msgid "Text highlights"
msgstr "Poudarki besedila"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:139
msgid ""
"Highlights can be added to titles and text using in the :guilabel:`Inline "
"Text` section of the website editor. To add a highlight:"
msgstr ""
"Poudarkam lahko dodate naslove in besedilo v razdelku :guilabel:`Besedilo v "
"vrstici` urejevalnika spletnega mesta. Dodajanje poudarka:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:142
msgid "Select the text or title you want to highlight."
msgstr "Izberite besedilo ali naslov, ki ga želite poudariti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:143
msgid "In the website editor, click on :guilabel:`Highlight`."
msgstr "V urejevalniku spletnega mesta kliknite :guilabel:`Poudarek`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:144
msgid "Select the highlight style."
msgstr "Izberite slog poudarka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:145
msgid "Modify its :guilabel:`Color`."
msgstr "Spremenite njegovo :guilabel:`Barvo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:146
msgid "Choose its :guilabel:`Thickness`."
msgstr "Izberite njegovo :guilabel:`Debelino`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:None
msgid "Highlight texts and titles"
msgstr "Poudarite besedila in naslove"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:154
msgid "Animations"
msgstr "Animacije"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:156
msgid ""
"Animations are used to add movement to :doc:`building blocks "
"<building_blocks>` and website elements such as images and text. Three types "
"of animation are available: :guilabel:`On Scroll`, :guilabel:`On "
"Appearance`, and :guilabel:`On Hover` (for images only)."
msgstr ""
"Animacije se uporabljajo za dodajanje gibanja :doc:`gradnikom "
"<building_blocks>` in elementom spletnega mesta, kot so slike in besedilo. "
"Na voljo so tri vrste animacij: :guilabel:`Ob pomikanju`, :guilabel:`Ob "
"pojavitvi` in :guilabel:`Ob lebdenju` (samo za slike)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:160
msgid "To add an animation to a website element:"
msgstr "Dodajanje animacije elementu spletnega mesta:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:162
msgid "Click on the element."
msgstr "Kliknite element."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the website editor, go to the relevant section for the element "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Button`, :guilabel:`Column`, :guilabel:`Inline Text`, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""
"V urejevalniku spletnega mesta pojdite na ustrezen razdelek za element "
"(npr. :guilabel:`Gumb`, :guilabel:`Stolpec`, :guilabel:`Besedilo v vrstici` "
"itd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:165
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Animation` field, select the desired animation type."
msgstr "V polju :guilabel:`Animacija` izberite želeno vrsto animacije."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:166
msgid ""
"Customize the animation settings as needed. Available options vary based on "
"the selected animation type."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi prilagodite nastavitve animacije. Razpoložljive možnosti se "
"razlikujejo glede na izbrano vrsto animacije."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:170
msgid "Animations on scroll"
msgstr "Animacije ob pomikanju"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:172
msgid "For animations on scroll, it is possible to:"
msgstr "Za animacije ob pomikanju je mogoče:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:174
msgid ""
"Choose :guilabel:`In` to add the animation when the element enters the "
"screen and :guilabel:`Out` to add it when it leaves the screen."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Vhod`, da dodate animacijo, ko element vstopi na zaslon, "
"in :guilabel:`Izhod`, da jo dodate, ko zapusti zaslon."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:176
msgid "Select an :guilabel:`Effect`."
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Učinek`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:188
msgid "Choose the :guilabel:`Direction` of the effect."
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Smer` učinka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:178
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:191
msgid "Adapt the :guilabel:`Intensity` of the effect."
msgstr "Prilagodite :guilabel:`Intenzivnost` učinka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:179
msgid ""
"Define the :guilabel:`Scroll Zone`, where the first value represents the "
"percentage of the screen shown when the effect starts, and the second value "
"represents its percentage at the end."
msgstr ""
"Določite :guilabel:`Drsno območje`, kjer prva vrednost predstavlja odstotek "
"zaslona, prikazanega ob začetku učinka, druga vrednost pa njegov odstotek ob "
"koncu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:183
msgid "Animations on appearance"
msgstr "Animacije ob prikazu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:185
msgid "For animations on appearance, it is possible to:"
msgstr "Za animacije ob prikazu je mogoče:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:187
msgid "Choose among different effects."
msgstr "Izbrati med različnimi učinki."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:189
msgid ""
"Pick a :guilabel:`Trigger` option to define when the animation occurs: "
"either the :guilabel:`First Time only` or :guilabel:`Every Time`."
msgstr ""
"Izberite možnost :guilabel:`Sprožilec`, da določite, kdaj pride do "
"animacije: bodisi :guilabel:`Samo prvič` bodisi :guilabel:`Vsakič`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:192
msgid ""
"If you want the animation to be triggered after a number of seconds, define "
"this number in the :guilabel:`Start After` field."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se animacija sproži po določenem številu sekund, to število "
"določite v polju :guilabel:`Začni po`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:194
msgid "Choose a :guilabel:`Duration` for the animation."
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Trajanje` animacije."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:197
msgid "Animations on hover (for images only)"
msgstr "Animacije ob prehodu miške (samo za slike)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:199
msgid ""
"Animations :guilabel:`On hover` can be added to :ref:`images <website/"
"elements/images>`. You can choose the :guilabel:`Effect` of the animation, "
"as well as the :guilabel:`Color` and the :guilabel:`Stroke Width`."
msgstr ""
"Animacije :guilabel:`Ob prehodu miške` lahko dodate :ref:`slikam <website/"
"elements/images>`. Izberete lahko :guilabel:`Učinek` animacije, kot "
"tudi :guilabel:`Barvo` in :guilabel:`Širino poteze`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:204
msgid ":doc:`Odoo HTML editor </applications/essentials/html_editor>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Urejevalnik Odoo HTML </applications/essentials/html_editor>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo provides a range of theme :ref:`customization options <website/themes/"
"page-layouts>` to define the website's :ref:`colors <website/themes/colors>` "
"and :ref:`fonts <website/themes/fonts>`, and the appearance "
"of :ref:`paragraphs and headings <website/themes/paragraphs-"
"headings>`, :ref:`buttons <website/themes/button-styles>`, :ref:`links "
"<website/themes/link-style>`, and :ref:`input fields <website/themes/input-"
"fields>`. Additional :ref:`advanced settings <website/themes/advanced>` are "
"also available."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:12
msgid ""
"When setting up a website for the first time, you are prompted to select a "
"theme. Hover the mouse over the themes to see an extended preview of each "
"one. Click a theme to select it, or click the :guilabel:`View more themes` "
"button to display the full list of available themes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:17
msgid ""
"If you leave without selecting a theme, the website is created with the "
"default theme."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:21
msgid ""
"To customize the theme, open the website editor, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Theme` tab, and go to the :guilabel:`Website` section. You "
"can:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:24
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Switch Theme` to open the theme selector. Hover the mouse "
"over the themes to see an extended preview of each one. Click :guilabel:`Use "
"this theme` to apply it to the website."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:26
msgid "Add a :doc:`language <../configuration/multi_website>` for the website."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:27
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Page Layout` to change the overall display and spacing "
"of building blocks and website elements on pages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:29
msgid "Customize the layout's :guilabel:`Background` by:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:31
msgid "choosing a :ref:`color <website/themes/colors>`;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:32
msgid "adding an :ref:`image <website/elements/images>`;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:33
msgid "using a selected image in a :guilabel:`Pattern`; or"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:34
msgid "selecting :icon:`fa-ban` :guilabel:`None`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:36
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to apply the changes to the website."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:41
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:43
msgid ""
"Odoo's website editor features two main types of colors: :ref:`theme colors "
"<website/themes/theme-colors>` and :ref:`status colors <website/themes/"
"status-colors>`."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik spletne strani Odoo vsebuje dve glavni vrsti barv: :ref:`barvne "
"sheme <website/themes/theme-colors>` in :ref:`statusne barve <website/themes/"
"status-colors>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:49
msgid "Theme colors"
msgstr "Barve teme"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:51
msgid ""
"Theme colors refer to the set of colors displayed across all pages of the "
"website. They consist of five colors: three :guilabel:`Main` colors, used "
"mainly for buttons and links, and two :guilabel:`Light & Dark` colors, used "
"mainly for text and headings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:55
msgid ""
"To edit the website's colors, navigate to the :guilabel:`Colors` section of "
"the :guilabel:`Theme` tab. Then:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:58
msgid ""
"Click the color you want to change, then select a "
"predefined :guilabel:`Solid` color or click :guilabel:`Custom` to pick a "
"specific color tone manually (or add its #HEX or RGBA code). Click :icon:`fa-"
"trash` (:guilabel:`Reset`) to remove the color selection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:61
msgid ""
"Click the paint palette icon and choose a color palette. As a result, all "
"color customizations are reset."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:64
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically creates :guilabel:`Color Presets` for the chosen colors "
"or palette. These predefined color combinations are applied to various "
"elements of the website to create a structured and visually appealing "
"design. When selecting a color palette, its presets define how those colors "
"are distributed across different elements. To modify them, "
"click :guilabel:`Color Presets`, then select a preset to open the "
"customization dropdown. Each color preset contains colors for the building "
"block’s :guilabel:`Background`, :guilabel:`Text`, :guilabel:`Headings`, :guilabel:`Links`, :guilabel:`Primary "
"Buttons`, and :guilabel:`Secondary Buttons`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:73
msgid ""
"To apply a color preset to a building block, select the building block, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, click the color dot located next "
"to :guilabel:`Background`, and choose a :guilabel:`Theme`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:78
msgid ""
"Changing a color preset automatically updates the colors of both the default "
"preset and the building blocks that use it."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje barvne predloge samodejno posodobi barve tako privzete predloge "
"kot gradnikov, ki jo uporabljajo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:84
msgid "Status colors"
msgstr "Statusne barve"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:86
msgid ""
"Status colors indicate the status of certain actions "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Success`, :guilabel:`Warning`, etc.). They're used in pop-"
"up messages that appear to provide feedback to users and website visitors. "
"To customize the website's :guilabel:`Status Colors`, scroll down to "
"the :ref:`Advanced <website/themes/advanced>` section and click the dots to "
"change their color."
msgstr ""
"Barve stanja označujejo stanje določenih dejanj "
"(npr. :guilabel:`Uspešno`, :guilabel:`Opozorilo` itd.). Uporabljajo se v "
"pojavnih sporočilih, ki se prikažejo uporabnikom in obiskovalcem spletnega "
"mesta ter jim zagotavljajo povratne informacije. Če želite "
"prilagoditi :guilabel:`Barve stanja` spletnega mesta, se pomaknite navzdol "
"do razdelka :ref:`Napredno <website/themes/advanced>` in kliknite pike za "
"spremembo njihove barve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:93
msgid ""
"Information related to a successful action on the website appears "
"in :icon:`oi-green-dot` green."
msgstr ""
"Informacije, povezane z uspešnim dejanjem na spletnem mestu, so prikazane "
"v :icon:`oi-green-dot` zeleni barvi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:0
msgid "Status color selection"
msgstr "Izbira statusne barve"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:0
msgid "Success pop-up"
msgstr "Pojavno sporočilo o uspehu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:104
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Pisave"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:106
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to customize the font family and font size of website "
"elements, including :ref:`paragraphs and headings <website/themes/paragraphs-"
"headings>`, :ref:`buttons <website/themes/button-styles>`, and :ref:`input "
"fields <website/themes/input-fields>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo vam omogoča prilagoditev družine pisave in velikosti pisave elementov "
"spletnega mesta, vključno z :ref:`odstavki in naslovi <website/themes/"
"paragraphs-headings>`, :ref:`gumbi <website/themes/button-styles>` "
"in :ref:`vnosnimi polji <website/themes/input-fields>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Font Size`: In "
"the :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings`, :guilabel:`Button`, "
"and :guilabel:`Input Fields` sections, use the :guilabel:`Font Size` field "
"to set a default size. Click the :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`Toggle "
"more options`) icon to expand the section and define custom sizes (e.g., "
"based on the heading level, button size, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Velikost pisave`: V "
"razdelkih :guilabel:`Odstavek`, :guilabel:`Naslovi`, :guilabel:`Gumb` "
"in :guilabel:`Vnosna polja` uporabite polje :guilabel:`Velikost pisave` za "
"nastavitev privzete velikosti. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-caret-right` "
"(:guilabel:`Preklopi več možnosti`), da razširite razdelek in določite "
"velikosti po meri (npr. glede na raven naslova, velikost gumba itd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Font Family`: In the :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings`, "
"and :guilabel:`Button` sections, select a font from the dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Font Family`: V "
"razdelkih :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings` in :guilabel:`Button` "
"izberite pisavo iz spustnega menija."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:118
msgid ""
"When :guilabel:`System Fonts` is selected, Odoo uses the native fonts "
"already installed on the visitor's operating system. For example, Android "
"uses **Roboto** as its default system font."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Sistemske pisave`, Odoo uporablja izvorne "
"pisave, ki so že nameščene v operacijskem sistemu obiskovalca. Na primer, "
"Android kot privzeto sistemsko pisavo uporablja **Roboto**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:122
msgid "Custom fonts"
msgstr "Pisave po meri"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:124
msgid ""
"To add a custom font not available by default in Odoo, click "
"the :guilabel:`Font Family` dropdown and select :guilabel:`Add a Custom "
"Font` at the bottom. In the :guilabel:`Add a Google font or upload a custom "
"font` pop-up:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati pisavo po meri, ki privzeto ni na voljo v Odooju, kliknite "
"spustni meni :guilabel:`Družina pisave` in na dnu izberite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"pisavo po meri`. V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Dodaj pisavo Google ali naloži "
"pisavo po meri`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:128
msgid ""
"To add a Google font, open the :guilabel:`Select a Google Font` dropdown and "
"select the desired font. Toggle off the :guilabel:`Serve font from Google "
"servers` if your website is operated from a location where regulations "
"require compliance with laws such as, but not limited to, the European "
"Union's GDPR. This will ensure the Google Font is stored on the website's "
"server rather than on Google's servers."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati pisavo Google, odprite spustni meni :guilabel:`Izberite "
